"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解一】1) 应用动力学方程讨论。\n\n在地面参照系中，取向右为正向。小物块和木板的加速度分别为\n$$\na_{m}=\\mu g \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\na_{M}=-\\dfrac{1}{M}\\mu mg \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n$m$相对$M$的相对加速度为\n$$\na'_{m}=a_{m}-a_{M}=\\mu g\\left(1+\\dfrac{m}{M}\\right) \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n$m$相对$M$的初速度为\n$$\nv'_{m0}=-V_{0} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n小物块从木板左端滑出，则$m$在$M$上的相对位移为$-L$。根据上述各量可以在木板参照系中写出运动学方程\n$$\nv'^{2}_{m}-v'^{2}_{m0}=2a'_{m}\\cdot(-L)\n$$\n其中$v'_{m}$为小物块滑离木板时的相对速度，方向向左，得\n$$\nv'_{m}=-\\sqrt{V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gL\\left(1+\\dfrac{m}{M}\\right)} \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n小物块在木板上滑行的时间$t$满足\n$$\nv'_{m}=v'_{m0}+a'_{m}t\n$$\n$$\nt=\\dfrac{v'_{m}-v'_{m0}}{a'_{m}}=\\dfrac{1}{\\mu g\\left(1+\\dfrac{m}{M}\\right)}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right] \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\n$M$在$t$时刻的速度为$V$\n$$\nV=V_{0}+a_{M}t=V_{0}-\\dfrac{m}{M(M+m)}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]\n$$\n$m$在$t$时刻对地的速度（即滑离$M$时的速度）为$v$\n$$\nv=v'_{m}+V=\\dfrac{MV_{0}}{M+m}-\\dfrac{1}{M+m}\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)} \\quad \\text{⑦}\n$$\n为使$v$有实数解，应满足$M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)\\geqslant0$，得$V_{0}$应满足的条件\n$$\nV_{0}\\geqslant\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2\\mu gL(M+m)}{M}} \\quad \\text{⑧}\n$$\n系统损失的机械能等于一对摩擦力做的功，它等于摩擦力与相对位移的乘积，即\n$$\n|\\Delta E|=\\mu mgL \\quad \\text{⑨}\n$$\n\n2) 设小物块在木板上向左滑行的距离为$S$，当向右取为正时，滑行的相对位移为\n$$\nx'=-S\n$$\n再利用相对加速度式③、相对初速度式④，以及相对末速度为零（停在木板上），写出$S$满足的关系式\n$$\n0-v'^{2}_{m0}=2a'_{m}(-S)\n$$\n$$\nS=\\dfrac{v'^{2}_{m0}}{2a'_{m}}=\\dfrac{MV_{0}^{2}}{2\\mu g(M+m)} \\quad \\text{⑩}\n$$\n整个过程中损失的机械能为\n$$\n|\\Delta E|=\\mu mgS=\\dfrac{mV_{0}^{2}}{2(M+m)} \\quad \\text{⑪}\n$$\n\n【分析与解二】1) 这里利用系统水平动量守恒、动能定理以及小物块运动的动量定理\n$$\nMV_{0}=Mv+mv \\quad \\text{⑫}\n$$\n$$\n-\\mu mgL=\\left(\\dfrac{1}{2}Mv^{2}+\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^{2}\\right)-\\dfrac{1}{2}MV_{0}^{2} \\quad \\text{⑬}\n$$\n$$\n\\mu mgt=mv \\quad \\text{⑭}\n$$\n其中$V$和$v$是小物块滑离木板时，木板和小物块的速度。由式⑬知，整个过程中系统损失的机械能为\n$$\n|\\Delta E|=\\mu mgL\n$$\n即式⑨，再联立式⑫和⑬，消去$V$整理得\n$$\n(Mm+m^{2})v^{2}-2mMv_{0}v+2\\mu mgL=0\n$$\n解出$v$\n$$\nv=\\dfrac{1}{M+m}\\left[MV_{0}\\pm\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]\n$$\n小物块能够从木板滑落，$v$应有实数解，所以\n$$\nM^{2}V_{0}^{2}\\geqslant2\\mu gML(M+m)\n$$\n$V_{0}$应满足条件\n$$\nV_{0}\\geqslant\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2\\mu gL(M+m)}{M}}\n$$\n又因为小物块所能达到的最大速度应为$v_{\\max}=V$，根据方程⑫，得到\n$$\nv_{\\max}=\\dfrac{M}{M+m}V_{0}\n$$\n因此，在$v$的实数解中，只能取\n$$\nv=\\dfrac{1}{M+m}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]\n$$\n这就是小物块滑离木板时的速度。与式⑧相同。\n\n由式⑭可得小物块在木板上滑行的时间\n$$\nt=\\dfrac{1}{\\mu g(M+m)}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]\n$$\n与式⑥相同。", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution 1】1) Using dynamic equations.\n\nIn the ground frame, taking right as positive, the accelerations of the block and plank are:\n$$\na_{m}=\\mu g \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\na_{M}=-\\dfrac{1}{M}\\mu mg \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nThe relative acceleration of $m$ with respect to $M$ is:\n$$\na'_{m}=a_{m}-a_{M}=\\mu g\\left(1+\\dfrac{m}{M}\\right) \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nThe initial relative velocity of $m$ with respect to $M$ is:\n$$\nv'_{m0}=-V_{0} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\nWhen the block slides off the left end, its relative displacement on $M$ is $-L$. In the plank's frame, the kinematic equation is:\n$$\nv'^{2}_{m}-v'^{2}_{m0}=2a'_{m}\\cdot(-L)\n$$\nwhere $v'_{m}$ is the relative velocity when sliding off (leftward):\n$$\nv'_{m}=-\\sqrt{V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gL\\left(1+\\dfrac{m}{M}\\right)} \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\nThe sliding time $t$ satisfies:\n$$\nv'_{m}=v'_{m0}+a'_{m}t\n$$\n$$\nt=\\dfrac{v'_{m}-v'_{m0}}{a'_{m}}=\\dfrac{1}{\\mu g\\left(1+\\dfrac{m}{M}\\right)}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right] \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\nThe velocity of $M$ at time $t$ is:\n$$\nV=V_{0}+a_{M}t=V_{0}-\\dfrac{m}{M(M+m)}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]\n$$\nThe velocity of $m$ at time $t$ (when sliding off) is:\n$$\nv=v'_{m}+V=\\dfrac{MV_{0}}{M+m}-\\dfrac{1}{M+m}\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)} \\quad \\text{⑦}\n$$\nFor $v$ to be real, we need $M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)\\geqslant0$, so:\n$$\nV_{0}\\geqslant\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2\\mu gL(M+m)}{M}} \\quad \\text{⑧}\n$$\nThe mechanical energy lost by the system equals the work done by friction over the relative displacement:\n$$\n|\\Delta E|=\\mu mgL \\quad \\text{⑨}\n$$\n\n2) Let the sliding distance of the block on the plank be $S$. Taking right as positive, the relative displacement is $x'=-S$. Using ③, ④, and final relative velocity $0$:\n$$\n0-v'^{2}_{m0}=2a'_{m}(-S)\n$$\n$$\nS=\\dfrac{v'^{2}_{m0}}{2a'_{m}}=\\dfrac{MV_{0}^{2}}{2\\mu g(M+m)} \\quad \\text{⑩}\n$$\nThe energy loss is:\n$$\n|\\Delta E|=\\mu mgS=\\dfrac{mV_{0}^{2}}{2(M+m)} \\quad \\text{⑪}\n$$\n\n【Analysis and Solution 2】1) Using conservation of momentum, work-energy theorem, and momentum theorem for the block:\n$$\nMV_{0}=Mv+mv \\quad \\text{⑫}\n$$\n$$\n-\\mu mgL=\\left(\\dfrac{1}{2}Mv^{2}+\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^{2}\\right)-\\dfrac{1}{2}MV_{0}^{2} \\quad \\text{⑬}\n$$\n$$\n\\mu mgt=mv \\quad \\text{⑭}\n$$\nFrom ⑬, the energy loss is $|\\Delta E|=\\mu mgL$. Solving ⑫ and ⑬:\n$$\n(Mm+m^{2})v^{2}-2mMv_{0}v+2\\mu mgL=0\n$$\n$$\nv=\\dfrac{1}{M+m}\\left[MV_{0}\\pm\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]\n$$\nFor the block to slide off, $v$ must be real, so:\n$$\nM^{2}V_{0}^{2}\\geqslant2\\mu gML(M+m) \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad V_{0}\\geqslant\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2\\mu gL(M+m)}{M}}\n$$\nSince the maximum speed of the block is $v_{\\max}=\\dfrac{M}{M+m}V_{0}$, we take the smaller root:\n$$\nv=\\dfrac{1}{M+m}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]\n$$\nThe sliding time from ⑭ is:\n$$\nt=\\dfrac{1}{\\mu g(M+m)}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["质量为$M$、长为$L$的木板以速度$V_0$向右运动，右端放上质量为$m$的小物块。"], 
"img_en": ["A plank of mass $M$ and length $L$ moves right with speed $V_0$, and a block of mass $m$ is placed at its right end."], 
"problem_answer": "1) 系统损失的机械能为 $|\\Delta E|=\\mu mgL$；小物块在木板上运动的时间为 $t=\\dfrac{1}{\\mu g(M+m)}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]$；小物块脱离木板时的速度为 $v=\\dfrac{1}{M+m}\\left[MV_{0}-\\sqrt{M^{2}V_{0}^{2}-2\\mu gML(M+m)}\\right]$；$V_0$ 需满足 $V_{0}\\geqslant\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2\\mu gL(M+m)}{M}}$。\n\n2) 小物块滑行距离为 $S=\\dfrac{MV_{0}^{2}}{2\\mu g(M+m)}$；系统损失的机械能为 $|\\Delta E|=\\dfrac{mV_{0}^{2}}{2(M+m)}$；木板的最小长度为 $L_{\\min}=\\dfrac{MV_{0}^{2}}{2\\mu g(M+m)}$。", "problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 4 }

{ "problem_id": "85", 
"problem_text_cn": "池塘中一只青蛙停在一叶静止的、圆形荷叶中央。青蛙质量为$m$，荷叶质量为$M$、半径为$R$。\n\n1) 若青蛙能够一次跳离荷叶，那么青蛙至少应做多少功？\n\n2) 若青蛙从此荷叶中央起跳，正好跳落在紧挨着的另一叶完全相同的荷叶中央，随之一起向前滑动。试求机械能损失与青蛙所做功的比值。\n\n设青蛙跳离或跳落荷叶时，荷叶均不产生竖直方向运动，荷叶只能在水面无阻力地滑动。", 
"problem_text_en": "A frog of mass $m$ rests at the center of a stationary, circular lily pad of mass $M$ and radius $R$ in a pond.\n\n1) If the frog can jump off the lily pad in one leap, what is the minimum work it must do?\n\n2) If the frog jumps from the center of this pad and lands exactly at the center of an identical adjacent pad, which then slides forward together with the frog, find the ratio of the mechanical energy loss to the work done by the frog.\n\nAssume that when the frog jumps off or lands, the pad does not move vertically and slides without resistance on the water.", 
"problem_img": [], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】1) 设青蛙起跳后瞬间相对地面的水平速度分量和竖直向上速度分量分别为$v_x$和$v_y$，而荷叶后退速度为$v$，则跳起过程中青蛙做的功为\n$$\nW=\\dfrac{1}{2}Mv^{2}+\\dfrac{1}{2}m(v_{x}^{2}+v_{y}^{2}) \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n利用水平方向动量守恒定律，$v_x$和$v$满足关系\n$$\nmv_{x}=Mv \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n在荷叶参照系中，青蛙跳起后的相对$x$分量速度为\n$$\nv'_{x}=v_{x}+v\n$$\n根据题文要求，水平方向相对位移满足\n$$\nx'\\geqslant R\n$$\n又\n$$\nx'=(v_{x}+v)t=\\dfrac{2v_{y}}{g}(v_{x}+v)\n$$\n所以\n$$\nR\\leqslant\\dfrac{2v_{y}}{g}(v_{x}+v)\n$$\n$$\nv_{y}\\geqslant\\dfrac{gR}{2(v_{x}+v)}=\\dfrac{MgR}{2v_{x}(M+m)} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n联立方程①～③，得\n$$\nW\\geqslant\\dfrac{m(M+m)}{2M}v_{x}^{2}+\\dfrac{nmM^{2}g^{2}R^{2}}{8(M+m)^{2}v_{x}^{2}} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n利用\n$$\nA+B\\geqslant2\\sqrt{AB}\\quad(A,B\\text{为正量})\n$$\n改写式④，即\n$$\nW\\geqslant2\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m(M+m)}{2M}v_{x}^{2}\\cdot\\dfrac{nmM^{2}g^{2}R^{2}}{8(M+m)^{2}v_{x}^{2}}}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m^{2}M}{M+m}}gR\n$$\n因此，青蛙为跳出荷叶，至少应做的功为\n$$\nW_{\\min}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m^{2}M}{M+m}}gR\n$$\n\n2) 为了便于处理，我们把青蛙起跳后瞬间相对地面的速度分量$v_x$和$v_y$，改为相对地面的速率$v_0$和起跳方向和水平方向夹角$\\theta$。因此，青蛙落到$2R$处的紧邻荷叶中心，满足射程表达式\n$$\n2R=\\dfrac{2v_{0}^{2}\\sin\\theta\\cos\\theta}{g}=\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}\\sin2\\theta}{g}\n$$\n可得起跳速率表达式\n$$\nv_{0}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2gR}{\\sin2\\theta}} \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\n依起跳前后水平方向动量守恒，荷叶后退速度$v$满足\n$$\nMv=mv_{0}\\cos\\theta \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad v=\\dfrac{m}{M}v_{0}\\cos\\theta \\quad \\text{⑦}\n$$\n青蛙落到紧邻荷叶中心后，设青蛙与此荷叶的共同水平速度为$V$，则再次利用水平方向动量守恒定律\n$$\nmv_{0}\\cos\\theta=(M+m)V \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad V=\\dfrac{m}{M+m}v_{0}\\cos\\theta \\quad \\text{⑧}\n$$\n青蛙做功为\n$$\nW=\\dfrac{1}{2}Mv^{2}+\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{0}^{2}=\\dfrac{mv_{0}^{2}}{2M^{2}}(m\\cos^{2}\\theta+M) \\quad \\text{⑨}\n$$\n机械能损失\n$$\n\\Delta E=W-\\dfrac{1}{2}Mv^{2}-\\dfrac{1}{2}(M+m)V^{2}\n$$\n分别代入式⑦、⑧、⑨，得\n$$\n\\Delta E=\\dfrac{mv_{0}^{2}}{2(M+m)}(m\\sin^{2}\\theta+M)\n$$\n所求比值为\n$$\n\\dfrac{\\Delta E}{W}=\\dfrac{M(m\\sin^{2}\\theta+M)}{(M+m)(m\\cos^{2}\\theta+M)}\n$$\n因为\n$$\n0<\\theta<\\dfrac{\\pi}{2}\n$$\n所以\n$$\n\\left(\\dfrac{M}{M+m}\\right)^{2}<\\dfrac{\\Delta E}{W}<1 \\quad \\text{⑪}\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】1) Let the horizontal and vertical velocity components of the frog relative to the ground be $v_x$ and $v_y$, and the recoil velocity of the pad be $v$. The work done by the frog during the jump is:\n$$\nW=\\dfrac{1}{2}Mv^{2}+\\dfrac{1}{2}m(v_{x}^{2}+v_{y}^{2}) \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nBy conservation of horizontal momentum:\n$$\nmv_{x}=Mv \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nIn the pad's frame, the relative horizontal velocity is $v'_{x}=v_{x}+v$. To jump off the pad, the relative horizontal displacement must satisfy $x'\\geqslant R$. The time of flight is $t=\\dfrac{2v_{y}}{g}$, so:\n$$\nx'=(v_{x}+v)t=\\dfrac{2v_{y}}{g}(v_{x}+v)\\geqslant R\n$$\n$$\nv_{y}\\geqslant\\dfrac{gR}{2(v_{x}+v)}=\\dfrac{MgR}{2v_{x}(M+m)} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nCombining ①–③:\n$$\nW\\geqslant\\dfrac{m(M+m)}{2M}v_{x}^{2}+\\dfrac{nmM^{2}g^{2}R^{2}}{8(M+m)^{2}v_{x}^{2}} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\nUsing $A+B\\geqslant2\\sqrt{AB}$:\n$$\nW\\geqslant2\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m(M+m)}{2M}v_{x}^{2}\\cdot\\dfrac{nmM^{2}g^{2}R^{2}}{8(M+m)^{2}v_{x}^{2}}}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m^{2}M}{M+m}}gR\n$$\nThe minimum work to jump off is:\n$$\nW_{\\min}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m^{2}M}{M+m}}gR\n$$\n\n2) Let the frog's takeoff speed be $v_0$ at an angle $\\theta$ to the horizontal. The range to the adjacent pad is $2R$, so:\n$$\n2R=\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}\\sin2\\theta}{g} \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad v_{0}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2gR}{\\sin2\\theta}} \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\nBy horizontal momentum conservation at takeoff:\n$$\nMv=mv_{0}\\cos\\theta \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad v=\\dfrac{m}{M}v_{0}\\cos\\theta \\quad \\text{⑦}\n$$\nAt landing, conservation of momentum gives the common velocity $V$:\n$$\nmv_{0}\\cos\\theta=(M+m)V \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad V=\\dfrac{m}{M+m}v_{0}\\cos\\theta \\quad \\text{⑧}\n$$\nThe work done by the frog is:\n$$\nW=\\dfrac{1}{2}Mv^{2}+\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{0}^{2}=\\dfrac{mv_{0}^{2}}{2M^{2}}(m\\cos^{2}\\theta+M) \\quad \\text{⑨}\n$$\nThe mechanical energy loss is:\n$$\n\\Delta E=W-\\dfrac{1}{2}Mv^{2}-\\dfrac{1}{2}(M+m)V^{2}\n$$\nSubstituting ⑦–⑨:\n$$\n\\Delta E=\\dfrac{mv_{0}^{2}}{2(M+m)}(m\\sin^{2}\\theta+M)\n$$\nThe ratio is:\n$$\n\\dfrac{\\Delta E}{W}=\\dfrac{M(m\\sin^{2}\\theta+M)}{(M+m)(m\\cos^{2}\\theta+M)}\n$$\nSince $0<\\theta<\\dfrac{\\pi}{2}$:\n$$\n\\left(\\dfrac{M}{M+m}\\right)^{2}<\\dfrac{\\Delta E}{W}<1 \\quad \\text{⑪}\n$$", 
"img_cn": [], 
"img_en": [], 
"problem_answer": "1) 青蛙至少应做的功为 $W_{\\min}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m^{2}M}{M+m}}gR$。\n\n2) 机械能损失与青蛙所做功的比值为 $\\dfrac{\\Delta E}{W}=\\dfrac{M(m\\sin^{2}\\theta+M)}{(M+m)(m\\cos^{2}\\theta+M)}$，满足 $\\left(\\dfrac{M}{M+m}\\right)^{2}<\\dfrac{\\Delta E}{W}<1$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 4 }

{ "problem_id": "86", 
"problem_text_cn": "如图86_1所示，长为$l$的轻质悬线，下端系一质量为$M$的砂袋，初始静止。一颗质量为$m$的子弹以速度$v_0$水平射向砂袋。子弹射入砂袋后一起绕绳上端悬挂点摆动，求最大摆动角$\\theta_0$。", "problem_text_en": "As shown in Figure 86_1, a light suspension string of length $l$ has a sandbag of mass $M$ attached to its lower end, initially stationary. A bullet of mass $m$ is fired horizontally at the sandbag with speed $v_0$. After the bullet embeds in the sandbag, they swing together around the upper suspension point. Find the maximum swing angle $\\theta_0$.", 
"problem_img": ["861.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】这里不用通常解法，而采用柯尼希定理对二质点系统的应用做个练习。\n\n系统包括$m$和$M$两质点，系统总动能为\n$$\nE_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{0}^{2} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n质心系中系统动能为\n$$\nE'_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_{0}^{2} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n式②中$v_0$被看作两质点相对速度，$\\mu$为折合质量。系统质心动能为\n$$\nE_{kc}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{0}^{2}-\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_{0}^{2}=\\dfrac{m^{2}}{2(M+m)}v_{0}^{2} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n此处已利用$\\mu=\\dfrac{Mm}{M+m}$。根据题意，子弹射入砂袋，损耗了$E'_{k}$，只剩$E_{kc}$。利用机械能守恒，写出最大摆动角$\\theta_0$满足的关系式\n$$\nE_{kc}=(M+m)gl(1-\\cos\\theta_{0})\n$$\n解得\n$$\n\\cos\\theta_{0}=1-\\dfrac{m^{2}v_{0}^{2}}{2(M+m)gl}\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】Instead of the usual method, we use König's theorem for the two-particle system.\n\nThe total kinetic energy of the system (bullet + sandbag) is:\n$$\nE_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{0}^{2} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nThe kinetic energy in the center-of-mass frame is:\n$$\nE'_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_{0}^{2} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nwhere $v_0$ is the relative velocity and $\\mu$ is the reduced mass. The kinetic energy of the center of mass is:\n$$\nE_{kc}=E_{k}-E'_{k}=\\dfrac{m^{2}}{2(M+m)}v_{0}^{2} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nusing $\\mu=\\dfrac{Mm}{M+m}$. The bullet embeds in the sandbag, losing $E'_{k}$ and retaining $E_{kc}$. By conservation of mechanical energy:\n$$\nE_{kc}=(M+m)gl(1-\\cos\\theta_{0})\n$$\nSolving for $\\theta_0$:\n$$\n\\cos\\theta_{0}=1-\\dfrac{m^{2}v_{0}^{2}}{2(M+m)gl}\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["长为$l$的轻质悬线下端系质量为$M$的砂袋，质量为$m$的子弹以速度$v_0$水平射入砂袋后一起摆动。"], 
"img_en": ["A light suspension string of length $l$ with a sandbag of mass $M$ at its lower end, a bullet of mass $m$ is fired horizontally into the sandbag with speed $v_0$, and they swing together."], 
"problem_answer": "最大摆动角满足 $\\cos\\theta_{0}=1-\\dfrac{m^{2}v_{0}^{2}}{2(M+m)gl}$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "87", 
"problem_text_cn": "如图87_1所示，在光滑的水平桌面上，质量为$M$的框架内有一弹簧，一端被固定，弹性系数为$k$。质量为$m$的小物体，以速度$v_0$射向弹簧的自由端，压缩弹簧。求：弹簧的最大压缩量为多少？", "problem_text_en": "As shown in Figure 87_1, on a smooth horizontal tabletop, a spring with spring constant $k$ is fixed inside a frame of mass $M$. A small object of mass $m$ shoots toward the free end of the spring with speed $v_0$, compressing it. Find the maximum compression of the spring.", 
"problem_img": ["87_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】这里仍作为柯尼希定理对二体系统的应用，做个练习。\n\n系统是一个包括$M$和$m$的二体系统。质心系中系统的动能为\n$$\nE'_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_{0}^{2}=\\dfrac{Mm}{2(M+m)}v_{0}^{2}\n$$\n当小物体压缩弹簧达最大压缩量$\\Delta x$时，$E'_{k}$全部转变成弹性势能。所以\n$$\nE'_{p}=\\dfrac{1}{2}k(\\Delta x)^{2}\n$$\n联立得到弹簧的最大压缩量为\n$$\n\\Delta x=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{Mm}{k(M+m)}}v_{0}\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】This is an exercise in applying König's theorem to a two-body system.\n\nThe system consists of $M$ and $m$. The kinetic energy in the center-of-mass frame is:\n$$\nE'_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_{0}^{2}=\\dfrac{Mm}{2(M+m)}v_{0}^{2}\n$$\nWhen the spring is compressed to its maximum $\\Delta x$, $E'_{k}$ is entirely converted into elastic potential energy:\n$$\nE'_{p}=\\dfrac{1}{2}k(\\Delta x)^{2}\n$$\nSolving for $\\Delta x$:\n$$\n\\Delta x=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{Mm}{k(M+m)}}v_{0}\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["光滑水平桌面上，质量为$M$的框架内有一弹簧，质量为$m$的小物体以速度$v_0$射向弹簧自由端。"], 
"img_en": ["On a smooth horizontal tabletop, a spring inside a frame of mass $M$ is compressed by a small object of mass $m$ moving with speed $v_0$."], 
"problem_answer": "弹簧的最大压缩量为 $\\Delta x = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{Mm}{k(M+m)}}v_{0}$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 2 }

{ "problem_id": "88", 
"problem_text_cn": "光滑水平面上有一质量为$M$的小车，车里有一平台，平台上有一质量为$m$的光滑小球，一根轻质弹簧一端固定在车后壁上，弹簧被压缩并用线捆住，小球与弹簧自由端接触，如图88_1所示。若小车固定，烧断线后，小球弹出，飞出的水平距离$OA=S_1$。若小车不固定，同样条件下烧断线后，小球弹出后在车内飞出的水平距离$S_2$为多大？", "problem_text_en": "On a smooth horizontal surface, there is a cart of mass $M$ with a platform holding a smooth ball of mass $m$. A light spring is fixed to the rear wall of the cart, compressed and tied with a thread, with the ball touching the free end of the spring, as shown in Figure 88_1. If the cart is fixed, burning the thread ejects the ball, which travels a horizontal distance $OA=S_1$. If the cart is not fixed, find the horizontal distance $S_2$ the ball travels inside the cart when the thread is burned under the same conditions.", 
"problem_img": ["88_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】此题不难求解。在此利用二质点系统质心系中的动能定理，解法更显简洁。\n\n小车固定时，对小球施以动能定理，得\n$$\n\\text{弹力做功}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{1}^{2} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n其中$v_1$为小球离开弹簧瞬时（即弹簧自然长度）小球的速度大小。\n\n当小车不固定时，在质心系中系统的动能定理有关系\n$$\n\\text{弹力做功}=\\text{质心系中动能的增量}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_{\\text{相}}^{2}=\\dfrac{Mm}{2(M+m)}v_{\\text{相}}^{2} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n其中$v_{\\text{相}}$为小球离开弹簧时小球相对小车的相对速度大小，$\\mu$为折合质量，$\\mu=\\dfrac{Mm}{M+m}$。\n\n联立式①和②，得\n$$\nv_{1}^{2}=\\dfrac{M}{M+m}v_{\\text{相}}^{2}\n$$\n又由于小球下落高度相同，平抛时间相同，所以\n$$\n\\dfrac{S_{2}}{S_{1}}=\\dfrac{v_{\\text{相}}}{v_{1}}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{M+m}{M}}\n$$\n即，在小车不固定条件下，小球在车内飞出的水平距离\n$$\nS_{2}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{M+m}{M}}S_{1}\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】This problem can be solved concisely using the kinetic theorem in the center-of-mass frame of the two-particle system.\n\nWhen the cart is fixed, applying the work-energy theorem to the ball:\n$$\n\\text{Work done by spring}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{1}^{2} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nwhere $v_1$ is the speed of the ball when it leaves the spring.\n\nWhen the cart is free to move, the work-energy theorem in the center-of-mass frame gives:\n$$\n\\text{Work done by spring}=\\text{Kinetic energy in CM frame}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_{\\text{rel}}^{2}=\\dfrac{Mm}{2(M+m)}v_{\\text{rel}}^{2} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nwhere $v_{\\text{rel}}$ is the relative speed of the ball with respect to the cart, and $\\mu=\\dfrac{Mm}{M+m}$ is the reduced mass.\n\nEquating ① and ②:\n$$\nv_{1}^{2}=\\dfrac{M}{M+m}v_{\\text{rel}}^{2}\n$$\nSince the time of flight is the same (same drop height),\n$$\n\\dfrac{S_{2}}{S_{1}}=\\dfrac{v_{\\text{rel}}}{v_{1}}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{M+m}{M}}\n$$\nThus, the horizontal distance when the cart is free is:\n$$\nS_{2}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{M+m}{M}}S_{1}\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["光滑水平面上质量为$M$的小车，车内平台上质量为$m$的小球与被压缩的弹簧接触，烧断线后小球弹出。"], 
"img_en": ["On a smooth horizontal surface, a cart of mass $M$ contains a ball of mass $m$ touching a compressed spring; burning the thread ejects the ball."], 
"problem_answer": "小球在车内飞出的水平距离为 $S_{2} = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{M+m}{M}}S_{1}$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "89", 
"problem_text_cn": "两个具有相同能量和相同质量的粒子1和2作如图89_1中所示的碰撞。在某个以速度$V$运动的参照系（质心系）看，这两粒子将作对心正碰撞。\n\n1) 求质心系的速度$V$；\n\n2) 将碰撞前质心系中的总动能和原参照系中的总动能作比较，将结果用速度$u$和碰撞角$\\theta$表示出来。", "problem_text_en": "Two particles 1 and 2 with identical mass and energy collide as shown in Figure 89_1. In a reference frame moving with velocity $V$ (the center-of-mass frame), the particles undergo a head-on collision.\n\n1) Find the velocity $V$ of the center-of-mass frame.\n\n2) Compare the total kinetic energy in the center-of-mass frame before collision with that in the original frame, expressing the result in terms of speed $u$ and collision angle $\\theta$.", 
"problem_img": ["89_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】1) 粒子1和2的速度在图中坐标下矢量表出：\n$$\n\\boldsymbol{u}_{1}=u\\boldsymbol{i}\n$$\n$$\n\\boldsymbol{u}_{2}=-u\\cos\\theta\\boldsymbol{i}-u\\sin\\theta\\boldsymbol{j}\n$$\n利用质心定义，写出质心速度$\\boldsymbol{V}$的矢量表示\n$$\n\\boldsymbol{V}=\\dfrac{m_{1}\\boldsymbol{u}_{1}+m_{2}\\boldsymbol{u}_{2}}{m_{1}+m_{2}}\n$$\n利用$m_1=m_2$，改写为\n$$\n\\boldsymbol{V}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\boldsymbol{u}_{1}+\\dfrac{1}{2}\\boldsymbol{u}_{2}=\\dfrac{1}{2}u\\boldsymbol{i}-\\dfrac{1}{2}u\\cos\\theta\\boldsymbol{i}-\\dfrac{1}{2}u\\sin\\theta\\boldsymbol{j}=\\dfrac{1}{2}u(1-\\cos\\theta)\\boldsymbol{i}-\\dfrac{1}{2}u\\sin\\theta\\boldsymbol{j}\n$$\n其大小为\n$$\nV=\\dfrac{1}{2}u\\sqrt{(1-\\cos\\theta)^{2}+\\sin^{2}\\theta}=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}u\\sqrt{1-\\cos\\theta}\n$$\n\n2) 质心系中二体系统的动能可以用相对运动动能给出。设两粒子相对速度为$v$，利用余弦定理得：\n$$\nv^{2}=u^{2}+u^{2}+2u\\cdot u\\cos\\theta=2u^{2}(1+\\cos\\theta)\n$$\n质心系中二体系统的总动能为\n$$\nE'_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v^{2}=\\dfrac{1}{4}mv^{2}\n$$\n这里已利用折合质量$\\mu=\\dfrac{mm}{m+m}=\\dfrac{1}{2}m$。再把$v^{2}$代入，得\n$$\nE'_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mu^{2}(1+\\cos\\theta)=\\dfrac{1}{2}(1+\\cos\\theta)E_{k}\n$$\n其中已利用原参照系中总动能表达式\n$$\nE_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mu^{2}+\\dfrac{1}{2}mu^{2}=mu^{2}\n$$\n当$\\theta=0$时，系统总动能全部为资用能（质心系中动能）。", "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】1) The velocities of particles 1 and 2 in the coordinate system are:\n$$\n\\boldsymbol{u}_{1}=u\\boldsymbol{i}\n$$\n$$\n\\boldsymbol{u}_{2}=-u\\cos\\theta\\boldsymbol{i}-u\\sin\\theta\\boldsymbol{j}\n$$\nThe center-of-mass velocity $\\boldsymbol{V}$ is:\n$$\n\\boldsymbol{V}=\\dfrac{m_{1}\\boldsymbol{u}_{1}+m_{2}\\boldsymbol{u}_{2}}{m_{1}+m_{2}}\n$$\nWith $m_1=m_2$, this simplifies to:\n$$\n\\boldsymbol{V}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\boldsymbol{u}_{1}+\\dfrac{1}{2}\\boldsymbol{u}_{2}=\\dfrac{1}{2}u(1-\\cos\\theta)\\boldsymbol{i}-\\dfrac{1}{2}u\\sin\\theta\\boldsymbol{j}\n$$\nThe magnitude is:\n$$\nV=\\dfrac{1}{2}u\\sqrt{(1-\\cos\\theta)^{2}+\\sin^{2}\\theta}=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}u\\sqrt{1-\\cos\\theta}\n$$\n\n2) The kinetic energy in the CM frame is given by the relative motion. Using the law of cosines for the relative speed $v$:\n$$\nv^{2}=u^{2}+u^{2}+2u^{2}\\cos\\theta=2u^{2}(1+\\cos\\theta)\n$$\nThe total kinetic energy in the CM frame is:\n$$\nE'_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v^{2}=\\dfrac{1}{4}mv^{2}\n$$\nwhere $\\mu=\\dfrac{m}{2}$ is the reduced mass. Substituting $v^{2}$:\n$$\nE'_{k}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mu^{2}(1+\\cos\\theta)=\\dfrac{1}{2}(1+\\cos\\theta)E_{k}\n$$\nwhere $E_{k}=mu^{2}$ is the total kinetic energy in the original frame. When $\\theta=0$, all kinetic energy is available (CM frame kinetic energy).", "img_cn": ["两个质量和能量相同的粒子以速度$u$和角度$\\theta$发生碰撞，质心系中为对心正碰撞。"], "img_en": ["Two particles of identical mass and energy collide with speed $u$ and angle $\\theta$, resulting in a head-on collision in the CM frame."], 
"problem_answer": "1) 质心系的速度大小为 $V = \\dfrac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}u\\sqrt{1-\\cos\\theta}$。\n\n2) 质心系总动能与原参照系总动能的关系为 $E'_{k} = \\dfrac{1}{2}(1+\\cos\\theta)E_{k}$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "90", 
"problem_text_cn": "质点的势函数$V(r)$即单位质量的质点在空间位置$r$处所具有的势能。今有一质量为$m$的质点，在一维直线势场$V(x)=A|x|$的作用下，在直线$x$上运动，$A$为大于零的常量。已知质点的能量为$E$，求质点运动周期。", "problem_text_en": "The potential function $V(r)$ is the potential energy per unit mass of a particle at position $r$. A particle of mass $m$ moves along the $x$-axis under a one-dimensional linear potential $V(x)=A|x|$, where $A>0$. Given the particle's energy is $E$, find its period of motion.", "problem_img": ["90_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解一】先画出$V(r)$在$V-x$坐标中的曲线，如图90_1。在质点能量为$E$的条件下，质点只能在$-x_0$到$x_0$之间运动。当$x=x_0$时，$E=mV(x_0)$，质点只有势能，速度为零；当$x=0$时，质点势能为零，动能达最大值；一般情况下，\n$$\nE=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^{2}+mV(x)=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^{2}+mA|x| \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n解得速度为\n$$\nv=\\pm\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2}{m}(E-mA|x|)}=\\pm\\dfrac{\\Delta x}{\\Delta t} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n由于势场的对称性，质点将在$-x_0$和$x_0$之间往复运动。为计算质点运动周期，可计算$x=0$到$x=x_0$的四分之一周期，在这一段中$x,v>0$。所以\n$$\n\\Delta t=\\dfrac{\\Delta x}{\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2}{m}(E-mAx)}} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n$$\nT=4\\int_{0}^{x_0}\\Delta t=4\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m}{2}}\\int_{0}^{x_0}\\dfrac{\\Delta x}{\\sqrt{E-mAx}} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n令\n$$\ny=\\sqrt{E-mAx}\n$$\n$$\ny^{2}=E-mAx\n$$\n当$x\\to x+\\Delta x$时，有$y\\to y+\\Delta y$，上式变为\n$$\n(y+\\Delta y)^{2}=E-mA(x+\\Delta x)\n$$\n联立并略去高级小量$(\\Delta y)^{2}$，得\n$$\n\\Delta x=-\\dfrac{2y}{mA}\\Delta y\n$$\n代入式④，得到\n$$\nT=4\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m}{2}}\\left(-\\dfrac{2}{mA}\\right)\\int_{\\sqrt{E}}^{0}\\Delta y\\sqrt{E-mAx}=\\dfrac{8}{mA}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m}{2}}(\\sqrt{E}-\\sqrt{E-mAx_0})\n$$\n利用$x=x_0$时，$E=mV(x_0)=mA x_0$，代入式⑤，得质点运动周期\n$$\nT=\\dfrac{4}{A}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2E}{m}} \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\n\n【分析与解二】考察质点从$x=0$到$x=x_0$的四分之一周期内的运动。设运动中质点受力为$F(x)$，当质点从$x\\to x+\\Delta x$（设$\\Delta x$为小量）时，因$\\Delta x$很小，$F(x)$可近似认为不变。$F(x)$做的元功为\n$$\n\\Delta A=F(x)\\Delta x\n$$\n有势力做的功等于势能的减小：\n$$\n\\Delta A=mV(x)-mV(x+\\Delta x)=-m\\Delta V\n$$\n所以\n$$\nF(x)=-\\dfrac{m\\Delta V}{\\Delta x}=-\\dfrac{m\\Delta(Ax)}{\\Delta x}=-mA\n$$\n此力是一常力。负号表示指向平衡点$o$。在此常力作用下，质点自$o$点处的最大速度匀减速到$x_0$静止，经历的时间为\n$$\nt=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2x_0}{a}}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2x_0}{A}}\n$$\n再利用$E=mV(x_0)=mA x_0$，$t$改写为\n$$\nt=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2E}{mA^{2}}}\n$$\n最后得质点运动周期\n$$\nT=4t=\\dfrac{4}{A}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2E}{m}}\n$$\n此结论就是式⑥。", "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution 1】Plot the potential $V(x)=A|x|$ in the $V-x$ plane. For energy $E$, the particle moves between $-x_0$ and $x_0$, where $E=mA x_0$. The energy equation is:\n$$\nE=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^{2}+mA|x| \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nSolving for velocity:\n$$\nv=\\pm\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2}{m}(E-mA|x|)} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nBy symmetry, we compute the quarter-period from $x=0$ to $x=x_0$:\n$$\n\\Delta t=\\dfrac{\\Delta x}{\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2}{m}(E-mAx)}} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n$$\nT=4\\int_{0}^{x_0}\\dfrac{dx}{\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2}{m}(E-mAx)}} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\nSubstitute $y=\\sqrt{E-mAx}$:\n$$\n\\Delta x=-\\dfrac{2y}{mA}\\Delta y\n$$\n$$\nT=4\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m}{2}}\\left(-\\dfrac{2}{mA}\\right)\\int_{\\sqrt{E}}^{0}y\\,dy=\\dfrac{8}{mA}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{m}{2}}\\sqrt{E}\n$$\nUsing $E=mA x_0$:\n$$\nT=\\dfrac{4}{A}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2E}{m}} \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\n\n【Analysis and Solution 2】The force is $F(x)=-mA$ (constant). The time to decelerate from maximum speed at $x=0$ to rest at $x=x_0$ is:\n$$\nt=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2x_0}{A}}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2E}{mA^{2}}}\n$$\nThe period is:\n$$\nT=4t=\\dfrac{4}{A}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2E}{m}}\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["一维线性势场$V(x)=A|x|$的势能曲线，质点在$-x_0$到$x_0$间往复运动。"], 
"img_en": ["Potential energy curve for the linear potential $V(x)=A|x|$, showing the particle oscillating between $-x_0$ and $x_0$."], 
"problem_answer": "质点运动周期为 $T = \\dfrac{4}{A}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2E}{m}}$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "91", 
"problem_text_cn": "如图91_1所示，单摆上的摆锤拉至水平位置，静止释放，当摆锤获得的竖直方向分速度达到最大值时，求摆锤此时的位置$\\theta$。", "problem_text_en": "As shown in Figure 91_1, the bob of a simple pendulum is pulled to the horizontal position and released from rest. Find the angle $\\theta$ of the pendulum when the vertical component of the bob's velocity is maximized.", 
"problem_img": ["91_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】设此摆的摆长为$l$，摆锤质量为$m$。摆在运动中，摆锤的速率满足\n$$\nmgl\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^{2} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n绳中张力$T$满足：\n$$\nT-mg\\sin\\theta=m\\dfrac{v^{2}}{l} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n当摆锤在水平位置静止释放后，开始阶段，随$\\theta$的增加，摆锤在竖直向下的速度随之增加，这是因为，此阶段竖直方向合力向下。当竖直方向速度分量达最大时，竖直方向合力为零，竖直向下速度不再增加，达最大。此时满足关系\n$$\nT\\sin\\theta=mg \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n联立方程①、②和③，解得\n$$\n\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}\n$$\n$$\n\\theta=\\arcsin\\left(\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}\\right)\n$$", "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】Let the pendulum length be $l$ and mass $m$. The speed of the bob satisfies:\n$$\nmgl\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^{2} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nThe tension $T$ in the string is:\n$$\nT-mg\\sin\\theta=m\\dfrac{v^{2}}{l} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nThe vertical velocity component is maximized when the net vertical force is zero:\n$$\nT\\sin\\theta=mg \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nSolving ①–③:\n$$\n\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}\n$$\n$$\n\\theta=\\arcsin\\left(\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}\\right)\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["单摆摆锤从水平位置静止释放，摆长为$l$，求竖直分速度最大时的摆角$\\theta$。"], 
"img_en": ["A pendulum bob of length $l$ is released from rest in the horizontal position; find the angle $\\theta$ when the vertical velocity component is maximized."], 
"problem_answer": "摆锤竖直分速度最大时的位置为 $\\theta = \\arcsin\\left(\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}\\right)$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 2 }

{ "problem_id": "92", 
"problem_text_cn": "一人站在水平地面上，手握细绳一端，另一端拴一石块，并使其以手为中心在竖直面内作圆周运动。问：当石块在什么位置时，地面对人的弹力最小？设绳长为$l$。
", "problem_text_en": "A person stands on a horizontal ground, holding one end of a string with a stone attached to the other end, swinging it in a vertical circle around their hand. At what position of the stone is the normal force exerted by the ground on the person minimized? Let the string length be $l$.", "problem_img": ["92_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】设石块在最高点的速率为$v_0$，为完成竖直面内的圆周运动，$v_0$必须满足关系\n$$\n\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{l}\\geqslant g\n$$\n即\n$$\nv_{0}\\geqslant\\sqrt{gl} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n在此条件下，石块在竖直面内作圆周运动过程中，通过绳中张力与人手相互作用。当张力作用在人手上的作用力在竖直向上方向的分力最大时，地面对人的弹力最小。设此时绳与竖直方向的夹角为$\\theta$，如图92_1所示，石块速度为$v$，绳中张力为$T$。写出石块运动满足的能量关系和法向动力学方程：\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^{2}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{0}^{2}+mgl(1-\\cos\\theta) \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n$$\nT+mg\\cos\\theta=m\\dfrac{v^{2}}{l} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n联立式②和③，写出绳中张力在竖直向上方向的分量（此分力即为绳作用在人手上作用力在竖直向上分力的大小）：\n$$\nT_{1}=T\\cos\\theta\n$$\n$$\n=\\left(m\\dfrac{v^{2}}{l}-mg\\cos\\theta\\right)\\cos\\theta\n$$\n$$\n=\\left[\\dfrac{mv_{0}^{2}+2mgl(1-\\cos\\theta)}{l}-mg\\cos\\theta\\right]\\cos\\theta\n$$\n$$\n=-3mg\\cos^{2}\\theta+\\left(\\dfrac{mv_{0}^{2}}{l}+2mg\\right)\\cos\\theta\n$$\n$$\n=-3mg\\left[\\cos\\theta-\\left(\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{6gl}+\\dfrac{1}{3}\\right)\\right]^{2}+\\dfrac{3}{4}mg\\left(\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{3gl}+\\dfrac{2}{3}\\right)^{2} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n由此可得\n\n（ⅰ）若$\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{6gl}+\\dfrac{1}{3}<1$，即$v_0<2\\sqrt{gl}$，$T_1$达最大，$\\theta$满足\n$$\n\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{6gl}+\\dfrac{1}{3}\n$$\n若结合式①，$v_0$应有如下关系\n$$\n\\sqrt{gl}\\leqslant v_0<2\\sqrt{gl}\n$$\n\n（ⅱ）若$\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{6gl}+\\dfrac{1}{3}\\geqslant1$，即$v_0\\geqslant2\\sqrt{gl}$，$T_1$达最大，$\\theta$满足\n$$\n\\cos\\theta=1, \\quad \\theta=0\n$$\n\n当$T_1$达最大时，也就是地面对人的弹力最小。", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】Let the speed at the highest point be $v_0$. To complete the vertical circle:\n$$\n\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{l}\\geqslant g \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad v_0\\geqslant\\sqrt{gl} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nThe normal force on the person is minimized when the upward vertical component of the string tension on the hand is maximized. Let $\\theta$ be the angle between the string and the vertical, $v$ the speed of the stone, and $T$ the tension. The energy and radial force equations are:\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^{2}=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{0}^{2}+mgl(1-\\cos\\theta) \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n$$\nT+mg\\cos\\theta=m\\dfrac{v^{2}}{l} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nThe upward tension component is:\n$$\nT_{1}=T\\cos\\theta=\\left(m\\dfrac{v^{2}}{l}-mg\\cos\\theta\\right)\\cos\\theta\n$$\n$$\n=-3mg\\cos^{2}\\theta+\\left(\\dfrac{mv_{0}^{2}}{l}+2mg\\right)\\cos\\theta\n$$\n$$\n=-3mg\\left[\\cos\\theta-\\left(\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{6gl}+\\dfrac{1}{3}\\right)\\right]^{2}+\\dfrac{3}{4}mg\\left(\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{3gl}+\\dfrac{2}{3}\\right)^{2} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n\n(i) If $\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{6gl}+\\dfrac{1}{3}<1$ ($v_0<2\\sqrt{gl}$), $T_1$ is maximized when:\n$$\n\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{6gl}+\\dfrac{1}{3}\n$$\nwith $\\sqrt{gl}\\leqslant v_0<2\\sqrt{gl}$.\n\n(ii) If $\\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{6gl}+\\dfrac{1}{3}\\geqslant1$ ($v_0\\geqslant2\\sqrt{gl}$), $T_1$ is maximized when:\n$$\n\\cos\\theta=1 \\quad (\\theta=0)\n$$\n\nThe ground normal force is minimized when $T_1$ is maximized.", 
"img_cn": ["人在水平地面手握细绳，石块在竖直面内作圆周运动，绳长为$l$。"], 
"img_en": ["A person holds a string of length $l$ on horizontal ground, swinging a stone in a vertical circle."], 
"problem_answer": "当 $\\sqrt{gl}\\leqslant v_0<2\\sqrt{gl}$ 时，地面对人的弹力最小的位置满足 $\\cos\\theta = \\dfrac{v_{0}^{2}}{6gl}+\\dfrac{1}{3}$；当 $v_0\\geqslant2\\sqrt{gl}$ 时，在 $\\theta=0$（最低点）处弹力最小。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "93", 
"problem_text_cn": "质量分别为$m_1$和$m_2$的两个重物系于不可伸长的细绳两端（$m_1>m_2$），绳子绕过一个半径为$r$的滑轮，如图93_1所示。在滑轮的轴上固定了四个长为$L$、分布均匀的细辐条，辐条端点各固定有质量为$m$的小球。质量为$m_1$和$m_2$的重物由于本身的重量作匀加速运动。求$m_1$和$m_2$的运动加速度。设轴的摩擦力、细辐条及滑轮质量均忽略不计，四个小球线速度很小，细绳与滑轮间不发生滑动。", "problem_text_en": "Two masses $m_1$ and $m_2$ ($m_1>m_2$) are attached to the ends of an inextensible string passing over a pulley of radius $r$, as shown in Figure 93_1. Four uniform spokes of length $L$ are fixed to the pulley's axle, each with a mass $m$ at its end. The masses $m_1$ and $m_2$ accelerate due to gravity. Find the acceleration of $m_1$ and $m_2$. Neglect axle friction, the mass of the spokes and pulley, and assume the balls have small linear speed and no slipping between the string and pulley.", 
"problem_img": ["93_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】系统在运动中，只有重力做功，机械能守恒。因四根辐条分布均匀，当$m_1$和$m_2$两重物运动时带动四个质量均为$m$的小球作为整体的重心势能保持不变。因此，在考虑机械能守恒时，无须计入四小球的重力势能。\n\n设初始时，系统保持静止，$m_1$和$m_2$处在初始位置，释放$m_1$和$m_2$，系统开始运动。设经一段时间后，$m_1$下降高度$h$。与此同时，$m_2$上升高度$h$，$m_1$和$m_2$的速率为$v$，四小球的速率为$v'$，则根据机械能守恒定律，有关系式\n$$\n(m_1-m_2)gh=\\dfrac{1}{2}(m_1+m_2)v^{2}+\\dfrac{1}{2}(4m)v'^{2} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n由于四根辐条固定在滑轮转轴上，所以有关系\n$$\nv=\\omega r \\quad v'=\\omega L \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n其中$\\omega$为滑轮及其辐条的共同角速度。再利用匀加速运动公式\n$$\nh=\\dfrac{v^{2}}{2a} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n联立以上三式，解得$m_1$和$m_2$的加速度\n$$\na=\\dfrac{(m_1-m_2)g}{m_1+m_2+\\dfrac{4mL^{2}}{r^{2}}} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n\n【讨论】有人提出质疑，在写出式③时，实际上已判定$m_1$和$m_2$的运动是匀加速运动，妥当否？严格地说，利用式③确实欠严密。规范的求解方法可以用动力学方程求解。这里用另一种方法。\n\n式①两边均作一微小变化，并除以此变化经历的极短时间，即\n$$\n(m_1-m_2)g\\dfrac{\\Delta h}{\\Delta t}=\\dfrac{1}{2}(m_1+m_2)\\dfrac{\\Delta(v^{2})}{\\Delta t}+\\dfrac{1}{2}(4m)\\dfrac{\\Delta(v'^{2})}{\\Delta t} \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n并利用\n$$\n\\dfrac{\\Delta h}{\\Delta t}=v=\\omega r\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{\\Delta(v^{2})}{\\Delta t}=r^{2}\\dfrac{\\Delta(\\omega^{2})}{\\Delta t}=2r^{2}\\omega\\dfrac{\\Delta\\omega}{\\Delta t}\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{\\Delta(v'^{2})}{\\Delta t}=L^{2}\\dfrac{\\Delta(\\omega^{2})}{\\Delta t}=2L^{2}\\omega\\dfrac{\\Delta\\omega}{\\Delta t}\n$$\n代入式⑤，并利用角加速度$\\dfrac{\\Delta\\omega}{\\Delta t}$与线加速度$a$的关系\n$$\na=r\\dfrac{\\Delta\\omega}{\\Delta t}\n$$\n解得\n$$\na=\\dfrac{(m_1-m_2)g}{m_1+m_2+\\dfrac{4mL^{2}}{r^{2}}}\n$$\n与式④相同。", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】Only gravity does work, so mechanical energy is conserved. The center of mass of the four balls remains at the same height, so their potential energy does not change. Let $h$ be the distance $m_1$ falls, $v$ the speed of $m_1$ and $m_2$, and $v'$ the speed of the balls. Energy conservation gives:\n$$\n(m_1-m_2)gh=\\dfrac{1}{2}(m_1+m_2)v^{2}+\\dfrac{1}{2}(4m)v'^{2} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nThe angular velocity $\\omega$ is related to $v$ and $v'$ by:\n$$\nv=\\omega r, \\quad v'=\\omega L \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nUsing the kinematic relation for constant acceleration:\n$$\nh=\\dfrac{v^{2}}{2a} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nSolving ①–③:\n$$\na=\\dfrac{(m_1-m_2)g}{m_1+m_2+\\dfrac{4mL^{2}}{r^{2}}} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n\nA more rigorous derivation using time derivatives confirms this result:\n$$\n(m_1-m_2)g\\dfrac{\\Delta h}{\\Delta t}=\\dfrac{1}{2}(m_1+m_2)\\dfrac{\\Delta(v^{2})}{\\Delta t}+\\dfrac{1}{2}(4m)\\dfrac{\\Delta(v'^{2})}{\\Delta t}\n$$\nUsing $\\dfrac{\\Delta h}{\\Delta t}=v$, $\\dfrac{\\Delta(v^{2})}{\\Delta t}=2va$, and $\\dfrac{\\Delta(v'^{2})}{\\Delta t}=2v'a'$, we find:\n$$\na=\\dfrac{(m_1-m_2)g}{m_1+m_2+\\dfrac{4mL^{2}}{r^{2}}}\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["质量为$m_1$和$m_2$的重物通过滑轮连接，滑轮轴上固定四个带小球的细辐条。"], 
"img_en": ["Masses $m_1$ and $m_2$ are connected by a string over a pulley with four spokes, each carrying a mass $m$ at the end."], 
"problem_answer": "运动加速度为 $a = \\dfrac{(m_1-m_2)g}{m_1+m_2+\\dfrac{4mL^{2}}{r^{2}}}$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "94", 
"problem_text_cn": "如图94_1所示，质量为$M$的滑块可以在光滑水平导轨上无摩擦滑动，长为$l$的轻绳一端系于滑块$M$上，另一端系一质量为$m$的小球。今将轻绳沿水平拉直，使小球与滑块等高，并同时释放。试问，当轻绳与水平导轨夹角为$\\theta$时绳中张力$T$为多大？", 
"problem_text_en": "As shown in Figure 94_1, a slider of mass $M$ slides frictionlessly on a smooth horizontal rail. A light string of length $l$ is attached to the slider at one end and to a ball of mass $m$ at the other. The string is initially horizontal, with the ball at the same height as the slider, and both are released simultaneously. Find the tension $T$ in the string when it makes an angle $\\theta$ with the horizontal rail.", 
"problem_img": ["94_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】因系统在运动过程中不受水平方向外力作用，所以水平方向系统动量守恒。设小球在图中坐标下的水平方向速度为$v_x$，滑块在导轨上的速度大小为$u$，依水平方向动量守恒有关系式\n$$\nmv_x=Mu \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n又因为系统是一个保守系统（只有保守力做功），所以系统机械能守恒，有关系式\n$$\nmgl\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{1}{2}m(v_x^2+v_y^2)+\\dfrac{1}{2}Mu^2 \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n再在滑块参照系中，$v_x$、$v_y$、$u$、$\\theta$有约束关系式\n$$\n\\text{tg}\\theta=\\dfrac{v_y}{v_x+u} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n把$\\theta$作为参量，则式①—③联立，可解出$v_x$、$v_y$、$u$：\n$$\nv_y^2=\\dfrac{2M^2gl\\sin^3\\theta}{(M+m)(m\\cos^2\\theta+M)} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n$$\nu=\\dfrac{M}{M+m}v_x \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n$$\nv_x=\\left(\\dfrac{M+m}{M}\\text{ctg}\\theta\\right)v_y \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\n再利用滑块参照系，求绳中张力。\n设小球相对于滑块的速度为$v'$，其大小为\n$$\nv'^2=(v_x+u)^2+v_y^2=\\left(\\dfrac{M+m}{M}\\right)^2v_y^2+\\left(\\dfrac{M+m}{M}\\text{ctg}\\theta\\right)^2v_y^2=\\dfrac{2(M+m)g\\sin\\theta}{m\\cos^2\\theta+M} \\quad \\text{⑦}\n$$\n设滑块在绳子张力$T$的水平方向分力作用下的加速度为$a$，显然，滑块在导轨参照系中的动力学方程为\n$$\nT\\cos\\theta=Ma \\quad \\text{⑧}\n$$\n在滑块参照系（非惯性系）中，小球的法向动力学方程为\n$$\nT+ma\\cos\\theta-mg\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{mv'^2}{l} \\quad \\text{⑨}\n$$\n联立方程⑦—⑨，消去$a$和$v'$，最后解得绳中张力为\n$$\nT=\\dfrac{mMg\\sin\\theta\\left[3M+m(2+\\cos^2\\theta)\\right]}{(M+m\\cos^2\\theta)^2}\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】The system has no horizontal external forces, so horizontal momentum is conserved. Let $v_x$ be the horizontal velocity of the ball and $u$ the velocity of the slider:\n$$\nmv_x=Mu \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nMechanical energy is conserved:\n$$\nmgl\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{1}{2}m(v_x^2+v_y^2)+\\dfrac{1}{2}Mu^2 \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nIn the slider's frame, the velocity components satisfy:\n$$\n\\tan\\theta=\\dfrac{v_y}{v_x+u} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nSolving ①–③:\n$$\nv_y^2=\\dfrac{2M^2gl\\sin^3\\theta}{(M+m)(m\\cos^2\\theta+M)} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n$$\nu=\\dfrac{M}{M+m}v_x \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n$$\nv_x=\\left(\\dfrac{M+m}{M}\\cot\\theta\\right)v_y \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\nThe relative speed of the ball with respect to the slider is:\n$$\nv'^2=(v_x+u)^2+v_y^2=\\dfrac{2(M+m)g\\sin\\theta}{m\\cos^2\\theta+M} \\quad \\text{⑦}\n$$\nThe slider's acceleration $a$ is:\n$$\nT\\cos\\theta=Ma \\quad \\text{⑧}\n$$\nIn the slider's (non-inertial) frame, the radial force equation for the ball is:\n$$\nT+ma\\cos\\theta-mg\\sin\\theta=\\dfrac{mv'^2}{l} \\quad \\text{⑨}\n$$\nSolving ⑦–⑨ gives:\n$$\nT=\\dfrac{mMg\\sin\\theta\\left[3M+m(2+\\cos^2\\theta)\\right]}{(M+m\\cos^2\\theta)^2}\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["质量为$M$的滑块在光滑水平导轨上，轻绳一端系滑块，另一端系质量为$m$的小球，初始时绳水平拉直。"], 
"img_en": ["A slider of mass $M$ on a smooth horizontal rail, with a light string attaching it to a ball of mass $m$, initially horizontal."], 
"problem_answer": "绳中张力为 $T = \\dfrac{mMg\\sin\\theta\\left[3M+m(2+\\cos^2\\theta)\\right]}{(M+m\\cos^2\\theta)^2}$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 4 }

{ "problem_id": "95", 
"problem_text_cn": "长为$L$的细绳上端固定在天花板上并靠近墙壁的$o$点，下端系一质量为$m$的小球竖直悬挂起来，$A$点是平衡时小球的位置。现保持绳伸直，将小球在平行于墙壁的竖直面内从$A$点拉到绳水平的位置$B$。在$oA$连线方向的墙上点$o_1$固定一细长钉子。问下列两种情况下，到悬点$o$的距离各为多少？\n\n1) 将球释放后，绳被钉挡住，小球绕$o_1$作圆周运动，如图95_1所示。\n\n2) 将球释放后，绳被钉挡住，小球开始绕$o_1$运动，而后小球将击中钉子，如图95_2所示。", 
"problem_text_en": "A string of length $L$ is fixed at the ceiling near a wall at point $o$, with a ball of mass $m$ hanging vertically at equilibrium point $A$. The ball is pulled to the horizontal position $B$ (keeping the string taut) and released. A nail is fixed on the wall at point $o_1$ along the line $oA$. Find the distance from $o$ to $o_1$ in each case:\n\n1) The string catches the nail, and the ball moves in a circular path around $o_1$, as in Figure 95_1.\n\n2) The string catches the nail, the ball starts moving around $o_1$, and then hits the nail, as in Figure 95_2.", 
"problem_img": ["95_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】1) 球自$B$点释放后，绕$o$点运动至$A$点，绳被阻后，再绕钉子所在处$o_1$完成圆周运动，整个过程中机械能守恒。小球刚好能作圆周运动，球达圆顶点$C$时，绳中张力为零。$R_1=o_1A$为球绕$o_1$完成圆周运动的最大半径。\n\n据此，写出小球在$C$点满足的机械能守恒方程和法向动力学方程\n$$\nmg(L-R_1)=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_C^2 \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\nmg=\\dfrac{mv_C^2}{R_1} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n联立解得\n$$\nR_1=\\dfrac{2}{5}L \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n所以钉子$o_1$到悬挂点$o$的距离为\n$$\noo_1=L-R_1=\\dfrac{3}{5}L \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n因此，当$\\overline{oo_1}\\geqslant\\dfrac{3}{5}L$时，小球均可绕$o_1$完成圆周运动。\n\n2) 球自$B$点释放后，绕$o$点运动至$A$点，绳被阻后，再绕钉子所在处$o_1$点运动，当球抵达图95_2中$D$点处绳中张力为零，然后不能完成圆周运动，只能作斜上抛运动，正好击中钉子$o_1$点。\n\n设此种情况下，$R_2=o_1A$。由图95_2中知，$D$点位置用此处圆半径与竖直方向夹角$\\theta$表示。仍然利用小球在$D$点满足的机械能守恒方程和法向动力学方程\n$$\nmg(L-R_2-R_2\\cos\\theta)=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_D^2 \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n$$\nmg\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{mv_D^2}{R_2} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n上述两方程中未知量有三个：$R_2$、$v_D$、$\\theta$，还需寻找新的方程。若把抛出点$D$作为坐标原点，水平向左为$x$坐标，竖直向上为$y$坐标，则钉子坐标为\n$$\nx=R_2\\sin\\theta, \\quad y=-R_2\\cos\\theta\n$$\n小球击中钉子的条件为\n$$\nR_2\\sin\\theta=(v_D\\sin\\theta)t \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n$$\n-R_2\\cos\\theta=(v_D\\cos\\theta)t-\\dfrac{1}{2}gt^2 \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\n这里引进了一个新的参量$t$，但给出了两个方程。联立方程③和④，解得\n$$\n\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{2(L-R_2)}{3R_2} \\quad \\text{⑦}\n$$\n联立方程④、⑤和⑥，得\n$$\n\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{3} \\quad \\text{⑧}\n$$\n联立方程⑦和⑧，解得\n$$\nR_2=2(2-\\sqrt{3})L\n$$\n因此，为使小球击中钉子，要求\n$$\n\\overline{oo_1}=L-R_2=(2\\sqrt{3}-3)L\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】1) The ball is released from $B$, swings to $A$, then moves in a circle around $o_1$. At the top of the circle ($C$), tension is zero. Let $R_1=o_1A$. Energy conservation and radial force at $C$:\n$$\nmg(L-R_1)=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_C^2 \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\nmg=\\dfrac{mv_C^2}{R_1} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nSolving:\n$$\nR_1=\\dfrac{2}{5}L, \\quad \\overline{oo_1}=L-R_1=\\dfrac{3}{5}L\n$$\n\n2) The ball swings to $A$, then around $o_1$ until tension is zero at $D$, then moves in projectile motion to hit $o_1$. Let $R_2=o_1A$. At $D$:\n$$\nmg(L-R_2-R_2\\cos\\theta)=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_D^2 \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n$$\nmg\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{mv_D^2}{R_2} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\nProjectile motion from $D$ to $o_1$:\n$$\nR_2\\sin\\theta=(v_D\\sin\\theta)t \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n$$\n-R_2\\cos\\theta=(v_D\\cos\\theta)t-\\dfrac{1}{2}gt^2 \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\nSolving ③–⑥:\n$$\n\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}, \\quad R_2=2(2-\\sqrt{3})L\n$$\n$$\n\\overline{oo_1}=L-R_2=(2\\sqrt{3}-3)L\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["长为$L$的细绳悬挂小球，墙上$oA$连线上的钉子$o_1$挡住绳子，小球绕$o_1$运动或击中钉子。"], 
"img_en": ["A string of length $L$ with a ball, a nail at $o_1$ on the wall along $oA$, causing the ball to swing around $o_1$ or hit the nail."], 
"problem_answer": "1) 钉子到悬点的距离为 $\\overline{oo_1}=\\dfrac{3}{5}L$（当 $\\overline{oo_1}\\geqslant\\dfrac{3}{5}L$ 时可完成圆周运动）。\n\n2) 钉子到悬点的距离为 $\\overline{oo_1}=(2\\sqrt{3}-3)L$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "96", 
"problem_text_cn": "1) 如图96_1所示，长为$l$的轻杆，一端通过转轴与$o$点相连，另一端系一质量为$m$的质点，将杆从水平位置由静止释放。求杆运动到竖直位置$oA'$时，$A'$处的质点的速度及转轴所受的作用力。\n\n2) 如图96_2所示，将轻杆延长至$2l$长，杆端再系一质量为$m$的质点，两质点分别为$A$和$B$。求杆从水平位置运动到竖直位置，两质点抵达$A'$和$B'$时的速度，杆对两质点分别做多少功？\n\n3) 接2)，若在图96_2中杆在水平位置时，$A$、$B$之间再系一个质量同为$m$的质点$C$（图中未画出），当杆抵达竖直位置时，杆对质点$C$做的功为零，给出$oC$的长度。", 
"problem_text_en": "1) As shown in Figure 96_1, a light rod of length $l$ is pivoted at $o$ and has a mass $m$ at its end. The rod is released from rest in the horizontal position. Find the speed of the mass at the vertical position $oA'$ and the force exerted on the pivot.\n\n2) As shown in Figure 96_1, the rod is extended to length $2l$, with another mass $m$ at the new end, labeled $A$ and $B$. Find the speeds of $A$ and $B$ when the rod reaches the vertical position, and the work done by the rod on each mass.\n\n3) Continuing from 2), if a third mass $m$ (particle $C$) is attached between $A$ and $B$ when the rod is horizontal, find the length $oC$ such that the work done by the rod on $C$ is zero when the rod reaches the vertical position.", 
"problem_img": ["96_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】1) 因为在过程中质点只受重力和杆中拉力作用，而且拉力不做功，所以可利用机械能守恒定律，杆运动到竖直位置时质点速度$v$满足\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^2=mgl\n$$\n解得\n$$\nv=\\sqrt{2gl} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n方向向左。此位置杆中拉力$F$（即转轴受力）满足\n$$\nF-mg=\\dfrac{mv^2}{l}\n$$\n解得\n$$\nF=3mg \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n\n2) 由于两质点同在一根杆上，运动中系统所受各种力，只有重力做功，因此系统机械能守恒，并注意到运动中两质点相对于$o$的转动角速度相等，即\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_A^2+\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_B^2=mgl+mg2l\n$$\n其中$v_A$、$v_B$为杆竖直位置时$A$、$B$质点的速度。联立解得\n$$\nv_A=\\omega l, \\quad v_B=\\omega 2l\n$$\n$$\nv_A=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{6gl}{5}}, \\quad v_B=2\\sqrt{\\dfrac{6gl}{5}} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n若杆上只有一个质点$A$，由1)中得到在竖直位置的速度为\n$$\nv_{A1}=\\sqrt{2gl} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n若杆上只有一个质点$B$，同样可得在竖直位置时的速度\n$$\nv_{B1}=\\sqrt{4gl} \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n这说明，两质点同系于一根杆上后，由于杆的存在，对质点$A$和$B$做的功分别为\n$$\nW_A=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_A^2-\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{A1}^2=-\\dfrac{2}{5}mgl\n$$\n$$\nW_B=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_B^2-\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_{B1}^2=\\dfrac{2}{5}mgl\n$$\n\n【说明】杆对质点$A$或$B$做的功，是杆中垂直于杆的剪切力做的功。此剪切力减缓$A$达$A'$，加快$B$达$B'$。这一对力做功之和为零。同时，还告诉我们，两质点在重力做功下得到的能量，因两质点固连于同一刚性杆上而使得能量有转移，质点$A$得到能量的一部分转移到质点$B$。\n\n3) 若质点$C$在$A$和$B$之间某一点，设$oC=x$，根据2)中分析，如果重力做的功全部转变成动能，既没有增多，也没有减少，那么杆在运动中对$C$做功为零。即如下条件成立\n$$\nv_C=\\sqrt{2gx}\n$$\n又\n$$\nv_C=\\omega x=\\dfrac{v_A}{l}x=\\dfrac{x}{l}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{6gl}{5}}\n$$\n联立解得$oC$的长度$x$的合理解：\n$$\nx=\\dfrac{5}{3}l\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】1) Only gravity does work, so energy is conserved:\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^2=mgl \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad v=\\sqrt{2gl} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nThe pivot force $F$ is:\n$$\nF-mg=\\dfrac{mv^2}{l} \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad F=3mg \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n\n2) The system rotates with angular velocity $\\omega$, so $v_A=\\omega l$, $v_B=\\omega 2l$. Energy conservation:\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_A^2+\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_B^2=3mgl\n$$\n$$\nv_A=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{6gl}{5}}, \\quad v_B=2\\sqrt{\\dfrac{6gl}{5}} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nWork done by the rod:\n$$\nW_A=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_A^2-\\dfrac{1}{2}m(\\sqrt{2gl})^2=-\\dfrac{2}{5}mgl\n$$\n$$\nW_B=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_B^2-\\dfrac{1}{2}m(\\sqrt{4gl})^2=\\dfrac{2}{5}mgl\n$$\n\n3) For work on $C$ to be zero, its speed must be $v_C=\\sqrt{2gx}$. Since $v_C=\\omega x$:\n$$\n\\sqrt{2gx}=\\dfrac{x}{l}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{6gl}{5}} \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad x=\\dfrac{5}{3}l\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["1) 长为$l$的轻杆一端系质点$m$，水平释放后竖直位置的速度和转轴受力。\n\n2) 杆延长至$2l$，两端系质点$A$、$B$，求竖直位置的速度及杆做功。\n\n3) $A$、$B$间系质点$C$，求杆对$C$做功为零时的$oC$长度。"], 
"img_en": ["1) A light rod of length $l$ with mass $m$ at the end, released horizontally; find speed at vertical position and pivot force.\n\n2) Rod extended to $2l$ with masses $A$ and $B$; find speeds and work done by the rod.\n\n3) Mass $C$ between $A$ and $B$; find $oC$ such that work on $C$ is zero."], 
"problem_answer": "1) 质点速度为 $v = \\sqrt{2gl}$，转轴受力为 $F = 3mg$。\n\n2) $v_A = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{6gl}{5}}$，$v_B = 2\\sqrt{\\dfrac{6gl}{5}}$；杆对$A$做功 $W_A = -\\dfrac{2}{5}mgl$，对$B$做功 $W_B = \\dfrac{2}{5}mgl$。\n\n3) $oC$的长度为 $x = \\dfrac{5}{3}l$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "97", 
"problem_text_cn": "如图97_1的(a)、(b)、(c)所示，$PA$、$PA_1$、$PA_2$均为长$l$的刚性轻杆，$P$为固连于杆端的、质量为$m$的小球，$A$、$A_1$、$A_2$是轻杆下端的接触点，接触方式分别为：\n\n$A_1$是一个固定在地面上的光滑转轴，刚性杆可绕$A_1$转动。\n\n$A_2$是一个固定在质量为$M$的木板上的光滑转轴，轻杆可绕$A_2$转动，$M>m$。木板被置于光滑的地面上。\n\n$A_3$是轻杆下端与地面接触点，杆与地面间有足够大的静摩擦力（即静摩擦系数趋于无限大）。\n\n开始时，小球均处在最高点，球或球与板处于静止。放开后，受扰动，$m$倒下。当小球接近地面或接近板时，求小球的速度以及杆中张力。", 
"problem_text_en": "As shown in Figure 97_1的(a), (b), (c), $PA$, $PA_1$, $PA_2$ are rigid light rods of length $l$, with a ball of mass $m$ fixed at $P$. The lower ends $A$, $A_1$, $A_2$ have different contact conditions:\n\n$A_1$ is a smooth pivot fixed to the ground, allowing the rod to rotate about $A_1$.\n\n$A_2$ is a smooth pivot fixed to a wooden board of mass $M$ ($M>m$), which rests on a smooth ground.\n\n$A_3$ is a contact point with the ground, where static friction is infinite (no slipping).\n\nInitially, the ball is at the highest point, at rest. When released, it falls. Find the speed of the ball and the tension in the rod when it is near the ground or the board.", 
"problem_img": ["97_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】对图中三种情况分别讨论。\n\n1) 图97_1中(a)中情形。设小球接近地面时的速度为$v_1$，则依机械能守恒定律$v_1$满足\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_1^2=mgl\n$$\n$$\nv_1=\\sqrt{2gl} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n方向向下。杆中张力$T_1$满足\n$$\nT_1=\\dfrac{mv_1^2}{l}=2mg \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n\n2) 图97_1中(b)中情形。当$m$倒下过程中，板与小球均有水平方向运动，但水平方向系统动量始终为零。当小球接近板时，小球与板均没有水平方向分量。如若不然，由于杆长不变，板与小球的水平方向速度方向一定相同，但这破坏了系统水平方向动量为零的动量守恒规则。但是，板与小球水平方向速度为零并不表示板或小球水平方向加速度为零。此处由于杆的长度不变，所以水平方向（即沿杆方向）的加速度完全是由杆的转动引起。小球与板的加速度方向均指向质心。\n\n小球接近板时的速度$v_2$，可由机械能守恒求得\n$$\nv_2=\\sqrt{2gl} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n方向向下。小球相对于板的加速度为$a_{m-M}$，小球加速度大小为$a_m$，板加速度大小为$a_M$，则\n$$\na_{m-M}=\\dfrac{v_2^2}{l}=2g \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n$$\na_{m-M}=a_m+a_M \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n又设杆中张力为$T_2$，则\n$$\nT_2=Ma_M \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\n$$\nT_2=ma_m \\quad \\text{⑦}\n$$\n联立式④—⑦，解得\n$$\nT_2=\\dfrac{2Mm}{M+m}g \\quad \\text{⑧}\n$$\n还可用等效一体问题（6.5节）求$T_2$。当小球接近板时，$m$相对$M$的动力学方程为\n$$\nT_2=\\dfrac{mv_2^2}{l}=\\dfrac{Mm}{M+m}\\dfrac{2gl}{l}=\\dfrac{2Mm}{M+m}g\n$$\n\n3) 图97_1中(c)中情形。$A_3$点有摩擦存在，由于最大静摩擦力足够大，所以杆下端不会滑动。但是，当杆中张力为零时，摩擦力也随之消失。从此时开始，小球将作斜下抛运动。由于本题要求小球接近地面时的速度以及杆中张力，易知张力$T_3=0$，速度大小由机械能守恒得\n$$\nv_3=\\sqrt{2gl} \\quad \\text{⑨}\n$$\n但是速度$v_3$的方向，必须找出$A_3$处摩擦力消失时杆与竖直方向的夹角$\\theta$，如图97_1中(d)所示。以及此时的速率$v_0$，有关系\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2=mgl(1-\\cos\\theta) \\quad \\text{⑩}\n$$\n$$\nmg\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{mv_0^2}{l} \\quad \\text{⑪}\n$$\n联立解得\n$$\n\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{2}{3}, \\quad v_0=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2gl}{3}} \\quad \\text{⑫}\n$$\n利用斜向下的抛体运动，接近地面时小球的水平方向速度$v_x$和竖直方向的速度$v_y$分别满足\n$$\nv_x=v_0\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{2}{3}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2gl}{3}} \\quad \\text{⑬}\n$$\n$$\nv_y^2-v_0^2=2g\\cdot l\\cos\\theta \\quad \\text{⑭}\n$$\n$$\nv_y=\\sqrt{v_0^2+2gl\\cos\\theta}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2gl}{3}\\cdot\\dfrac{5}{9}+\\dfrac{4}{3}gl}=\\dfrac{2}{3}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{23gl}{3}} \\quad \\text{⑮}\n$$\n设速度与水平方向夹角为$\\varphi$，则\n$$\n\\text{tg}\\varphi=\\dfrac{v_y}{v_x}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{23}{6}}\\cdot\\sqrt{\\dfrac{3}{2}}=\\dfrac{1}{2}\\sqrt{23} \\quad \\text{⑯}\n$$\n$$\nv_3=\\sqrt{v_x^2+v_y^2}=\\sqrt{2gl} \\quad \\text{⑰}\n$$\n与式⑨中$v_3$相同。", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】We analyze each case:\n\n1) Case (a): Energy conservation gives:\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_1^2=mgl \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad v_1=\\sqrt{2gl} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nTension:\n$$\nT_1=\\dfrac{mv_1^2}{l}=2mg \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n\n2) Case (b): Horizontal momentum is zero. Energy conservation:\n$$\nv_2=\\sqrt{2gl} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nRelative acceleration $a_{m-M}=2g$. Since $T_2=Ma_M=ma_m$ and $a_{m-M}=a_m+a_M$:\n$$\nT_2=\\dfrac{2Mm}{M+m}g \\quad \\text{⑧}\n$$\n\n3) Case (c): Friction vanishes when tension is zero. At that point, $\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{2}{3}$, $v_0=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2gl}{3}}$. Projectile motion gives:\n$$\nv_x=\\dfrac{2}{3}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2gl}{3}}, \\quad v_y=\\dfrac{2}{3}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{23gl}{3}}\n$$\n$$\nv_3=\\sqrt{v_x^2+v_y^2}=\\sqrt{2gl}\n$$\nTension $T_3=0$ near the ground.", 
"img_cn": ["三种接触方式的刚性轻杆与小球系统：(a) 固定转轴，(b) 木板上转轴，(c) 地面接触（无限静摩擦）。"], 
"img_en": ["Rigid light rod and ball system with three contact types: (a) fixed pivot, (b) pivot on a board, (c) contact with ground (infinite friction)."], 
"problem_answer": "1) 小球速度 $v_1 = \\sqrt{2gl}$，杆中张力 $T_1 = 2mg$。\n\n2) 小球速度 $v_2 = \\sqrt{2gl}$，杆中张力 $T_2 = \\dfrac{2Mm}{M+m}g$。\n\n3) 小球速度 $v_3 = \\sqrt{2gl}$，杆中张力 $T_3 = 0$（接近地面时）。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 4 }

{ "problem_id": "98", 
"problem_text_cn": "半径为$R$、质量为$M$、表面光滑的半球静置于光滑水平面上。半球顶端有一质量为$m$的小滑块从静止开始下滑，如图98_1所示。在$\\theta$位置处脱离半球。已知$\\cos\\theta=0.7$，求$M/m$。", 
"problem_text_en": "A smooth hemisphere of radius $R$ and mass $M$ rests on a smooth horizontal surface. A small slider of mass $m$ starts from rest at the top of the hemisphere and slides down, detaching at angle $\\theta$ (where $\\cos\\theta=0.7$). Find the ratio $M/m$.", 
"problem_img": ["98_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】当半球顶上滑块自静止下滑时，通过滑块与半球间的相互作用，半球将向相反的水平方向移动。滑块到达$\\theta$位置时，由题知，滑块将离但又未离半球面，半球对滑块的支承力降为零，即此刻滑块与半球间无相互作用。\n\n由于滑块与半球系统水平方向无外力作用，所以水平方向动量守恒，即满足方程\n$$\nm(v\\cos\\theta-V)=MV \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n由系统机械能守恒，得\n$$\nmgR(1-\\cos\\theta)=\\dfrac{1}{2}m\\left[(v\\cos\\theta-V)^2+(v\\sin\\theta)^2\\right]+\\dfrac{1}{2}MV^2 \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n当滑块运动到图示位置时，滑块与半球无相互作用，此刻半球无加速度，半球参照系为惯性系，滑块的位置又在圆上，因此可写出此时半球系中的法向动力学方程\n$$\nmg\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{mv^2}{R} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n联立方程①、②、③，消去$v$和$V$，整理得比值$\\dfrac{M}{m}$：\n$$\n\\dfrac{M}{m}=\\dfrac{\\cos^3\\theta-3\\cos\\theta+2}{3\\cos\\theta-2}\\approx2.43\n$$\n这里的运算，已利用题给条件$\\cos\\theta=0.7$。", "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】The system has horizontal momentum conservation:\n$$\nm(v\\cos\\theta-V)=MV \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nEnergy conservation:\n$$\nmgR(1-\\cos\\theta)=\\dfrac{1}{2}m\\left[(v\\cos\\theta-V)^2+(v\\sin\\theta)^2\\right]+\\dfrac{1}{2}MV^2 \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nAt detachment, the normal force is zero, so in the hemisphere's frame:\n$$\nmg\\cos\\theta=\\dfrac{mv^2}{R} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nSolving ①–③ with $\\cos\\theta=0.7$:\n$$\n\\dfrac{M}{m}=\\dfrac{\\cos^3\\theta-3\\cos\\theta+2}{3\\cos\\theta-2}\\approx2.43\n$$", "img_cn": ["光滑半球置于光滑水平面，小滑块从顶端下滑，在$\\theta$位置脱离（$\\cos\\theta=0.7$）。"], "img_en": ["A smooth hemisphere on a smooth horizontal surface, a slider slides down from the top and detaches at $\\theta$ ($\\cos\\theta=0.7$)."], 
"problem_answer": "质量比为 $\\dfrac{M}{m} \\approx 2.43$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "99", 
"problem_text_cn": "一质量为$M$、半径为$R$的半圆环，竖直放置于水平面上（假设圆环不倒下，也不能沿水平面滑动——水平地面足够粗糙）。一质量为$m$的小珠套在大圆环上，并静置于环的顶部。今小珠受轻微扰动向右无摩擦滑下。问小珠滑至什么位置（用图99_1中$\\theta$表示）可使半圆环右端$A$点与水平面间的作用力为零？", "problem_text_en": "A semi-circular ring of mass $M$ and radius $R$ stands vertically on a rough horizontal surface (no slipping or toppling). A bead of mass $m$ rests at the top of the ring and slides down without friction. Find the angle $\\theta$ (as in Figure 99_1) where the normal force between the right end $A$ of the ring and the ground becomes zero.", "problem_img": ["99_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】小珠自环顶由静止开始下滑。初始阶段，小珠速度小，重力在法向分力的一部分作为向心力，另一部分由环对珠的支承力抵消。随着珠的高度不断下降，速度逐渐变大，在某一位置$\\theta_1$处，重力在法向分力全部作为向心力，环与珠之间无相互作用。\n\n小珠进一步下滑，速度进一步加大，重力在法向分力已不足以维持小珠的圆周运动，为维持小珠在环上运动，还需由环对小珠施加另一部分向心力。它的反作用力就是小珠对半圆环沿法向向外的力。此力有可能使半圆环右端$A$点抬起来。设半圆环右端$A$点与水平面间无相互作用，但环上$A$点还未离开水平地面时，小珠与环间的相互作用力大小为$N$（法向力），小珠位置在$\\theta_1$，小珠速率为$v_1$。此时，小珠运动满足的法向动力学方程为\n$$\nmg\\cos\\theta_1+N=\\dfrac{mv_1^2}{R} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n并满足机械能守恒条件\n$$\nmgR(1-\\cos\\theta_1)=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_1^2 \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n与此同时，对于半圆环可以写出相对于半圆环左端点$B$的力矩平衡方程，即半圆环重力相对于$B$的力矩等于小珠在$\\theta_1$处作用在环上径向向外的力$N$对$B$点的力矩：\n$$\nMgR=NR\\cos\\theta_1 \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n联立方程①—③，消去$v_1$、$N$，得$\\theta_1$满足的方程\n$$\n3m\\cos^2\\theta_1-2m\\cos\\theta_1+M=0\n$$\n解得为满足题文要求，小珠将滑至$\\theta_1$：\n$$\n\\cos\\theta_1=\\dfrac{1}{3}\\left(1+\\sqrt{1-\\dfrac{3M}{m}}\\right)\n$$\n由于在小珠到达\n$$\n\\theta_1>\\arccos\\left[\\dfrac{1}{3}\\left(1+\\sqrt{1-\\dfrac{3M}{m}}\\right)\\right]\n$$\n时半圆环右端点已离开水平台，因此$\\theta_1$的另一个解（在假设环不动时解得）在此是非物理解。最后得\n$$\n\\theta_1=\\arccos\\left[\\dfrac{1}{3}\\left(1+\\sqrt{1-\\dfrac{3M}{m}}\\right)\\right]\n$$\n显然，上述解存在的条件是\n$$\n1-\\dfrac{3M}{m}\\geqslant0\n$$\n即\n$$\nm\\geqslant3M\n$$", "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】The bead slides from rest at the top. At angle $\\theta_1$, the normal force between the ring and ground at $A$ is zero. The bead's radial force equation:\n$$\nmg\\cos\\theta_1+N=\\dfrac{mv_1^2}{R} \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nEnergy conservation:\n$$\nmgR(1-\\cos\\theta_1)=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_1^2 \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nMoment balance for the ring about point $B$:\n$$\nMgR=NR\\cos\\theta_1 \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nSolving ①–③:\n$$\n3m\\cos^2\\theta_1-2m\\cos\\theta_1+M=0\n$$\n$$\n\\cos\\theta_1=\\dfrac{1}{3}\\left(1+\\sqrt{1-\\dfrac{3M}{m}}\\right)\n$$\nThe solution exists if $m\\geqslant3M$, giving:\n$$\n\\theta_1=\\arccos\\left[\\dfrac{1}{3}\\left(1+\\sqrt{1-\\dfrac{3M}{m}}\\right)\\right]\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["半圆环竖直放置在粗糙水平面，小珠从顶端下滑，求半圆环右端$A$点对地面压力为零时的角度$\\theta$。"], 
"img_en": ["A semi-circular ring on a rough horizontal surface, a bead slides from the top; find $\\theta$ where the normal force at $A$ is zero."], 
"problem_answer": "小珠滑至 $\\theta_1=\\arccos\\left[\\dfrac{1}{3}\\left(1+\\sqrt{1-\\dfrac{3M}{m}}\\right)\\right]$ 时，半圆环右端$A$点与水平面间的作用力为零（条件 $m\\geqslant3M$）。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 4 }

{ "problem_id": "100", 
"problem_text_cn": "一质量为$m$的入射粒子与一质量为$M$的原来静止的靶粒子发生正碰。若已知碰后会有定量的能量$E$转移到入射粒子和靶粒子的内部（即作为靶粒子内能的增值），问入射粒子至少应具有多大的初始动能？", 
"problem_text_en": "A particle of mass $m$ collides head-on with a stationary target particle of mass $M$. A fixed amount of energy $E$ is transferred to the internal energy of the particles after the collision. Find the minimum initial kinetic energy of the incident particle required for this energy transfer.", 
"problem_img": [], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】设入射粒子的初始速度为$v_0$，则初动能为\n$$\nE_k=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2\n$$\n$m$与$M$正碰，有动量守恒和能量守恒关系式\n$$\nmv_0=mv+MV \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^2+\\dfrac{1}{2}MV^2+E \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n其中$v$和$V$分别为碰后入射粒子和靶粒子的速度。这两个方程中，$v$、$V$、$v_0$三个量未知，联立消去$V$，用$v_0$表达$v$。联立消去$V$后，整理得$v$的二次方程\n$$\n\\left(m+\\dfrac{m^2}{M}\\right)v^2-2\\dfrac{m^2}{M}v_0v+\\left(\\dfrac{m^2}{M}v_0^2-mv_0^2+2E\\right)=0\n$$\n由于$v$必须为实数，即$v$要求实数解，必须满足条件\n$$\n\\left(2\\dfrac{m^2}{M}v_0\\right)^2-4\\left(m+\\dfrac{m^2}{M}\\right)\\left(\\dfrac{m^2}{M}v_0^2-mv_0^2+2E\\right)\\geqslant0\n$$\n解得\n$$\nv_0\\geqslant\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2(M+m)E}{Mm}}\n$$\n即入射粒子初始动能应满足条件为\n$$\nE_k=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2\\geqslant\\dfrac{M+m}{M}E\n$$\n【说明】尽管有部分能量转移到靶粒子内部，但系统动量守恒仍成立。产生这种能量转移的下限，就是把质心系中的动能（即相对运动动能）全部转变为$E$，而质心动能不变。得\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_0^2\\geqslant E, \\quad \\text{其中} \\quad \\mu=\\dfrac{Mm}{M+m}\n$$\n由此，立即得到$E_k$。", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】Let the initial velocity be $v_0$, so initial kinetic energy is $E_k=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2$. Momentum and energy conservation:\n$$\nmv_0=mv+MV \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^2+\\dfrac{1}{2}MV^2+E \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nEliminating $V$ gives a quadratic in $v$. For real $v$, the discriminant is non-negative:\n$$\nv_0\\geqslant\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2(M+m)E}{Mm}}\n$$\nThus, the initial kinetic energy must satisfy:\n$$\nE_k\\geqslant\\dfrac{M+m}{M}E\n$$\nThe minimum occurs when the CM-frame kinetic energy equals $E$, using $\\mu=\\dfrac{Mm}{M+m}$:\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_0^2=E \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad E_k\\geqslant\\dfrac{M+m}{M}E\n$$", 
"img_cn": [], 
"img_en": [], 
"problem_answer": "入射粒子至少应具有的初始动能为 $E_k \\geqslant \\dfrac{M+m}{M}E$。", "problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "101", 
"problem_text_cn": "一质量为$m$的入射粒子与一质量为$M$的原来静止的靶粒子发生正碰。若已知碰后会有定量的能量$E$转移到入射粒子和靶粒子的内部（即作为靶粒子内能的增值），问入射粒子至少应具有多大的初始动能？", 
