"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】Let the initial velocity be $v_0$, so initial kinetic energy is $E_k=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2$. Momentum and energy conservation:\n$$\nmv_0=mv+MV \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^2+\\dfrac{1}{2}MV^2+E \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nEliminating $V$ gives a quadratic in $v$. For real $v$, the discriminant is non-negative:\n$$\nv_0\\geqslant\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2(M+m)E}{Mm}}\n$$\nThus, the initial kinetic energy must satisfy:\n$$\nE_k\\geqslant\\dfrac{M+m}{M}E\n$$\nThe minimum occurs when the CM-frame kinetic energy equals $E$, using $\\mu=\\dfrac{Mm}{M+m}$:\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}\\mu v_0^2=E \\quad \\Rightarrow \\quad E_k\\geqslant\\dfrac{M+m}{M}E\n$$", 
"img_cn": [], 
"img_en": [], 
"problem_answer": "入射粒子至少应具有的初始动能为 $E_k \\geqslant \\dfrac{M+m}{M}E$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "102", 
"problem_text_cn": "两个钢球，质量密度相同，下面一个的半径为$2a$，上面一个的半径为$a$，由一水平巨型钢板平面上高$h$处（按大球的球心测量）落下。求两球下落并与钢板碰后，上面那个球弹起的最大高度（球心到钢板平台）是多少？", 
"problem_text_en": "Two steel balls of the same density, with radii $2a$ and $a$, are dropped from height $h$ (measured from the center of the larger ball) onto a horizontal steel plate. Find the maximum height reached by the smaller ball after both balls collide with the plate and then with each other.", "problem_img": ["102_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】设下面小球质量为$m_1$，下面大球质量为$m_2$，显然，$m_2=8m_1$。当两球下落、大球落地时的共同速度为\n$$\nv_2=\\sqrt{2g(h-2a)}\n$$\n大球同地面作弹性碰撞，弹起向上的速度仍为$v_2$，接着大球与向下的小球作弹性碰撞，此时，小球向下的速度为\n$$\nv_1=v_2\n$$\n设大小两球碰后的速度分别为$v_2'$和$v_1'$，向上取为正方向。写出两球弹性碰撞的方程\n$$\nm_2v_2-m_1v_1=m_2v_2'+m_1v_1' \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\nv_2+v_1=v_1'-v_2' \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n联立解得\n$$\nv_2'=\\dfrac{5}{9}v_2=\\dfrac{5}{9}\\sqrt{2g(h-2a)}\n$$\n$$\nv_1'=\\dfrac{23}{9}v_2=\\dfrac{23}{9}\\sqrt{2g(h-2a)}\n$$\n利用机械能守恒可以求出小球能达到的最大高度$H$（由地面算起至小球球心）：\n$$\nH=3a+\\dfrac{v_1'^2}{2g}=3a+\\dfrac{529}{81}(h-2a)\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】Let $m_1$ be the mass of the small ball, $m_2=8m_1$ the large ball. Speed when the large ball hits the ground:\n$$\nv_2=\\sqrt{2g(h-2a)}\n$$\nThe large ball rebounds with speed $v_2$, then collides elastically with the small ball (speed $v_1=v_2$ downward). Elastic collision equations:\n$$\nm_2v_2-m_1v_1=m_2v_2'+m_1v_1' \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\nv_2+v_1=v_1'-v_2' \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nSolving:\n$$\nv_2'=\\dfrac{5}{9}v_2, \\quad v_1'=\\dfrac{23}{9}v_2\n$$\nMaximum height of the small ball:\n$$\nH=3a+\\dfrac{v_1'^2}{2g}=3a+\\dfrac{529}{81}(h-2a)\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["两个钢球（半径$a$和$2a$）从高$h$处下落，与钢板碰撞后小球弹起的最大高度。"], 
"img_en": ["Two steel balls (radii $a$ and $2a$) dropped from height $h$, find the maximum height of the smaller ball after collisions."], 
"problem_answer": "上面小球弹起的最大高度为 $H = 3a + \\dfrac{529}{81}(h-2a)$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "103", 
"problem_text_cn": "如图103_1所示，一弹子球由阶梯上逐级弹下，它在每一步阶梯的同一位置，并且在每一步阶梯上弹起相同的高度。设该阶梯的高和宽均为$s$，弹起后与弹起前在竖直方向的速度大小之比等于$e$，球与阶梯相碰无摩擦。求弹子球所需的水平速度和弹起高度。", 
"problem_text_en": "As shown in Figure 103_1, a billiard ball bounces down a staircase, bouncing to the same height on each step. Each step has height and width $s$, and the coefficient of restitution in the vertical direction is $e$. There is no friction between the ball and the steps. Find the required horizontal velocity and the bounce height.", 
"problem_img": ["103_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】图103_1(b)表示相继两阶梯间弹子球的运动。设一级弹起后的速度为$v_2$，下一级落地前的速度为$v_1$，分别用分量表示：\n$$\nv_1=v_x\\boldsymbol{i}+v_y\\boldsymbol{j}\n$$\n$$\nv_2=v_x\\boldsymbol{i}+v_y'\\boldsymbol{j}\n$$\n其中$v_x$、$v_y$为代数值。利用碰撞关系：\n$$\n-v_y'=ev_y \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n一级弹起后至下一级弹前机械能守恒：\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}m(v_x^2+v_y'^2)=\\dfrac{1}{2}m(v_x^2+v_y^2)+mgs \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n联立解得\n$$\nv_y^2=\\dfrac{2gs}{1-e^2} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n利用运动学关系\n$$\nv_y=v_y'+gt\n$$\n$$\nt=\\dfrac{v_y-v_y'}{g}=\\dfrac{v_y(1+e)}{g}=\\dfrac{1+e}{g}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2gs}{1-e^2}} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n$$\nv_x=\\dfrac{s}{t}\n$$\n$$\nv_x=\\dfrac{gs}{v_y(1+e)}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{gs(1-e)}{2(1+e)}} \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n最后求出弹起高度$H$：\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_y'^2=mgH\n$$\n$$\nH=\\dfrac{v_y'^2}{2g}=\\dfrac{e^2}{2g}v_y^2=\\dfrac{e^2s}{1-e^2} \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\n式⑤、⑥即为水平速度和弹起的高度。", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】The motion between two steps is shown in Figure 103_1(b). Let $v_1=v_x\\boldsymbol{i}+v_y\\boldsymbol{j}$ (before impact) and $v_2=v_x\\boldsymbol{i}+v_y'\\boldsymbol{j}$ (after impact). The coefficient of restitution gives:\n$$\n-v_y'=ev_y \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nEnergy conservation between bounce and next impact:\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}m(v_x^2+v_y'^2)=\\dfrac{1}{2}m(v_x^2+v_y^2)+mgs \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nSolving:\n$$\nv_y^2=\\dfrac{2gs}{1-e^2} \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nTime between impacts:\n$$\nt=\\dfrac{v_y-v_y'}{g}=\\dfrac{v_y(1+e)}{g} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\nHorizontal velocity:\n$$\nv_x=\\dfrac{s}{t}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{gs(1-e)}{2(1+e)}} \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\nBounce height:\n$$\nH=\\dfrac{v_y'^2}{2g}=\\dfrac{e^2s}{1-e^2} \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["弹子球在阶梯上逐级弹下，每步高宽均为$s$，竖直恢复系数为$e$，求水平速度和弹起高度。"], 
"img_en": ["A billiard ball bouncing down a staircase with step height/width $s$ and vertical restitution coefficient $e$; find horizontal velocity and bounce height."], 
"problem_answer": "水平速度为 $v_x = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{gs(1-e)}{2(1+e)}}$，弹起高度为 $H = \\dfrac{e^2s}{1-e^2}$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "104", 
"problem_text_cn": "如图104_1(a)所示，一截面为等腰直角三角形的棱柱$ABC$，被约束在一光滑平面轨道上，$AB$边沿只能沿$DE$光滑轨道运动。现有一质量与棱柱$ABC$质量$m$相同的光滑小球，在与$ABC$同一水平平面沿直轨道$DE$的方向，以速度$v_0$与处于静止的$ABC$发生完全弹性碰撞。求碰撞后各自的速度。", 
"problem_text_en": "As shown in Figure 104_1(a), a prism $ABC$ with an isosceles right triangular cross-section is constrained to move along a smooth horizontal track $DE$. A smooth ball of mass $m$ (same as the prism) moves along $DE$ with speed $v_0$ and collides elastically with the stationary prism. Find the velocities of both after the collision.", 
"problem_img": ["104_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】分别以小球和棱柱$ABC$作为研究对象，并设碰后小球速度为$v$，方向与轨道方向夹角$\\theta$，棱柱的速度为$V$，方向沿轨道，如图5-练28(b)所示。\n\n小球与棱柱系统沿轨道方向动量守恒，有\n$$\nmv_0=mv\\cos\\theta+mV \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^2+\\dfrac{1}{2}mV^2 \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n以上两方程中，有三个未知量$v$、$V$和$\\theta$。还需一个方程。\n\n以小球为对象，它与棱柱$ABC$碰撞中，受到垂直于$AC$面的水平力$N$作用。由动量定理得\n$$\nN\\Delta t=mv_{\\perp}-mv_{0\\perp}\n$$\n此矢量式在$AC$方向上的分量为\n$$\n0=mv\\cos(45^{\\circ}-\\theta)-mv_0\\cos45^{\\circ}\n$$\n即\n$$\nv(\\cos\\theta+\\sin\\theta)=v_0 \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n联立方程①、②、③，解得\n$$\n\\text{tg}\\theta=\\dfrac{1}{2} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n$$\nv=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{5}}{3}v_0 \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n$$\nV=\\dfrac{2}{3}v_0 \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】Let the ball's velocity after collision be $v$ at angle $\\theta$ to the track, and the prism's velocity be $V$ along the track. Momentum conservation along the track:\n$$\nmv_0=mv\\cos\\theta+mV \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\nEnergy conservation:\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv^2+\\dfrac{1}{2}mV^2 \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\nThe force during collision is perpendicular to $AC$, so the component of velocity along $AC$ is unchanged:\n$$\nv(\\cos\\theta+\\sin\\theta)=v_0 \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\nSolving ①–③:\n$$\n\\tan\\theta=\\dfrac{1}{2}, \\quad v=\\dfrac{\\sqrt{5}}{3}v_0, \\quad V=\\dfrac{2}{3}v_0\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["等腰直角三角形棱柱$ABC$被约束在光滑轨道，小球以速度$v_0$与之发生弹性碰撞，求碰后速度。"], 
"img_en": ["An isosceles right prism $ABC$ on a smooth track, a ball collides elastically with it at speed $v_0$; find post-collision velocities."], 
"problem_answer": "小球速度为 $v = \\dfrac{\\sqrt{5}}{3}v_0$（与轨道夹角 $\\tan\\theta=\\dfrac{1}{2}$），棱柱速度为 $V = \\dfrac{2}{3}v_0$（沿轨道方向）。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "105", 
"problem_text_cn": "三个大小相同、质量不同的小球，并排平行地悬挂在同样长度的绳上，彼此相接触。今把质量为$m_1$的第一个小球与竖直方向，上升到高为$h$处，再自由释放，如图105_1所示。要使第一个小球与质量为$m_2$的第二个小球、第二个小球与质量为$m_3$的第三个小球碰撞后，三球具有相同动量，问$m_2$和$m_3$各为多大（用$m_1$表示）？三球碰后各上升多高？", 
"problem_text_en": "Three balls of the same size but different masses hang from strings of equal length, touching each other. The first ball (mass $m_1$) is pulled aside to height $h$ and released, colliding elastically with the second ($m_2$), which then collides elastically with the third ($m_3$). Find $m_2$ and $m_3$ (in terms of $m_1$) such that all three balls have the same momentum after the collisions, and find the height each ball rises to.", 
"problem_img": ["105_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】由于碰撞是弹性碰撞，满足动量守恒，在摆动中满足机械能守恒。各次碰撞逐次讨论。\n\n$m_1$与$m_2$的碰撞。未碰前$m_1$的动量为$p_1$，即\n$$\np_1=m_1v_0=m_1\\sqrt{2gh}\n$$\n$m_1$与$m_2$碰撞的守恒方程\n$$\np_1=p_1'+p_2' \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{p_1^2}{2m_1}=\\dfrac{p_1'^2}{2m_1}+\\dfrac{p_2'^2}{2m_2} \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n其中$p_1'$和$p_2'$为碰后$m_1$和$m_2$的动量。联立解得\n$$\np_1'=\\dfrac{m_1-m_2}{m_1+m_2}p_1\n$$\n$$\np_2'=\\dfrac{2m_1}{m_1+m_2}p_1\n$$\n$m_2$与$m_3$的碰撞。碰撞的守恒方程\n$$\np_2'=p_2''+p_3' \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{p_2'^2}{2m_2}=\\dfrac{p_2''^2}{2m_2}+\\dfrac{p_3'^2}{2m_3} \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n其中$p_2''$和$p_3'$为碰后$m_2$和$m_3$的动量。联立解得\n$$\np_2''=\\dfrac{m_2-m_3}{m_2+m_3}p_2'=\\dfrac{m_2-m_3}{m_2+m_3}\\cdot\\dfrac{2m_1}{m_1+m_2}p_1\n$$\n$$\np_3'=\\dfrac{2m_2}{m_2+m_3}p_2'=\\dfrac{2m_2}{m_2+m_3}\\cdot\\dfrac{2m_1}{m_1+m_2}p_1\n$$\n为了使碰后三个小球动量相等，即\n$$\np_1'=p_2''=p_3'\n$$\n得到\n$$\n\\dfrac{m_1-m_2}{m_1+m_2}=\\dfrac{m_2-m_3}{m_2+m_3}\\cdot\\dfrac{2m_1}{m_1+m_2}=\\dfrac{2m_1}{m_1+m_2}\\cdot\\dfrac{2m_2}{m_2+m_3}\n$$\n即\n$$\nm_1-m_2=\\dfrac{4m_1m_2}{m_2+m_3}\n$$\n$$\nm_1(m_2+m_3)-m_2(m_2+m_3)=4m_1m_2\n$$\n解得$m_2$、$m_3$\n$$\nm_2=\\dfrac{1}{3}m_1, \\quad m_3=\\dfrac{1}{6}m_1\n$$\n因三小球动量相等，质量$m_1>m_2>m_3$，所以三小球各自摆向最高点。\n\n设三个小球上升的高度分别为$h_1$、$h_2$、$h_3$，且\n$$\np_1'=p_2''=p_3'=\\dfrac{1}{3}p_1\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{p_1'^2}{2m_1}=m_1gh_1\n$$\n利用第一个小球在无碰撞下摆动，高度$h$表示碰后三小球的高度：\n$$\n\\dfrac{p_1^2}{2m_1}=m_1gh\n$$\n$$\nh_1=\\dfrac{p_1'^2}{2m_1g}=\\dfrac{p_1^2}{2m_1g}\\cdot\\dfrac{1}{9}=\\dfrac{h}{9}\n$$\n同理\n$$\nh_2=\\dfrac{p_2''^2}{2m_2g}=\\dfrac{4h}{9}\n$$\n$$\nh_3=\\dfrac{p_3'^2}{2m_3g}=4h\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】Elastic collisions conserve momentum and kinetic energy. For $m_1$ and $m_2$:\n$$\np_1=p_1'+p_2', \\quad \\dfrac{p_1^2}{2m_1}=\\dfrac{p_1'^2}{2m_1}+\\dfrac{p_2'^2}{2m_2}\n$$\n$$\np_1'=\\dfrac{m_1-m_2}{m_1+m_2}p_1, \\quad p_2'=\\dfrac{2m_1}{m_1+m_2}p_1\n$$\nFor $m_2$ and $m_3$:\n$$\np_2'=p_2''+p_3', \\quad \\dfrac{p_2'^2}{2m_2}=\\dfrac{p_2''^2}{2m_2}+\\dfrac{p_3'^2}{2m_3}\n$$\n$$\np_2''=\\dfrac{m_2-m_3}{m_2+m_3}p_2', \\quad p_3'=\\dfrac{2m_2}{m_2+m_3}p_2'\n$$\nSetting $p_1'=p_2''=p_3'$:\n$$\n\\dfrac{m_1-m_2}{m_1+m_2}=\\dfrac{m_2-m_3}{m_2+m_3}\\cdot\\dfrac{2m_1}{m_1+m_2}=\\dfrac{4m_1m_2}{(m_1+m_2)(m_2+m_3)}\n$$\nSolving:\n$$\nm_2=\\dfrac{1}{3}m_1, \\quad m_3=\\dfrac{1}{6}m_1\n$$\nHeights:\n$$\nh_1=\\dfrac{h}{9}, \\quad h_2=\\dfrac{4h}{9}, \\quad h_3=4h\n$$", 
"img_cn": ["三个小球悬挂碰撞，使碰后动量相等，求$m_2$、$m_3$及各球上升高度。"], 
"img_en": ["Three hanging balls collide elastically; find $m_2$, $m_3$, and the heights each rises to, given equal final momentum."], 
"problem_answer": "质量为 $m_2 = \\dfrac{1}{3}m_1$，$m_3 = \\dfrac{1}{6}m_1$；上升高度为 $h_1 = \\dfrac{h}{9}$，$h_2 = \\dfrac{4h}{9}$，$h_3 = 4h$。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 3 }

{ "problem_id": "106", 
"problem_text_cn": "如图106所示，水平桌面上有一质量为$m=0.5$千克的长形盒，运动时与桌面的摩擦系数为$\\mu=0.125$。在盒内左端放一个质量同为$m$的小物块，物块与盒间无摩擦，在盒的最大行程$L=0.5$米，初始时小物块与盒系统静止，且物块与盒左端相接触。今在盒左端外壁突然给一向右的冲量$I=1$牛顿·秒，设物块与盒间碰撞没有机械能损失，且盒在左、右两端壁碰撞后速度方向立即反向，速度大小不变。求物块与盒从开始运动到完全静止所用时间是多少？取$g=10$米/秒²。", 
"problem_text_en": "As shown in Figure 106, a long box of mass $m=0.5$ kg slides on a horizontal table with friction coefficient $\\mu=0.125$. A block of mass $m$ is placed at the left end of the box, with no friction between them. The box's maximum travel is $L=0.5$ m. Initially, the system is at rest. An impulse $I=1$ N·s is applied to the left end of the box. Collisions between the block and box walls are elastic, and the box reverses direction (same speed) after hitting the walls. Find the total time until the system comes to rest. Take $g=10$ m/s².", 
"problem_img": ["106_1.png"], 
"problem_img_process": [], 
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】盒受击打，获动量$I=mv_0$。盒与物块相碰，因两者质量相等，物块与盒交换速度，物块获速度$v_1$\n$$\nv_1=\\dfrac{I}{m}=\\dfrac{1}{0.5}=2\\text{（米/秒）}\n$$\n在此前经历时间可略而不计。\n\n以后的运动，物块以速度$v_1$在静止盒内匀速运动开始，达盒右端与盒相撞，交换速度，物块静止，盒向右作减速运动。当盒左端与物块相撞（未碰）时，盒速度降为$v_2$。最后，物块与盒以某一速度交换。盒静止，物块开始以速度$v_2$向右运动，重复前面的过程。最后，物块与盒在左、右两端与盒壁相继两次碰撞，交换速度，物块静止，盒向左运动，在左左端与物块相碰而停止为止。\n\n从以上分析知，物块在静止盒内的运动为匀速运动，物块的运动只起到传递速度的作用。盒在桌面上运动是一个匀减速运动，由于物块的运动只起到传递速度的作用，因此，把盒的各段匀减速运动作为整个运动。就是一个以$v_1$为初速度，以$a=\\dfrac{\\mu2mg}{m}=2\\mu g$为加速度值、以末速度为零的匀减速运动。总位移为$l$\n$$\nl=\\dfrac{v_1^2}{2\\cdot2\\mu g}=\\dfrac{4}{4\\times0.125\\times10}=0.8\\text{（米）}>L\n$$\n经历的时间\n$$\nt_0=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2l}{2\\mu g}}=\\sqrt{\\dfrac{0.8}{0.25\\times10}}=0.8\\text{（秒）}\n$$\n物在盒内第一次运动速度为$v_1$，所以用时\n$$\nt_1=\\dfrac{L}{v_1}=\\dfrac{0.5}{2}=0.25\\text{（秒）}\n$$\n物在盒内第二次运动速度为$v_2$，这是盒以初速$v_1$、阻力$\\mu\\cdot2mg$作用下经过位移$L$后的末速度，所以$v_2$满足\n$$\n\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_1^2=\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_2^2+2\\mu gL\\cdot\\dfrac{1}{2}m\n$$\n$$\nv_2=\\sqrt{v_1^2-\\mu gL}=\\sqrt{4-0.4\\times0.125\\times10\\times0.5}=1.225\\text{（米/秒）}\n$$\n所以，物块在盒内第二次以速度$v_2$所用时间\n$$\nt_2=\\dfrac{L}{v_2}=\\dfrac{0.5}{1.225}=0.41\\text{（秒）}\n$$\n此后，盒与物块撞后，位移$l-L=0.3$米后停下来。整个过程\n最后得从初始直到盒停止作整个运动过程总共用的时间为$t$\n$$\nt=T_0+t_1+t_2=0.8+0.25+0.41=1.46\\text{（秒）}\n$$", 
"problem_solution_en": "【Analysis and Solution】The box receives an impulse $I=mv_0$, so $v_1=\\dfrac{I}{m}=2$ m/s. Collisions between the block and box exchange velocities, so the block moves at $v_1$ while the box decelerates with $a=2\\mu g=2.5$ m/s². The total distance the box slides is:\n$$\nl=\\dfrac{v_1^2}{2a}=0.8\\text{ m}\n$$\nTime for the box to stop:\n$$\nt_0=\\dfrac{v_1}{a}=0.8\\text{ s}\n$$\nTime for the block to move $L=0.5$ m at $v_1$:\n$$\nt_1=\\dfrac{L}{v_1}=0.25\\text{ s}\n$$\nAfter the first collision, the box's speed is:\n$$\nv_2=\\sqrt{v_1^2-2aL}=1.225\\text{ m/s}\n$$\nTime for the block to move $L$ at $v_2$:\n$$\nt_2=\\dfrac{L}{v_2}=0.41\\text{ s}\n$$\nTotal time:\n$$\nt=t_0+t_1+t_2=1.46\\text{ s}\n$$",
"img_cn": ["长形盒在桌面受冲量后与物块弹性碰撞，求系统静止所用时间。"], 
"img_en": ["A box on a table is given an impulse, colliding elastically with a block inside; find the time until the system stops."], 
"problem_answer": "系统从开始运动到完全静止所用时间为 $t = 1.46$ 秒。", 
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Kinematics"], "difficulty": 4 }
  {
    "problem_id": "107",
    "problem_text_cn": "【练习 5-31】在用轴 235 作燃料的核反应堆中, 轴 235 核吸收一个动能约为 $0.025 \text{eV}$ 的热中子(慢中子)后, 可发生裂变反应, 放出能量和 2~3 个快中子, 而快中子不利于轴 235 的裂变。为了能使裂变反应继续下去, 需要将反应中放出的快中子减速。有一种减速的方法是使用石墨(碳 12)作减速剂。设中子与碳原子的碰撞是对心弹性碰撞, 问一个动能为 $E_0 = 1.75 \text{MeV}$ 的快中子需要与静止的碳原子碰撞多少次, 才能减速成为 $0.025 \text{eV}$ 的热中子?",
    "problem_text_en": "【Exercise 5-31】 In a nuclear reactor using Uranium-235 as fuel, a U-235 nucleus absorbs a thermal neutron (slow neutron) with a kinetic energy of approximately $0.025 \text{eV}$, leading to a fission reaction that releases energy and 2-3 fast neutrons. However, fast neutrons are not conducive to the fission of U-235. To sustain the fission reaction, the fast neutrons released must be decelerated. One method of deceleration is using graphite (Carbon-12) as a moderator. Assuming the collisions between neutrons and carbon atoms are head-on elastic collisions, how many times must a fast neutron with an initial kinetic energy of $E_0 = 1.75 \text{MeV}$ collide with stationary carbon atoms to slow down to a thermal neutron energy of $0.025 \text{eV}$?",
    "problem_img": [],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】 设中子和碳核的质量分别为 $m$ 和 $M$, 碰撞前中子的速度为 $v_0$, 碳核静止, 碰撞后中子和碳核的速度分别为 $v$ 和 $V$。因为碰撞是弹性碰撞, 所以在碰撞前后, 动量和动能均守恒。又因对心碰撞, 故有\n$$\nmv_0 = mv + MV \\quad \\text{①}\n$$\n$$\n\\frac{1}{2}mv_0^2 = \frac{1}{2}mv^2 + \frac{1}{2}MV^2 \\quad \\text{②}\n$$\n解得\n$$\nv = \\frac{m - M}{m + M} v_0 \\quad \\text{③}\n$$\n因 $M = 12m$, 代入式③得\n$$\nv = -\\frac{11}{13} v_0 \\quad \\text{④}\n$$\n负号表示 $v$ 的方向与 $v_0$ 方向相反, 即与碳核碰撞后中子被反弹。因此, 经过一次碰撞后中子的能量为\n$$\nE_1 = \\frac{1}{2}mv^2 = \\frac{1}{2}m \\left(-\\frac{11}{13}\\right)^2 v_0^2\n$$\n即\n$$\nE_1 = \\left(\\frac{11}{13}\\right)^2 E_0 \\quad \\text{⑤}\n$$\n经过 $2, 3, \\cdots, n$ 次碰撞后, 中子的能量依次为 $E_2, E_3, \\cdots, E_n$, 有\n$$\nE_2 = \\left(\\frac{11}{13}\\right)^2 E_1 = \\left(\\frac{11}{13}\\right)^4 E_0\n$$\n$$\nE_3 = \\left(\\frac{11}{13}\\right)^6 E_0\n$$\n$$\\cdots$$\n$$\nE_n = \\left(\\frac{E_1}{E_0}\\right)^n E_0 = \\left(\\frac{11}{13}\\right)^{2n} E_0 \\quad \\text{⑥}\n$$\n解出 $n$\n$$\nn = \\frac{1}{2} \\frac{\\lg(E_n/E_0)}{\\lg(11/13)} \\quad \\text{⑦}\n$$\n已知\n$$\n\\frac{E_n}{E_0} = \\frac{0.025}{1.75 \\times 10^6} = \\frac{1}{7} \\times 10^{-7}\n$$\n代入式⑦得\n$$\nn = \\frac{\\lg(\\frac{1}{7} \\times 10^{-7})}{2\\lg(\\frac{11}{13})} = \\frac{-7 - \\lg 7}{2(-0.07255)} = \\frac{7.8451}{0.1451} \\approx 54\n$$\n因此, 初能量 $E_0 = 1.75 \text{MeV}$ 的快中子经过 54 次碰撞后, 才能减速成为 $0.025 \text{eV}$ 的热中子。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】 Let the masses of the neutron and carbon nucleus be $m$ and $M$ respectively. The initial velocity of the neutron is $v_0$, and the carbon nucleus is stationary. Let $v$ and $V$ be their velocities after collision. Since it's an elastic head-on collision, momentum and kinetic energy are conserved:\n$$\nmv_0 = mv + MV \\quad (1)\n$$\n$$\n\\frac{1}{2}mv_0^2 = \frac{1}{2}mv^2 + \frac{1}{2}MV^2 \\quad (2)\n$$\nSolving these equations yields:\n$$\nv = \\frac{m - M}{m + M} v_0 \\quad (3)\n$$\nSince $M = 12m$, substituting this into (3) gives:\n$$\nv = -\\frac{11}{13} v_0 \\quad (4)\n$$\nThe negative sign indicates the neutron recoils. The energy after one collision $E_1$ is:\n$$\nE_1 = \\frac{1}{2}mv^2 = \\left(\\frac{11}{13}\\right)^2 E_0 \\quad (5)\n$$\nAfter $n$ collisions, the energy $E_n$ is:\n$$\nE_n = \\left(\\frac{11}{13}\\right)^{2n} E_0 \\quad (6)\n$$\nSolving for $n$:\n$$\nn = \\frac{\\lg(E_n/E_0)}{2\\lg(11/13)} \\quad (7)\n$$\nGiven $E_n/E_0 = 0.025 / (1.75 \\times 10^6) = \\frac{1}{7} \\times 10^{-7}$, substituting the values:\n$$\nn = \\frac{\\lg(1/7 \\times 10^{-7})}{2\\lg(11/13)} \\approx 54\n$$\nTherefore, it takes 54 collisions.",
    "img_cn": [],
    "img_en": [],
    "problem_answer": "需要碰撞约 54 次。",
    "problem_tags": ["Modern Physics", "Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "2"
  },
  {
    "problem_id": "108",
    "problem_text_cn": "【练习 5-32】如图 5-练 32 所示, 质量为 $m$ 的长方形箱子, 放在光滑的水平地面上, 箱内有一质量也为 $m$ 的小滑块, 滑块与箱底间无摩擦。开始时箱子静止不动, 滑块以恒定的速度 $v_0$ 从箱子的 A 壁处向 B 壁处运动, 后与 B 壁碰撞。假定滑块与箱壁每碰撞一次, 两者相对速度的大小变为该次碰撞前相对速度的 $e$ 倍, $e = \\sqrt[4]{\\frac{1}{2}}$。\n1) 要使滑块与箱子这一系统损耗的总动能不超过其初始动能的 $40\\%$, 滑块与箱壁最多可碰撞几次?\n2) 从滑块开始运动到刚完成上述次数的碰撞期间, 箱子的平均速度是多少?",
    "problem_text_en": "【Exercise 5-32】 As shown in Figure 5-Ex 32, a rectangular box of mass $m$ is placed on a smooth horizontal surface. Inside the box is a small slider, also of mass $m$, with no friction between the slider and the bottom of the box. Initially, the box is stationary, and the slider moves from wall A toward wall B at a constant velocity $v_0$, then collides with wall B. Assume that for each collision between the slider and the box wall, the magnitude of their relative velocity becomes $e$ times the relative velocity before the collision, where $e = \\sqrt[4]{1/2}$.\n1) To ensure that the total kinetic energy loss of the slider-box system does not exceed 40% of its initial kinetic energy, what is the maximum number of collisions allowed between the slider and the walls?\n2) What is the average velocity of the box during the interval from the start of the slider's motion until the completion of the aforementioned number of collisions?",
    "problem_img": ["108_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1) 这是一个二质点系统, 系统初始动能为 $E_0 = \\frac{1}{2}mv_0^2$。滑块与箱子间的碰撞损耗的是相对运动动能。碰撞前的相对运动速度为 $v_0$; 碰一次后相对运动速度为 $ev_0$; 碰 $n$ 次后相对运动速度为 $e^n v_0$。因此, 经 $n$ 次碰撞后, 相对运动动能的损失为\n$$\n\\Delta E'_k = \\frac{1}{2}\\mu v_0^2 - \\frac{1}{2}\\mu(e^n v_0)^2 = \\frac{1}{2}(1 - e^{2n})\\mu v_0^2 = \\frac{1}{4}(1 - e^{2n})mv_0^2\n$$\n其中利用了折合质量 $\\mu = \\frac{mm}{m+m} = \\frac{1}{2}m$。系统动能损耗与原系统动能之比为\n$$\n\\eta = \\frac{\\Delta E'_k}{E_0} = \\frac{1}{2}(1 - e^{2n})\n$$\n为满足题文要求 $\\eta < 40\\%$, 得 $1 - e^{2n} < 0.8$, 即 $e^{2n} > 0.2$。代入 $e = \\sqrt[4]{1/2}$, 解得 $n \le 4.64$, 最大正整数为 $n=4$。\n2) 设第 1, 2, 3, 4 次碰撞的时刻为 $t_1, t_2, t_3, t_4$, 每一段时间间隔内箱子与物块相对位移均为 $L$。利用相对速度表达式得出每段时间表达式:\n$\\Delta t_0 = t_1 - 0 = L/v_0$; $\\Delta t_1 = t_2 - t_1 = L/ev_0$; $\\Delta t_2 = t_3 - t_2 = L/e^2v_0$; $\\Delta t_3 = t_4 - t_3 = L/e^3v_0$。\n质心速度为 $v_c = \\frac{1}{2}v_0$。各段箱子速度为 $V_1=0$, $V_2=\\frac{1}{2}v_0(1+e)$, $V_3=\\frac{1}{2}v_0(1-e^2)$, $V_4=\\frac{1}{2}v_0(1+e^3)$。\n在第四次碰撞前箱子的平均速度为 $\\overline{V} = \\frac{\\sum V_i \\Delta t_i}{\\sum \\Delta t_i} = \\frac{v_0}{2}$。\n简洁解法：箱子的平均速度 = 位移/时间 = (质心的位移 + 相对质心的位移)/时间。由于箱子相对质心的位置在初态和末态（第四次碰撞瞬间）未变, 相对质心的位移为零, 故平均速度等于质心速度 $v_0/2$。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】\n1) For this two-particle system, the initial kinetic energy is $E_0 = \\frac{1}{2}mv_0^2$. The energy loss occurs in the relative kinetic energy. The initial relative velocity is $v_0$. After $n$ collisions, it is $e^n v_0$. The loss in relative kinetic energy is $\\Delta E'_k = \\frac{1}{2}\\mu v_0^2 (1 - e^{2n})$, where $\\mu = m/2$. The loss ratio is $\\eta = \\frac{1}{2}(1 - e^{2n})$. Setting $\\eta < 0.4$, we get $e^{2n} > 0.2$. With $e = (1/2)^{1/4}$, $n \le 4.64$, so $n_{max} = 4$.\n2) Let the collision times be $t_1, t_2, t_3, t_4$. The relative displacement between each collision is $L$. The time intervals are $\\Delta t_i = L / (e^i v_0)$. The center-of-mass velocity $v_c = v_0/2$ is constant. The box's average velocity can be calculated by $\\overline{V} = \\frac{\\text{Total Displacement}}{\\text{Total Time}}$. Since the box's position relative to the center of mass is the same at $t=0$ and just before the 4th collision (both at wall A), the total displacement of the box equals the displacement of the center of mass. Thus, $\\overline{V} = v_c = v_0/2$.",
    "img_cn": ["质量为 $m$ 的长方形箱子, 放在光滑的水平地面上, 箱内有一质量也为 $m$ 的小滑块, 箱内长为 $L$。滑块以速度 $v_0$ 从 A 壁向 B 壁运动。"],
    "img_en": ["A rectangular box of mass $m$ on a smooth surface with a slider of mass $m$ inside. The length of the box is $L$. The slider moves from wall A to wall B with velocity $v_0$."],
    "problem_answer": "1) 最多碰撞 4 次; 2) 箱子的平均速度为 $v_0/2$。",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "3"
  },
  {
    "problem_id": "109",
    "problem_text_cn": "【练习 5-33】质量分别为 $m_1$ 和 $m_2$ 的两个小球, 系在长为 $l$ 的不可伸长的轻绳两端, 放置在光滑水平桌面面上。初始时绳是拉直的。在桌面上另有一质量为 $m_3$ 的光滑小球, 以垂直于绳的速度 $u$ 与小球 $m_1$ 对心正碰, 若恢复系数为 $e$, 求碰撞后瞬间绳中的张力。",
    "problem_text_en": "【Exercise 5-33】 Two small balls with masses $m_1$ and $m_2$ are attached to the ends of an inextensible light string of length $l$, placed on a smooth horizontal table. Initially, the string is taut. Another smooth small ball of mass $m_3$ moves on the table with a velocity $u$ perpendicular to the string and undergoes a head-on collision with ball $m_1$. If the coefficient of restitution is $e$, find the tension in the string immediately after the collision.",
    "problem_img": ["109_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】 设 $m_3$ 与 $m_1$ 碰后沿垂直于绳方向的速度分别为 $u'$ 和 $u_1$。由于绳方向对 $m_1$ 的冲量并不影响垂直于绳方向的动量, 故有：\n$$\nm_3 u = m_3 u' + m_1 u_1\n$$\n$$\neu = u_1 - u'\n$$\n联立解得 $u_1 = \\frac{m_3}{m_1 + m_3}(1 + e)u$。\n在 $m_3$ 与 $m_1$ 碰后, 考察 $m_1$ 和 $m_2$ 系统。质心沿垂直于绳方向的速度大小为 $u_c = \\frac{m_1 u_1 + m_2 u_2}{m_1 + m_2} = \\frac{m_1}{m_1 + m_2} u_1$ (此处利用了 $u_2=0$)。\n小球 $m_1$ 离质心的距离为 $l_1 = \\frac{m_2}{m_1 + m_2} l$。\n因此, 绳的张力 $T$ 满足关系式：\n$$\nT = m_1 \\frac{(u_1 - u_c)^2}{l_1} = m_1 \\frac{(u_1 - u_c)^2}{m_2 l / (m_1 + m_2)}\n$$\n代入 $u_c$ 和 $u_1$ 的表达式, 整理得：\n$$\nT = \\frac{m_1 m_2 m_3^2}{l (m_1 + m_2)(m_1 + m_3)^2} (1+e)^2 u^2\n$$",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】 Let the velocities of $m_3$ and $m_1$ after the collision in the direction perpendicular to the string be $u'$ and $u_1$ respectively. From conservation of momentum and the definition of the coefficient of restitution:\n$$\nm_3 u = m_3 u' + m_1 u_1, \\quad eu = u_1 - u'\n$$\nSolving these gives $u_1 = \\frac{m_3}{m_1 + m_3}(1 + e)u$. After the collision, consider the $m_1-m_2$ system. The velocity of the center of mass perpendicular to the string is $u_c = \\frac{m_1}{m_1 + m_2} u_1$. The distance from $m_1$ to the center of mass is $l_1 = \\frac{m_2}{m_1 + m_2} l$. The tension $T$ provides the centripetal acceleration for the rotation of $m_1$ relative to the center of mass in the center-of-mass frame:\n$$\nT = m_1 \\frac{(u_1 - u_c)^2}{l_1}\n$$\nSubstituting the expressions for $u_c$, $l_1$, and $u_1$ yields:\n$$\nT = \\frac{m_1 m_2 m_3^2}{l (m_1 + m_2)(m_1 + m_3)^2} (1+e)^2 u^2\n$$",
    "img_cn": ["图(a)显示质量为 $m_3$ 的球以速度 $u$ 撞击连接在绳子一端的 $m_1$; 图(b)显示撞击后 $m_1$ 获得垂直速度 $u_1$, $m_3$ 速度变为 $u'$。"],
    "img_en": ["Figure (a) shows ball $m_3$ with velocity $u$ hitting $m_1$ which is attached to a string; Figure (b) shows $m_1$ gaining a perpendicular velocity $u_1$ and $m_3$ changing velocity to $u'$ after impact."],
    "problem_answer": "$T = \\dfrac{m_1 m_2 m_3^2}{l(m_1 + m_2)(m_1 + m_3)^2} (1+e)^2 u^2$",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "3"
  }
  {
    "problem_id": "110",
    "problem_text_cn": "【练习 5-34】有三个质量相等的粒子, 粒子 1 与 粒子 2 中间夹置一个被充分压缩了的轻质弹簧, 并用轻质细线缚在一起 (可视为一个小物体), 静止地放置在光滑水平面上。另一个粒子 3 沿该光滑水平面射向它们。粒子 3 和粒子 1 相碰撞并粘连在一起运动, 之后轻质细线自动崩断, 使弹簧释放, 三个粒子分成两部分: 一部分为粒子 2, 另一部分为粘在一起的粒子 1、3。已知弹簧被充分压缩时的弹性势能为 $E_p$。为了使释放出的粒子 2 的散射角保持在 $30^\circ$ 之内, 求粒子 3 入射时的动能应满足什么条件。\n提示: 此处散射角是指粒子 2 射出后的运动方向与粒子 3 入射时的运动方向之间的夹角。",
    "problem_text_en": "【Exercise 5-34】 Three particles of equal mass are given. Particle 1 and particle 2 have a fully compressed light spring between them and are bound together by a light string (acting as a single object), resting on a smooth horizontal surface. Another particle 3 is projected along the surface towards them. Particle 3 collides with and sticks to particle 1. Subsequently, the string breaks, releasing the spring, and the three particles separate into two parts: particle 2, and the combined particles 1 and 3. The initial elastic potential energy of the compressed spring is $E_p$. To keep the scattering angle of particle 2 within $30^\circ$, what condition must the initial kinetic energy of particle 3 satisfy?\nHint: The scattering angle refers to the angle between the final velocity of particle 2 and the initial velocity of particle 3.",
    "problem_img": [],
    "problem_img_process": ["110_1.png"],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】 当粒子 3 与粒子 1 相碰撞并粘在一起运动, 而轻质细线未崩断之前, 三个粒子的共同速度 $v$ 满足：\n$$\nmv_0 = 3mv \\Rightarrow v = \\frac{1}{3}v_0 \\quad \\text{①}$$\n其中 $v_0$ 为粒子 3 的入射速度。\n三粒子整体经轻质细线自动崩断后, 粒子 2 和粘在一起的粒子 1、3 被分开。在三粒子质心系中讨论此过程。设分离后, 粒子 2 的速率为 $v'_2$, 粘在一起的粒子 1、3 的速率为 $v'_{13}$, 在质心系中满足动量守恒和能量守恒：\n$$\n2mv'_{13} = mv'_2 \\quad \\text{②}$$\n$$\n\\frac{1}{2}(2m)v_{13}'^2 + \\frac{1}{2}mv_2'^2 = E_p \\quad \\text{③}$$\n联立②和③, 消去 $v'_{13}$, 解得 $v'_2$：\n$$\nv'_2 = \\sqrt{\\frac{4E_p}{3m}} \\quad \\text{④}$$\n粒子 2 在原参照系中的速度 $\\vec{v}_2$ 满足：\n$$\n\\vec{v}_2 = \\vec{v} + \\vec{v}'_2 \\quad \\text{⑤}$$\n其中质心速度 $\\vec{v}$ 的方向为粒子 3 的入射方向。为了使释放出的粒子 2 的散射角保持在 $30^\circ$ 之内, 由图 5-练 34 可知：\n$$\n\\sin 30^\circ \ge \\frac{v'_2}{v} = \\frac{3}{v_0} \\sqrt{\\frac{4E_p}{3m}}$$\n解得\n$$\nv_0 \ge \\frac{3}{\\sin 30^\circ} \\sqrt{\\frac{4E_p}{3m}} \\quad \\text{⑥}$$\n粒子 3 入射时的动能满足\n$$\n\\frac{1}{2}mv_0^2 \ge \\frac{1}{2}m \\cdot 36 \\cdot \\frac{4E_p}{3m} = 24E_p \\quad \\text{⑦}$$",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】 Before the string breaks, the common velocity $v$ of the three particles after particle 3 sticks to particle 1 is $mv_0 = 3mv \Rightarrow v = v_0/3$. In the center-of-mass frame after the spring is released, let $v'_2$ be the speed of particle 2 and $v'_{13}$ be the speed of the combined particles 1 and 3. Momentum conservation gives $2mv'_{13} = mv'_2$, and energy conservation gives $m v_{13}'^2 + \frac{1}{2}mv_2'^2 = E_p$. Solving these yields $v'_2 = \sqrt{4E_p/3m}$. In the lab frame, $\vec{v}_2 = \vec{v} + \vec{v}'_2$. To keep the scattering angle within $30^\circ$, the maximum angle occurs when $\vec{v}'_2$ is perpendicular to $\vec{v}_2$, but here the condition for the angle to be $\le 30^\circ$ requires $v \ge v'_2 / \sin 30^\circ$. Substituting $v = v_0/3$, we get $v_0 \ge \frac{3}{\sin 30^\circ}\sqrt{4E_p/3m}$. Thus, the initial kinetic energy $E_{k0} = \frac{1}{2}mv_0^2 \ge 24E_p$.",
    "img_cn": ["图 5-练 34 展示了速度矢量合成关系, $\\vec{v}$ 为质心速度, $\\vec{v}'_2$ 为质心系速度, $\\vec{v}_2$ 为合速度, 散射角为 $30^\circ$。"],
    "img_en": ["Figure 5-Ex 34 shows the velocity vector addition where $\\vec{v}$ is the CM velocity, $\\vec{v}'_2$ is the velocity in the CM frame, $\\vec{v}_2$ is the resultant velocity, and the scattering angle is $30^\circ$."],
    "problem_answer": "粒子 3 入射时的动能应满足 $E_{k0} \ge 24E_p$。",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "4"
  },
  {
    "problem_id": "111",
    "problem_text_cn": "【练习 5-35】质量为 $m$ 的滑块在质量也为 $m$ 的直角盒内可以作无摩擦运动。盒子置于涂有薄油的桌面上, 如图 5-练 35 所示。盒子与桌面间的阻力仅与盒的速度 $v$ 有关, 大小为 $f = -kv, k$ 为正常量。开始时盒静止, 滑块靠左壁以初速度 $v_0$ 向右运动。设盒长 $L$ 比滑块大得多。问滑块与盒子发生多少次碰撞? 设滑块与盒子碰撞是弹性碰撞。",
    "problem_text_en": "【Exercise 5-35】 A slider of mass $m$ can move without friction inside a rectangular box also of mass $m$. The box is placed on a table coated with a thin layer of oil, as shown in Figure 5-Ex 35. The resistance between the box and the table depends only on the box's velocity $v$, given by $f = -kv$ where $k$ is a positive constant. Initially, the box is stationary, and the slider moves from the left wall to the right at an initial velocity $v_0$. Assume the box length $L$ is much larger than the slider. How many collisions occur between the slider and the box? Assume the collisions are elastic.",
    "problem_img": ["111_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】 滑块自左向右运动中, 不受水平方向阻力, 保持速度 $v_0$ 不变, 直抵静止盒右端与盒相碰。由于两者质量相等, 弹性碰撞后交换速度, 滑块静止, 盒以速度 $v_0$ 向右运动。\n盒向右运动, 滑块保持静止。盒运动的牛顿方程为 $m \frac{\Delta v}{\Delta t} = -kv$。改写为 $m \Delta v = -k \Delta x$。在盒左端与滑块相碰前, 盒经历位移 $L$, 设此时盒速度为 $v_1$, 则：\n$$\nv_1 - v_0 = -\frac{k}{m}L \\Rightarrow v_1 = v_0 - \frac{k}{m}L \\quad \\text{④}$$\n然后, 盒左端与滑块碰撞 (第二次相碰), 再次交换速度, 盒静止, 滑块自左向右以速度 $v_1$ 运动。直抵盒右端与盒相碰, 交换速度, 滑块静止, 盒以速度 $v_1$ 向右运动。依相同分析, $v_2$ 满足：\n$$\nv_2 = v_1 - \frac{k}{m}L = v_0 - 2\left(\frac{k}{m}L\right) \\quad \\text{⑤}$$\n如此循环进行, 直到盒右行中与滑块相碰前速度减为零为止。\n由式①知, 若 $v_0 = \frac{k}{m}L$, 则相碰一次; 若 $v_0 = n(\frac{k}{m}L)$, 则碰撞 $(2n-1)$ 次。结论：\n(i) 若 $\frac{mv_0}{kL} = n$ (正整数), 则碰撞次数为 $(\frac{2mv_0}{kL}-1)$ 次;\n(ii) 若 $\frac{mv_0}{kL}$ 不等于正整数, 则碰撞次数为 $(2 \cdot \lceil \frac{mv_0}{kL} \rceil + 1)$ 次。 其中方括号表示取整数部分（注：原文用的是向上取整逻辑）。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】 The slider moves at $v_0$ until it hits the right wall. Since masses are equal and the collision is elastic, they exchange velocities: the slider stops, and the box moves at $v_0$. The box's motion is governed by $m(dv/dt) = -kv$, which implies $m \cdot dv = -k \cdot dx$. Over a displacement $L$, the velocity changes by $\Delta v = -(k/m)L$. Thus, before the second collision (at the left wall), the box velocity is $v_1 = v_0 - (k/m)L$. They exchange velocities again. This process repeats. The number of collisions depends on how many times the velocity can decrease by $(k/m)L$ before reaching zero. If $mv_0/kL = n$ (integer), the total collisions are $2n-1$. If not an integer, the number is $2 \cdot [mv_0/kL] + 1$, where $[\cdot]$ is the floor function.",
    "img_cn": ["图 5-练 35 展示了一个质量为 $m$ 的滑块在长度为 $L$、质量为 $m$ 的盒子中运动, 盒子在有阻力的桌面上。"],
    "img_en": ["Figure 5-Ex 35 shows a slider of mass $m$ inside a box of mass $m$ and length $L$, on a table with resistance."],
    "problem_answer": "若 $\\dfrac{mv_0}{kL}=n$ 为整数, 碰撞 $2n-1$ 次; 否则为 $2[\\dfrac{mv_0}{kL}]+1$ 次。",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "4"
  },
  {
    "problem_id": "112",
    "problem_text_cn": "【例题 5-1】一根长为 $l$ 的轻摆线上端固定于 O 点, 下端悬一小球。在 O 点下方与竖直线偏离 $\phi$ 角, 离 O 点距离为 $a$ 处有一颗固定的钉子 A, 如图 5-例 1 所示。现将摆球在过 OA 的竖直平面内拉离平衡位置, 使摆线与竖直线成 $\theta$ 角, 然后静止释放。当摆线与钉子 A 接触后, 摆球继续运动。假设摆线受钉子阻挡不损失机械能。试讨论摆线被钉子 A 阻挡后, A 与摆球间的摆线不弯曲, $\theta$ 角与 $\phi$ 角应满足什么关系?",
    "problem_text_en": "【Example 5-1】 A light pendulum string of length $l$ is fixed at point O with a small ball at the lower end. A fixed nail A is located at a distance $a$ from O, making an angle $\phi$ with the vertical line, as shown in Figure 5-Ex 1. The ball is pulled in the vertical plane containing OA to an angle $\theta$ from the vertical and released from rest. After the string hits nail A, the ball continues to move. Assuming no mechanical energy loss, discuss the relationship between $\theta$ and $\phi$ such that the string between A and the ball does not slacken (remain taut).",
    "problem_img": ["112_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】 根据题文所述摆线与钉子 A 接触, 必有关系式 $\theta \ge \phi$ (①)。为使摆线不弯曲, 线中张力 $T$ 有条件 $T \ge 0$ (②)。小球摆下, 摆线与钉子 A 接触受阻, 小球将在半径为 $l-a$ 的圆上运动。法向动力学方程为：\n$$\nT - mg \cos\alpha = m \frac{v^2}{l-a} \\quad \\text{③}$$\n其中 $\alpha$ 为摆线摆到与竖直向下成 $\alpha$ 角时小球的速度大小。根据机械能守恒定律, $v$ 还满足：\n$$\nmgl(1 - \cos\theta) = \frac{1}{2}mv^2 + mg[l - a\cos\phi - (l-a)\cos\alpha] \\quad \\text{④}$$\n当小球达到最高点位置 $\alpha \le \frac{\pi}{2}$ 时, 且 $v=0, T \ge 0$ 恒满足。将式①代入整理得：\n$$\nl\cos\theta \ge a\cos\phi \\quad \\text{⑤}$$\n当小球达到的位置 $\alpha > \frac{\pi}{2}$ 时, 为了使摆线不弯曲, 必须达 $\alpha = \pi$。即一旦 $\alpha > \frac{\pi}{2}$, 最高点位置必须达 $\phi = \pi$, 才能使摆线不弯曲。令小球沿圆周运动达到的顶点为 C, $v_c$ 和 $T_c$ 分别为最高点速度和张力, 应有条件：\n$$\nmg + T_c = m \frac{v_c^2}{l-a} \\Rightarrow T_c = \frac{mv_c^2}{l-a} - mg \ge 0 \\Rightarrow v_c^2 \ge g(l-a) \\quad \\text{⑦}$$\n将 $\alpha = \pi$ 代入式④, 可得：\n$$\nl(1 - \cos\theta) \ge \frac{1}{2}(l-a) + (2l - a - a\cos\phi)$$\n化简整理得：\n$$\n\cos\theta \le \frac{a}{l}\cos\phi - \frac{3(l-a)}{2l} \\quad \\text{⑧}$$\n因此, 要求摆线不弯曲, $\theta$ 和 $\phi$ 必须满足的关系是式⑤或式⑧。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】 For the string to hit the nail, $\theta \ge \phi$ (1). To remain taut, $T \ge 0$ (2). The ball moves in a circle of radius $l-a$ after hitting A. The radial equation is $T - mg \cos\alpha = m v^2 / (l-a)$ (3). Energy conservation gives $mgl(1 - \cos\theta) = \frac{1}{2}mv^2 + mg[l - a\cos\phi - (l-a)\cos\alpha]$ (4). If the highest point reached has $\alpha \le \pi/2$, the string is always taut if $v=0$ is reached; this leads to $l\cos\theta \ge a\cos\phi$ (5). If $\alpha > \pi/2$, to prevent slackening, the ball must be able to complete the circle or satisfy $T \ge 0$ at the top ($\alpha = \pi$). At the top, $v_c^2 \ge g(l-a)$. Substituting this into the energy equation with $\alpha = \pi$ gives $\cos\theta \le \frac{a}{l}\cos\phi - \frac{3(l-a)}{2l}$ (8). The conditions are (5) or (8).",
    "img_cn": ["图 5-例 1 展示了一个摆长为 $l$ 的摆, 钉子 A 位于 O 点下方 $a$ 处, 偏角为 $\phi$, 摆球初始偏角为 $\theta$。"],
    "img_en": ["Figure 5-Ex 1 shows a pendulum of length $l$ with a nail A at distance $a$ from O and angle $\phi$. The initial angle of the ball is $\theta$."],
    "problem_answer": "关系式为 $l\cos\theta \ge a\cos\phi$ 或 $\cos\theta \le \dfrac{a}{l}\cos\phi - \dfrac{3(l-a)}{2l}$。",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "3"
  }
  {
    "problem_id": "113",
    "problem_text_cn": "【例题 5-2】水平桌面有一半径为 $R$ 的固定光滑圆环形轨道, 在距圆心 $R/2$ 处开有小孔 Q。轻质弹性绳一端固定在孔正下方固定点 P, 绳的劲度系数为 $k$, 绳的自由长度等于 $\\overline{QP}$。将绳的另一端穿过小孔 Q, 拉到桌面上, 在端点系一质量为 $m$ 的小球, 并将小球嵌在圆形轨道内, 使其在轨道内可以无摩擦地运动。设初始时小球在与孔距离为 $R/2$ 的轨道上, 且初速为 $v_0$, 如图 5-例 2(a)所示。\n1) 为使小球能绕圆轨道连续不断地运动, 试求 $v_0$ 满足的条件;\n2) 假设所取 $v_0$ 值, 刚好小球不能完成绕圆轨道运动 (即, 若稍大于此值, 小球就能完成圆运动), 小球将停在何处? 小球受圆环形轨道的支持力 $N$, 在何处 $N > 0, N = 0$ 和 $N < 0$? 假设 $N$ 的方向以圆环径向向外为正, 小球的位置用孔 Q 至环上点的距离 $r$ 表示。",
    "problem_text_en": "【Example 5-2】 A fixed smooth circular track of radius $R$ is on a horizontal table, with a small hole Q at a distance $R/2$ from the center. One end of a light elastic string is fixed at point P directly below the hole, with stiffness coefficient $k$ and natural length equal to $\\overline{QP}$. The other end passes through Q and is attached to a ball of mass $m$ constrained to move frictionlessly within the track. Initially, the ball is at a point on the track at distance $R/2$ from Q with initial velocity $v_0$, as shown in Fig. 5-Ex 2(a).\n1) Find the condition for $v_0$ such that the ball can move continuously around the track.\n2) If $v_0$ is such that the ball just fails to complete the circle, where will it stop? Determine the positions where the track's normal force $N$ is $N > 0, N = 0$, and $N < 0$, using distance $r$ from Q to describe the ball's position (outward radial direction is positive).",
    "problem_img": ["113_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1) 小球在圆环轨道上运动时, 只有弹性力做功, 系统机械能守恒。设孔 Q 到小球距离为 $r$, 桌面上的绳长即为伸长量。有关系：\n$$\\frac{1}{2} m v_0^2 + \\frac{1}{2} k \\left(\\frac{R}{2}\\right)^2 = \\frac{1}{2} m v^2 + \\frac{1}{2} k r^2$$\n得 $v^2$ 表达式。为使小球能绕轨道连续运动, 在 $r$ 取最大值 $3R/2$ 时 (孔的对端), 应有 $v > 0$, 即：\n$$\\frac{1}{2} m v_0^2 + \\frac{1}{2} k \\left(\\frac{R}{2}\\right)^2 - \\frac{1}{2} k \\left(\\frac{3}{2} R\\right)^2 > 0$$\n解得 $v_0 > \\sqrt{\\frac{2k}{m}} R$。\n2) 若取临界值 $v_0 = \\sqrt{\\frac{2k}{m}} R$, 小球在 $r = \\frac{3}{2} R$ 处速度为零, 且法向和切向加速度均为零, 故小球将停在 $r = \\frac{3}{2} R$ 处。\n法向动力学方程为 $f \\cos\\varphi - N = m \\frac{v^2}{R}$, 其中 $f = kr$。利用余弦定理 $r \\cos\\varphi = \\frac{r^2}{2R} + \\frac{3}{8} R$, 代入整理得：\n$$N = \\frac{3k}{2R} \\left( r^2 - \\frac{5}{4} R^2 \\right)$$\n由此得出：\n当 $\\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{2} R < r \\le \\frac{3}{2} R$ 时, $N > 0$;\n当 $r = \\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{2} R$ 时, $N = 0$;\n当 $\\frac{R}{2} \\le r < \\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{2} R$ 时, $N < 0$。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】\n1) The system is conservative. Let $r$ be the distance from Q. Conservation of energy: $\\frac{1}{2}mv_0^2 + \\frac{1}{8}kR^2 = \\frac{1}{2}mv^2 + \\frac{1}{2}kr^2$. To complete the circle, $v > 0$ at the furthest point $r = 3R/2$. Solving gives $v_0 > \\sqrt{2k/m}R$.\n2) At $v_0 = \\sqrt{2k/m}R$, the ball stops at $r = 3R/2$. Using the normal force equation $f \\cos\\varphi - N = mv^2/R$ and the law of cosines $r \\cos\\varphi = r^2/2R + 3R/8$, we derive $N = \\frac{3k}{2R}(r^2 - 5R^2/4)$. \n- $N > 0$ for $\\sqrt{5}R/2 < r \\le 3R/2$;\n- $N = 0$ for $r = \\sqrt{5}R/2$;\n- $N < 0$ for $R/2 \\le r < \\sqrt{5}R/2$.",
    "img_cn": ["图(a)为实验装置俯视图, 显示小球在轨道上及下方固定点 P; 图(b)为受力分析图, 标注了支持力 $N$、弹性力 $f$ 及几何关系。"],
    "img_en": ["Figure (a) is the top view showing the ball on the track and fixed point P; Figure (b) is the force analysis diagram showing normal force $N$, elastic force $f$, and geometric relations."],
    "problem_answer": "1) $v_0 > \\sqrt{\\dfrac{2k}{m}} R$; 2) 停在 $r = \\dfrac{3}{2} R$ 处; $N=0$ 位于 $r = \\dfrac{\\sqrt{5}}{2} R$ 处。",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "3"
  },
  {
    "problem_id": "114",
    "problem_text_cn": "【例题 5-3】质量为 $m$、长度为 $2\\pi R$ 的细柔绳, 一端系在半径为 $R$ 的轻轮边缘上的 A 点, 绳紧绕在该轮上, 正好绕满一圈, 两端点交于 A 点。轻轮可绕过中心 $o$ 的水平光滑轴转动。\n1) 初始时, $o$ 与 A 的连线在水平方位, 由于绳的自由端 A' 有一无限小段自由悬挂, 使轻轮由静止开始转动, 同时绳的自由端部分逐渐松开, 如图 5-例 3(a) 所示。试求 A 点转过角 $\\theta_0$ 时轮的角速度。\n2) 若锁定 1) 中末态位移, 即 A 点转过角 $\\theta_0$, 并使轮保持静止不转动, 试求绳在最高点 D 处绳中张力多大?",
    "problem_text_en": "【Example 5-3】 A flexible rope of mass $m$ and length $2\\pi R$ has one end tied to point A on the edge of a light wheel of radius $R$. The rope is wound exactly once around the wheel. The wheel rotates around a smooth horizontal axis through its center $o$.\n1) Initially, $oA$ is horizontal. Due to an infinitesimal free-hanging segment at the free end A', the wheel starts rotating from rest, and the rope gradually unwinds, as shown in Fig. 5-Ex 3(a). Find the angular velocity of the wheel when A has rotated by angle $\\theta_0$.\n2) If the system is locked at the position where A has rotated by $\\theta_0$ and the wheel is kept stationary, what is the tension in the rope at the highest point D?",
    "problem_img": ["114_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1) 只有重力做功, 利用动能定理。松开部分长度为 $R\\theta_0$, 其重心下降高度的计算是关键。通过积分（元法）求得未松开圆弧段重心高度后, 结合下垂段重心位移, 重力功为：\n$$A = \\frac{mgR}{4\\pi}(\\theta_0^2 + 2\\cos\\theta_0 - 2)$$\n设轮角速度为 $\\omega$, 整个绳子动能增量为 $\\Delta E_k = \\frac{1}{2}m(R\\omega)^2$。由动能定理：\n$$\\omega = \\sqrt{\\frac{g}{2\\pi R}(\\theta_0^2 + 2\\cos\\theta_0 - 2)}$$\n2) 求 D 点张力。设想在 D 处切断绳, 考察 $DBA'$ 部分。对轮轴 $o$ 的力矩平衡方程：\n$RT = M_1 + M_2$, 其中 $M_1$ 为 $DB$ 段重力力矩, $M_2$ 为 $BA'$ 下垂段重力力矩。\n通过微元法求得：$M_1 = \\frac{mgR}{2\\pi}$, $M_2 = \\frac{m\\theta_0 gR}{2\\pi}$。\n代入方程解得：$T = \\frac{mg}{2\\pi}(1 + \\theta_0)$。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】\n1) Only gravity does work. The length of the unwound part is $R\\theta_0$. Using integration to find the center of mass shift, the work done by gravity is $A = \\frac{mgR}{4\\pi}(\\theta_0^2 + 2\\cos\\theta_0 - 2)$. The kinetic energy of the rope is $\\frac{1}{2}m(R\\omega)^2$. Applying the work-energy theorem: $\\omega = \\sqrt{\\frac{g}{2\\pi R}(\\theta_0^2 + 2\\cos\\theta_0 - 2)}$.\n2) To find the tension at D, consider the torque equilibrium for segment $DBA'$. $RT = M_{DB} + M_{BA'}$. Using integration, $M_{DB} = \\frac{mgR}{2\\pi}$ and $M_{BA'} = \\frac{m\\theta_0 gR}{2\\pi}$. Thus, $T = \\frac{mg}{2\\pi}(1 + \\theta_0)$.",
    "img_cn": ["图(a)显示初始状态及转动 $\\theta_0$ 后的形状; 图(b)展示求重心位置的元法示意; 图(c)用于分析 D 点张力, 标出了切断点 D。"],
    "img_en": ["Fig(a) shows initial state and state after rotating $\\theta_0$; Fig(b) illustrates the infinitesimal method for CM; Fig(c) is for tension analysis at D."],
    "problem_answer": "1) $\\omega = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{g}{2\\pi R}(\\theta_0^2 + 2\\cos\\theta_0 - 2)}$; 2) $T = \\dfrac{mg}{2\\pi}(1 + \\theta_0)$。",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "4"
  },
  {
    "problem_id": "115",
    "problem_text_cn": "【例题 5-4】大质量车厢在水平地面上以 $v_0$ 速度匀速行驶, 车厢内有一半径为 $R$ 的固定光滑半圆柱面, 顶部有一质量为 $m$ 的物块, 开始时滑块静止, 如图 5-例 4(a) 所示, 后因扰动在图示平面内下滑, 直到离开圆柱面。试求在此过程中圆柱面支持力对物块所做的功 $W$。",
    "problem_text_en": "【Example 5-4】 A massive carriage moves at a constant speed $v_0$ on a horizontal ground. Inside the carriage is a fixed smooth semi-cylindrical surface of radius $R$. A block of mass $m$ is initially at rest at the top, as shown in Fig. 5-Ex 4(a). Due to a disturbance, it slides down until it leaves the surface. Find the work $W$ done by the normal force of the cylindrical surface on the block during this process.",
    "problem_img": ["115_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】 在车厢参考系中, 支持力垂直于位移不做功。但在地面系中, 位移方向改变, 支持力做功。利用功能原理：$W = \\Delta E_k + \\Delta E_p$。\n在车厢参考系中, 机械能守恒：$mgR(1-\\cos\\theta) = \\frac{1}{2}mv'^2$; 离开瞬间法向动力学方程 $mg\\cos\\theta = mv'^2/R$。联立得 $\\cos\\theta = 2/3, v' = \\sqrt{\\frac{2}{3}gR}$。\n(i) 若物块向右滑, 地面系末速度 $v_G^2 = v_0^2 + v'^2 + 2v_0 v'\\cos\\theta$。代入功能原理：\n$W_1 = \\frac{1}{2}mv_G^2 - \\frac{1}{2}mv_0^2 - mgR(1-\\cos\\theta) = \\frac{2}{3}\\sqrt{\\frac{2}{3}gR} \\cdot mv_0$。\n(ii) 若物块向左滑, 速度合成中余弦项变负, 同理得 $W_2 = -\\frac{2}{3}\\sqrt{\\frac{2}{3}gR} \\cdot mv_0$。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】 In the carriage frame, the normal force does no work. In the ground frame, it does work $W = \\Delta E_k + \\Delta E_p$. In the carriage frame, the block leaves at $\\cos\\theta = 2/3$ with relative speed $v' = \\sqrt{2gR/3}$. \n(i) Sliding right: $v_G^2 = v_0^2 + v'^2 + 2v_0 v'\\cos\\theta$. Using the work-energy theorem: $W_1 = \\frac{2}{3}\\sqrt{\\frac{2}{3}gR} \\cdot mv_0$. \n(ii) Sliding left: $v_G^2 = v_0^2 + v'^2 - 2v_0 v'\\cos\\theta$. Similarly, $W_2 = -\\frac{2}{3}\\sqrt{\\frac{2}{3}gR} \\cdot mv_0$.",
    "img_cn": ["图(a)物块在匀速行驶车厢内的圆柱顶端; 图(b)展示了向右和向左下滑时的速度合成矢量图。"],
    "img_en": ["Fig(a) block at the top inside a moving carriage; Fig(b) velocity vector addition for sliding right and left."],
    "problem_answer": "$W = \\pm \\dfrac{2}{3}\\sqrt{\\dfrac{2}{3}gR} \\cdot mv_0$",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "3"
  },
  {
    "problem_id": "116",
    "problem_text_cn": "【例题 5-5】水平地面上整齐堆放着三个质量分布均匀、长度相等、半径均为 $r$ 的圆柱体, 如图 5-例 5(a) 所示。设图中三个圆柱体 A、B、C 的质量分别为 $m_A = 2m_B = 2m_C = 2m$。\n1) 设所有接触面的静摩擦系数均为 $\\mu$, 试确定保持图中位形所需的最小 $\\mu$ 值;\n2) 若 $\\mu = 0$, 即忽略所有接触面的摩擦时, 从图中位形静止释放, 求柱 A 落地时的速度。",
    "problem_text_en": "【Example 5-5】 Three uniform cylinders of equal length and radius $r$ are stacked on the ground as shown in Fig. 5-Ex 5(a). The masses are $m_A = 2m, m_B = m, m_C = m$.\n1) If all contact surfaces have a static friction coefficient $\\mu$, find the minimum $\\mu$ to maintain equilibrium.\n2) If $\\mu = 0$, find the velocity of cylinder A when it hits the ground after being released from rest.",
    "problem_img": ["116_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1) 临界状态下, A 与 C 接触处 P 先达临界, 即 $f_1 = \\mu N_1$。利用整体竖直受力平衡 $2N_2 = (m_A+m_B+m_C)g = 4mg$ 得 $N_2=2mg$。对 C 柱利用力矩平衡和受力分析, 联立 $\\theta=30^\\circ$, 解得 $\\mu = 2 - \\sqrt{3}$。\n2) 机械能守恒。系统动能为 $\\frac{1}{2}m_A v_A^2 + \\frac{1}{2}m_B v_B^2 + \\frac{1}{2}m_C v_C^2$。根据对称性 $v_B = v_C$。由于 A、B 接触, 沿连线速度相等: $v_A \\cos\\theta = v_B \\sin\\theta$。分离临界点满足法向加速度关系, 解得分离时 $\\cos\\theta = \\sqrt{3}/3$。之后 A 自由下落, 再次利用机械能守恒解得落地速度 $v'_A = \\frac{4}{3}\\sqrt{\\sqrt{3}gr} \\approx 1.75\\sqrt{gr}$。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】\n1) At the limit, $f_1 = \\mu N_1$ at point P. Total vertical equilibrium: $2N_2 = 4mg \\Rightarrow N_2 = 2mg$. From torque and force balance on C with $\\theta=30^\\circ$, we find $\\mu = 2 - \\sqrt{3}$.\n2) Energy conservation: $m_A gh_2 = \\frac{1}{2}m_A v_A^2 + m_B v_B^2$. Constraint: $v_A \\cos\\theta = v_B \\sin\\theta$. Separation occurs when $2gr \\cos\\theta = v_A^2 / \\sin^2\\theta$, yielding $\\cos\\theta = \\sqrt{3}/3$. After separation, A falls freely. Final velocity $v'_A = \\frac{4}{3}\\sqrt{\\sqrt{3}gr}$.",
    "img_cn": ["图(a)三圆柱堆放位形; 图(b)临界摩擦受力分析图; 图(c)运动过程中的速度矢量与角度关系。"],
    "img_en": ["Fig(a) stacking configuration; Fig(b) force analysis for limit friction; Fig(c) velocity vectors and angles during motion."],
    "problem_answer": "1) $\\mu = 2 - \\sqrt{3}$; 2) $v'_A \\approx 1.75\\sqrt{gr}$。",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "5"
  },
  {
    "problem_id": "117",
    "problem_text_cn": "【例题 5-6】质量分别为 $m_1$ 和 $m_2$ 的两物块用橡皮绳相连放在水平台面上, 橡皮绳原长为 $a$, 当它伸长时, 如同一个弹性系数为 $k$ 的弹簧。物块与台面间的摩擦系数为 $\\mu$。今将两物块拉开至相距 $b$ ($b>a$) 静止释放, 如图 5-例 6 所示。求两物块相碰时的相对速度大小。",
    "problem_text_en": "【Example 5-6】 Two blocks of masses $m_1$ and $m_2$ are connected by an elastic rope on a table. The rope's natural length is $a$, and it acts as a spring with constant $k$ when stretched. The coefficient of friction is $\\mu$. They are released from rest at a distance $b$ ($b>a$). Find their relative velocity when they collide.",
    "problem_img": ["117_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n方法一: 动力学方程。写出两物块的牛顿第二定律方程, 相减得出相对加速度 $a_r$ 关于相对距离 $y$ 的方程。利用 $a_r = v_r \\frac{dv_r}{dy}$ 进行积分。积分区间从 $y=b$ 到 $y=a$ (绳缩回原长), 之后绳不再施力, 只有摩擦力。最终解得相碰相对速度 $v_r = \\sqrt{\\frac{k(m_1+m_2)}{m_1 m_2}(b-a)^2 - 4\\mu gb}$。\n方法二: 质心系分析。在质心系中, 摩擦力作为外力做功。动能定理 $\\frac{1}{2}\\mu v_r^2 = \\frac{1}{2}k(b-a)^2 - \\mu m_1 g l_1 - \\mu m_2 g l_2$, 其中 $l_i$ 为位移。结合 $m_1 l_1 = m_2 l_2$ 和 $l_1+l_2=b$, 解得相同结果。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】\nMethod 1: Equations of motion. Subtracting Newton's equations for $m_1$ and $m_2$ gives relative acceleration $a_r$ vs $y$. Integrating $v_r dv_r = a_r dy$ from $b$ to $a$ (rope slackens) and then considering friction only until collision gives $v_r = \\sqrt{\\frac{k(m_1+m_2)}{m_1 m_2}(b-a)^2 - 4\\mu gb}$.\nMethod 2: Center-of-mass frame. Using the work-energy theorem in the CM frame where friction does work over segments $l_1, l_2$. With $m_1 l_1 = m_2 l_2$ and $l_1+l_2=b$, the same result is obtained.",
    "img_cn": ["图 5-例 6 显示两物块在坐标轴 $x$ 上的位置 $x_1, x_2$ 及相距 $b$ 的初始状态。"],
    "img_en": ["Fig 5-Ex 6 shows positions $x_1, x_2$ on axis $x$ and the initial distance $b$."],
    "problem_answer": "$v_r = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{k(m_1+m_2)}{m_1 m_2}(b-a)^2 - 4\\mu gb}$",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
