    "problem_id": "118",
    "problem_text_cn": "【例题 5-7】 $N$ 个相同的、质量均为 $m$ 的小滑块排成一行, 静止在光滑的水平面上, 各滑块间有间距。现有一质量为 $M(M > m)$ 的大滑块以速度 $u$ 从左方沿 $N$ 个滑块的联线射向滑块, 并与之正碰。假设滑块间的碰撞皆为完全弹性碰撞, 试求所有滑块的最终速度。",
    "problem_text_en": "【Example 5-7】 $N$ identical small blocks, each of mass $m$, are arranged in a row resting on a smooth horizontal surface with gaps between them. A large block of mass $M (M > m)$ moves from the left with velocity $u$ along the line of the $N$ blocks and undergoes a head-on collision. Assuming all collisions between blocks are perfectly elastic, find the final velocities of all the blocks.",
    "problem_img": [],
