    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】 先从总体上加以分析, 然后写出各滑块最终速度的表达式。设自左至右给小滑块编号: $1, 2, 3, \\cdots, N$。设大滑块 $M$ 与第一个小滑块碰撞后速度分别为 $V_1, v_1$。因 $M > m$, 有 $V_1 > 0$, 大滑块仍向前运动。但 $v_1 > V_1$, 所以第一块小滑块将与第 2 块小滑块相碰, 因小滑块质量均为 $m$, 结果交换速度, 第 1 块小滑块静止, 第 2 块小滑块将以 $v_1$ 前进; 继而与第 3 块小滑块碰撞, 第 2 块小滑块静止, 第 3 块小滑块以 $v_1$ 速度前进 $\\cdots\\cdots$; 依此, 把速度 $v_1$ 传至第 $N$ 块小滑块, 而其它小滑块均回复静止。在此过程中, 有可能大滑块 $M$ 已经与第 1 块小滑块再次相碰, 设碰后 $M$ 的速度为 $V_2$, 第 1 块小滑块速度为 $v_2$。同理, $v_2$ 速度将一直传给第 $N-1$ 块小滑块。依此计算, $N$ 块小滑块的速度分别为:\n第 $N$ 块: $v_1 = \\frac{2M}{M+m}u$\n第 $N-1$ 块: $v_2 = \\frac{2M}{M+m} \\left( \\frac{M-m}{M+m} \\right) u$\n第 1 块: $v_N = \\frac{2M}{M+m} \\left( \\frac{M-m}{M+m} \\right)^{N-1} u$\n大滑块最终速度为: $V_N = \\left( \\frac{M-m}{M+m} \\right)^N u$。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】 Analyze the overall process and express final velocities. Let blocks be $1, 2, \\dots, N$. After $M$ hits block 1, velocities are $V_1, v_1$. Since $M > m$, $V_1 > 0$. Since $v_1 > V_1$, block 1 hits block 2, exchanging velocities so block 1 stops and block 2 moves at $v_1$. This continues until block $N$ moves at $v_1$. Meanwhile, $M$ may hit block 1 again, sending a new velocity $v_2$ down the line to block $N-1$. Following this iteration, the final velocities are:\nBlock $N$: $v_1 = \\frac{2M}{M+m}u$\nBlock $N-1$: $v_2 = \\frac{2M}{M+m} \\left( \\frac{M-m}{M+m} \\right) u$\nBlock 1: $v_N = \\frac{2M}{M+m} \\left( \\frac{M-m}{M+m} \\right)^{N-1} u$\nFinal velocity of $M$: $V_N = \\left( \\frac{M-m}{M+m} \\right)^N u$.",
