  {
    "problem_id": "122",
    "problem_text_cn": "【例题 5-11】 有一个质量及线度足够大的水平板, 它绕垂直于水平板的竖直轴以匀角速度 $\\omega$ 旋转。在板的上方 $h$ 处有一群相同的小球 (视为质点), 它们以板的转轴为中心、$R$ 为半径均匀地在水平面内排成一个圆周。现让这些小球同时从静止状态开始自由落下, 设每个球与平板发生碰撞的时间非常短, 而且碰撞前后小球在竖直方向上速度的大小不变, 仅是方向反向; 而在水平方向则会发生滑动摩擦, 摩擦系数为 $\\mu$。\n1) 试求这些小球第 2 次和第 1 次与平板碰撞时小球线密度比值 $v_1$;\n2) 如果 $R < \\mu g/\\omega^2$ ($g$ 为重力加速度), 且 $v_1 = 1/\\sqrt{2}$, 试求这群小球第 3 次与第 1 次与平板碰撞时的小球线密度之比值 $v_2$。",
    "problem_text_en": "【Example 5-11】 A horizontal plate of sufficient size rotates with constant angular velocity $\\omega$ about a vertical axis. A group of identical small balls (treated as particles) are arranged in a circle of radius $R$ at a height $h$ above the plate, centered on the axis. They are released from rest simultaneously. The collision time is very short, the vertical velocity reverses its direction with unchanged magnitude, and sliding friction occurs in the horizontal direction with coefficient $\\mu$.\n1) Find the ratio of the linear densities of the balls at the 2nd and 1st collisions, $v_1$.\n2) If $R < \\mu g/\\omega^2$ and $v_1 = 1/\\sqrt{2}$, find the ratio of the linear densities at the 3rd and 1st collisions, $v_2$.",
    "problem_img": ["122_1.png"],
    "problem_img_process": [],
    "problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1) 小球第 1 次碰前竖直速度 $v_0 = \\sqrt{2gh}$。碰后竖直速度仍为 $v_0$, 水平受摩擦力 $f = \\mu N$。由动量定理 $N\\Delta t = 2mv_0$, 水平获得速度 $v_1 = 2\\mu v_0$。第 2 次碰撞时小球构成的圆半径 $R_1 = \\sqrt{R^2 + L_1^2}$, 其中水平射程 $L_1 = 2v_1 \\sqrt{2h/g} = 8\\mu h$。密度比 $v_1 = \\frac{R}{R_1} = 1/\\sqrt{1+(8\\mu h/R)^2}$。\n2) 根据 $v_1 = 1/\\sqrt{2}$ 和 $R < \\mu g/\\omega^2$ 的条件, 判定小球在第 2 次碰撞结束前已处于相对静止状态。因此第 2 次碰后水平速度变为板的速度 $v_2 = \\omega R_1$。计算第 3 次相碰时的半径 $R_2 = 2R$。最终线密度比值 $v_2 = \\frac{R}{R_2} = \\frac{1}{2}$。",
    "problem_solution_en": "【Analysis & Solution】\n1) Vertical velocity before the 1st collision is $v_0 = \\sqrt{2gh}$. After the collision, the impulse $N\Delta t = 2mv_0$ and horizontal velocity $v_1 = 2\\mu v_0$. The radius for the 2nd collision is $R_1 = \\sqrt{R^2 + L_1^2}$ with $L_1 = 8\\mu h$. The density ratio is $v_1 = R/R_1$.\n2) Given $v_1 = 1/\\sqrt{2}$ and $R < \\mu g/\\omega^2$, the balls reach relative rest during the 2nd collision. Thus, the horizontal velocity after the 2nd collision is the plate's velocity $v_2 = \\omega R_1$. The radius for the 3rd collision is $R_2 = 2R$. The density ratio is $v_2 = R/R_2 = 1/2$.",
    "img_cn": ["图 5-例 11 展示了小球运动的速度矢量图和几何半径关系图。"],
    "img_en": ["Fig 5-Ex 11 shows velocity vector diagrams and geometric radius relationships of the balls' motion."],
    "problem_answer": "1) $v_1 = 1/\\sqrt{1+(8\\mu h/R)^2}$ (当 $2\\mu\\sqrt{2gh} < \\omega R$); 2) $v_2 = 1/2$。",
    "problem_tags": ["Mechanics"],
    "difficulty": "6"
  }
