{
"problem_id": "141",
"problem_text_cn": "【141】一物自地面以第一宇宙速度竖直上抛，达最高点后返回地面上的抛掷点，求此物运动的时间。已知地球半径$R_e=6400$公里，设此过程中地球静止不动。",
"problem_text_en": "[141] An object is projected vertically upward from Earth's surface at the first cosmic velocity, reaching a maximum height and returning to the launch point. Find the total time of flight. Earth's radius $R_e=6400 \\text{ km}$, assume Earth is stationary.",
"problem_img": ["141_1.png", "141_2.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["141_3.png"],
"img_cn": ["退化椭圆轨道示意图（图141_1）；运动时间推导（图141_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Degenerate elliptical orbit diagram (Figure 141_1); derivation of flight time (Figure 141_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】利用引力场机械能守恒和第一宇宙速度$v_1 = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{GM_e}{R_e}}$，得最大高度$h = R_e$。运动路径可视为半长轴$a=R_e$的退化椭圆，其极限周期与近地圆轨道周期相同：\n$$T_0 = 2\\pi\\sqrt{\\dfrac{R_e}{g}}$$\n由开普勒第二定律，矢径扫过面积与时间成正比，总时间为：\n$$t = T_0\\left(\\dfrac{1}{2} + \\dfrac{1}{\\pi}\\right) = (\\pi + 2)\\sqrt{\\dfrac{R_e}{g}} \\approx 4.12 \\times 10^3 \\text{ s}$$\n",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] Using conservation of mechanical energy and the first cosmic velocity $v_1 = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{GM_e}{R_e}}$, the maximum height is $h = R_e$. The trajectory is a degenerate ellipse with semi-major axis $a=R_e$, whose period equals that of a low Earth orbit:\n$$T_0 = 2\\pi\\sqrt{\\dfrac{R_e}{g}}$$\nBy Kepler's second law, the total flight time is:\n$$t = (\\pi + 2)\\sqrt{\\dfrac{R_e}{g}} \\approx 4.12 \\times 10^3 \\text{ s}$$\n",
"problem_answer": "运动时间约为$4.12 \\times 10^3 \\text{ s}$（约68.7分钟）。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "142",
"problem_text_cn": "【142】一个质量为$M$、半径为$R$的星球以速度$V$通过质量密度为$\\rho$的非常稀薄的气体，如图142_1所示。由于它的引力场，此星球将吸引迎面接近它的粒子，并俘获撞在它表面上的所有气体分子。设相对于速度$V$，原子的热运动速度可以忽略，原子间的相互作用不计。求作用在星体上的阻力。",
"problem_text_en": "[142] A star of mass $M$ and radius $R$ moves at speed $V$ through a dilute gas of density $\\rho$. Its gravitational field captures gas molecules colliding with its surface. Neglect thermal motion and interatomic forces. Find the drag force on the star.",
"problem_img": ["142_1.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["142_2.png"],
"img_cn": ["星体与气体分子相互作用示意图（图142_1）。"],
"img_en": ["Interaction between star and gas molecules (Figure 142_1)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】在星体参考系中，气体分子以速度$-V$入射。由角动量守恒$vR = Vb$和机械能守恒$\\dfrac{1}{2}v^2 - \\dfrac{GM}{R} = \\dfrac{1}{2}V^2$，解得最大瞄准距离：\n$$b = \\sqrt{R^2 + \\dfrac{2GMR}{V^2}}$$\n单位时间俘获的动量即为阻力：\n$$f = \\pi\\rho V^2\\left(R^2 + \\dfrac{2GMR}{V^2}\\right) = \\pi R^2\\rho\\left(V^2 + \\dfrac{2GM}{R}\\right)$$\n",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] In the star's frame, gas molecules approach at speed $-V$. Using angular momentum and energy conservation, the maximum impact parameter is:\n$$b = \\sqrt{R^2 + \\dfrac{2GMR}{V^2}}$$\nThe drag force equals the momentum captured per unit time:\n$$f = \\pi R^2\\rho\\left(V^2 + \\dfrac{2GM}{R}\\right)$$\n",
"problem_answer": "星体受到的阻力为$f = \\pi R^2\\rho\\left(V^2 + \\dfrac{2GM}{R}\\right)$。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "143",
"problem_text_cn": "【143】质量为$M$的宇航站和对接上的质量为$m$的飞船沿圆形轨道围绕地球运动着，其轨道半径是地球半径的$n=1.25$倍。某瞬时，飞船从宇航站沿运动方向射出后沿椭圆圆轨道运动，其最远点到地心的距离为$8nR$。问飞船与宇航站的质量比$\\dfrac{m}{M}$为何值时，飞船绕地球运行一周后正好与宇航站相遇。",
"problem_text_en": "[143] A space station of mass $M$ and a docked spacecraft of mass $m$ orbit Earth in a circular path of radius $nR$ ($n=1.25$, $R$ is Earth's radius). The spacecraft is ejected forward, entering an elliptical orbit with apogee $8nR$. Find the mass ratio $\\dfrac{m}{M}$ such that the spacecraft meets the station after one orbit.",
"problem_img": ["143_1.png", "143_2.png", "143_3.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["143_4.png"],
"img_cn": ["轨道分离示意图（图143_1）；椭圆轨道参数（图143_2）；质量比推导（图143_3）。"],
"img_en": ["Orbital separation diagram (Figure 143_1); elliptical orbit parameters (Figure 143_2); mass ratio derivation (Figure 143_3)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】分离前共同速度$u = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{GM_\\oplus}{nR}}$。动量守恒：\n$$(M+m)u = Mv + mV$$\n飞船椭圆半长轴$a_2 = \\dfrac{9}{2}nR$，宇航站椭圆半长轴$a_1 = \\dfrac{nR + r}{2}$。由开普勒第三定律$\\left(\\dfrac{T_1}{T_2}\\right)^2 = \\left(\\dfrac{a_1}{a_2}\\right)^3$，结合相遇条件$T_2 = kT_1$（$k$为正整数），解得$k=10$或$11$，对应质量比：\n$$\\dfrac{m}{M} = 3 - \\sqrt{2(9 - k^{2/3})}$$\n代入$k=10$得$\\dfrac{m}{M} \\approx 0.048$，$k=11$得$\\dfrac{m}{M} \\approx 0.153$。",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] The initial common speed is $u = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{GM_\\oplus}{nR}}$. Conservation of momentum:\n$$(M+m)u = Mv + mV$$\nThe spacecraft's elliptical semi-major axis is $a_2 = \\dfrac{9}{2}nR$, and the station's is $a_1 = \\dfrac{nR + r}{2}$. By Kepler's third law and the meeting condition $T_2 = kT_1$, we find $k=10$ or $11$, giving:\n$$\\dfrac{m}{M} = 3 - \\sqrt{2(9 - k^{2/3})}$$\nFor $k=10$, $\\dfrac{m}{M} \\approx 0.048$; for $k=11$, $\\dfrac{m}{M} \\approx 0.153$.",
"problem_answer": "飞船与宇航站的质量比约为$0.048$或$0.153$。",
"difficulty": "4",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "144",
"problem_text_cn": "【144】假设宇宙空间中远离其它星体有两质点$A$和$B$，它们的质量分别为$m$和$M$。开始时，$A$和$B$相距为$l_0$，相对于某惯性系，$A$静止，$B$以初速$v_0$沿$AB$连线方向运动。为维持$B$的速度不变，应对$B$施加一个沿着其运动方向的外力$F$，如图144_1所示。1)试求$A$、$B$间距离最大时，外力$F$的值；2)计算从开始到$AB$距离最大时，变力$F$做的功。",
"problem_text_en": "[144] Two particles $A$ (mass $m$) and $B$ (mass $M$) are isolated in space, initially separated by $l_0$. $A$ is stationary, and $B$ moves at $v_0$ along the line connecting them. An external force $F$ maintains $B$'s speed. (1) Find $F$ when the distance between $A$ and $B$ is maximized. (2) Find the work done by $F$ up to that point.",
"problem_img": ["144_1.png", "144_2.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["144_3.png"],
"img_cn": ["质点相对运动示意图（图144_1）；能量与力的推导（图144_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Relative motion of particles (Figure 144_1); derivation of energy and force (Figure 144_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】1) 在$B$的参考系中，$A$以速度$v_0$远离，当距离最大时$A$的速度为零。由机械能守恒：\n$$\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2 - \\dfrac{GMm}{l_0} = -\\dfrac{GMm}{l_m}$$\n解得最大距离$l_m = \\dfrac{2l_0GM}{2GM - l_0v_0^2}$。此时外力$F$等于引力：\n$$F = \\dfrac{GMm}{l_m^2} = \\dfrac{(2GM - l_0v_0^2)^2m}{4G^2Ml_0^2}$$\n\n2) 由功能原理，功$W$等于系统机械能的增量：\n$$W = \\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2 + GMm\\left(\\dfrac{1}{l_0} - \\dfrac{1}{l_m}\\right) = mv_0^2$$\n",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] 1) In $B$'s frame, $A$ moves away at $v_0$. At maximum separation, $A$'s velocity is zero. Using energy conservation:\n$$\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_0^2 - \\dfrac{GMm}{l_0} = -\\dfrac{GMm}{l_m} \\implies l_m = \\dfrac{2l_0GM}{2GM - l_0v_0^2}$$\nThe force $F$ equals the gravitational force at this distance:\n$$F = \\dfrac{(2GM - l_0v_0^2)^2m}{4G^2Ml_0^2}$$\n\n2) The work done by $F$ is:\n$$W = mv_0^2$$\n",
"problem_answer": "1) 最大距离时外力$F = \\dfrac{(2GM - l_0v_0^2)^2m}{4G^2Ml_0^2}$；2) 变力$F$做的功为$W = mv_0^2$。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "145",
"problem_text_cn": "【145】一质量为$m=12×10^3\\text{kg}$的太空飞船在围绕月球的圆轨道上运动，其高度$h=100\\text{km}$。为使飞船降落到月球表面，喷气发动机在$P$点作一次短时间发动。从喷口喷出的热气流相对飞船的速度为$u=1000\\text{m/s}$。月球半径为$R=1700\\text{km}$，月球表面的落体加速度$g=1.7\\text{m/s}^2$。飞船可用两种不同方式到达月球（如图145_1所示）。1)向前喷射，使飞船到达月球背面的$A$点，并相切。$A$点与$P$点相对；2)向外侧喷射，使飞船得到一指出月球中心的动量，其轨道与月球表面$B$点相切。试计算上述两种情形下所需要的燃料量。",
"problem_text_en": "[145] A spacecraft of mass $m=12×10^3\\text{kg}$ orbits the Moon in a circular path at height $h=100\\text{km}$. To land on the Moon, its engine fires briefly at point $P$, ejecting gas at speed $u=1000\\text{m/s}$ relative to the spacecraft. The Moon's radius is $R=1700\\text{km}$, and surface gravity is $g=1.7\\text{m/s}^2$. Two landing strategies are used: (1) Forward thrust, placing the spacecraft into an elliptical orbit tangent to the Moon's far side at $A$ (opposite $P$). (2) Outward thrust, giving a radial velocity component, placing the spacecraft into an orbit tangent to the Moon's surface at $B$. Calculate the fuel mass required for each strategy.",
"problem_img": ["145_1.png", "145_2.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["145_3.png"],
"img_cn": ["两种登月轨道示意图（图145_1）；燃料量计算（图145_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Two landing orbit diagrams (Figure 145_1); fuel mass calculation (Figure 145_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】飞船原圆轨道速度：\n$$v_0 = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{gR^2}{R+h}} = 1652\\text{ m/s}$$\n\n**方式1（向前喷射）**：轨道为椭圆，$P$为远月点，$A$为近月点。由角动量守恒$v_a(R+h) = v_A R$和机械能守恒：\n$$\\dfrac{1}{2}mv_a^2 - \\dfrac{GMm}{R+h} = \\dfrac{1}{2}mv_A^2 - \\dfrac{GMm}{R}$$\n解得$v_a = 1628\\text{ m/s}$，速度变化$\\Delta v = v_0 - v_a = 24\\text{ m/s}$。由动量守恒：\n$$mv_0 = (m-\\Delta m_1)v_a + \\Delta m_1(v_a + u)$$\n解得燃料质量：\n$$\\Delta m_1 = \\dfrac{m\\Delta v}{u} = 28.8\\text{ kg}$$\n\n**方式2（向外喷射）**：获得径向速度$v_r$，由角动量守恒$v_0(R+h) = v_B R$和机械能守恒：\n$$\\dfrac{1}{2}m(v_0^2 + v_r^2) - \\dfrac{GMm}{R+h} = \\dfrac{1}{2}mv_B^2 - \\dfrac{GMm}{R}$$\n解得$v_r = 97\\text{ m/s}$。由径向动量守恒：\n$$0 = (m-\\Delta m_2)v_r - \\Delta m_2(u - v_r)$$\n解得燃料质量：\n$$\\Delta m_2 = \\dfrac{mv_r}{u} = 116.4\\text{ kg}$$\n",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] The initial orbital speed is:\n$$v_0 = \\sqrt{\\dfrac{gR^2}{R+h}} = 1652\\text{ m/s}$$\n\n**Strategy 1 (Forward Thrust)** The elliptical orbit has $P$ as the apolune and $A$ as the perilune. Solving conservation laws gives $v_a = 1628\\text{ m/s}$, so $\\Delta v = 24\\text{ m/s}$. By momentum conservation:\n$$\\Delta m_1 = \\dfrac{m\\Delta v}{u} = 28.8\\text{ kg}$$\n\n**Strategy 2 (Outward Thrust)** A radial velocity $v_r = 97\\text{ m/s}$ is acquired. By radial momentum conservation:\n$$\\Delta m_2 = \\dfrac{mv_r}{u} = 116.4\\text{ kg}$$\n",
"problem_answer": "方式1需要燃料$28.8\\text{ kg}$，方式2需要燃料$116.4\\text{ kg}$。方式1更节省燃料。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "146",
"problem_text_cn": "【146】质量为$m$的匀质圆环水平放置在一个表面光滑、半顶角为$\\theta$的圆锥体上。静止后，圆环半径为$r$。求环内张力的增量。",
"problem_text_en": "[146] A uniform ring of mass $m$ rests horizontally on a smooth cone with half-angle $\\theta$. In equilibrium, the ring has radius $r$. Find the tension in the ring.",
"problem_img": ["146_1.png", "146_2.png", "146_3.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["146_4.png"],
"img_cn": ["圆环在圆锥上的受力分析（图146_1）；微元法推导（图146_2）；半圆环受力分析（图146_3）。"],
"img_en": ["Force analysis of the ring on the cone (Figure 146_1); differential element derivation (Figure 146_2); half-ring force analysis (Figure 146_3)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】取微元$\\Delta s = r\\Delta\\varphi$，质量$\\Delta m = \\dfrac{m\\Delta\\varphi}{2\\pi}$。竖直方向平衡：\n$$\\Delta N\\sin\\theta = \\Delta mg$$\n水平方向平衡：\n$$\\Delta N\\cos\\theta = T\\Delta\\varphi$$\n联立解得：\n$$T = \\dfrac{mg}{2\\pi}\\cot\\theta$$\n",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] Consider a small element $\\Delta s = r\\Delta\\varphi$ of mass $\\Delta m = \\dfrac{m\\Delta\\varphi}{2\\pi}$. Vertical equilibrium:\n$$\\Delta N\\sin\\theta = \\Delta mg$$\nHorizontal equilibrium:\n$$\\Delta N\\cos\\theta = T\\Delta\\varphi$$\nSolving gives:\n$$T = \\dfrac{mg}{2\\pi}\\cot\\theta$$\n",
"problem_answer": "环内张力为$T = \\dfrac{mg}{2\\pi}\\cot\\theta$。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "147",
"problem_text_cn": "【147】两个质量分别为$m_1$、$m_2$的光滑小珠，套在竖直放置、固定的光滑大圆环上，并用不可伸长的细绳相连，如图147_1所示。平衡时细绳与铅直线的夹角为$\\theta$，细绳所对圆心角为$\\alpha$。求证$\\tan\\theta = \\dfrac{m_1+m_2}{m_1-m_2}\\cot\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}$（设$m_2>m_1$）。",
"problem_text_en": "[147] Two smooth beads of mass $m_1$ and $m_2$ ($m_2>m_1$) slide on a fixed vertical ring, connected by an inextensible string. In equilibrium, the string makes an angle $\\theta$ with the vertical and subtends a central angle $\\alpha$. Prove $\\tan\\theta = \\dfrac{m_1+m_2}{m_1-m_2}\\cot\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}$.",
"problem_img": ["147_1.png", "147_2.png", "147_3.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["147_4.png"],
"img_cn": ["小珠与细绳系统示意图（图147_1）；受力分析图（图147_2）；力矩平衡推导（图147_3）。"],
"img_en": ["Bead and string system diagram (Figure 147_1); force analysis (Figure 147_2); torque balance derivation (Figure 147_3)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】对两小珠分别受力分析，利用正弦定理得张力：\n$$T = -m_1g\\dfrac{\\cos\\left(\\theta+\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}\\right)}{\\cos\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}} = m_2g\\dfrac{\\cos\\left(\\theta-\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}\\right)}{\\cos\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}}$$\n消去$T$并展开余弦函数，整理得：\n$$\\tan\\theta = \\dfrac{m_1+m_2}{m_1-m_2}\\cot\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}$$\n\n或对整体应用力矩平衡：\n$$m_1gR\\sin\\beta_1 = m_2gR\\sin\\beta_2$$\n代入$\\beta_1 = \\theta-\\dfrac{\\pi-\\alpha}{2}$，$\\beta_2 = \\dfrac{\\pi-\\alpha}{2}-\\theta$，化简后同样得证。",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] Applying the law of sines to each bead's force balance gives:\n$$T = -m_1g\\dfrac{\\cos\\left(\\theta+\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}\\right)}{\\cos\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}} = m_2g\\dfrac{\\cos\\left(\\theta-\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}\\right)}{\\cos\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}}$$\nEliminating $T$ and expanding the cosine terms yields:\n$$\\tan\\theta = \\dfrac{m_1+m_2}{m_1-m_2}\\cot\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}$$\n\nAlternatively, torque balance for the system gives the same result.",
"problem_answer": "证明成立：$\\tan\\theta = \\dfrac{m_1+m_2}{m_1-m_2}\\cot\\dfrac{\\alpha}{2}$。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "148",
"problem_text_cn": "【148】如图148_1所示，在倾角为$\\varphi$的足够大粗糙斜面上，有一质量为$m$的质点，用一根弹性绳栓住。绳的另一端固定在斜面上$o'$点，弹性绳原长为$L$，劲度系数为$k$，斜面与质点间的静摩擦系数为$\\mu$。试确定质点在斜面上可静止的区域，并画出此区域边界的示意图。",
"problem_text_en": "[148] A particle of mass $m$ is attached to an elastic cord (natural length $L$, spring constant $k$) fixed at $o'$ on a rough inclined plane (angle $\\varphi$, coefficient of static friction $\\mu$). Determine the region where the particle can remain stationary and sketch the boundary.",
"problem_img": ["148_1.png", "148_2.png", "148_3.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["148_4.png"],
"img_cn": ["弹性绳约束质点示意图（图148_1）；二力平衡区域（图148_2）；三力平衡区域（图148_3）。"],
"img_en": ["Particle constrained by elastic cord (Figure 148_1); two-force equilibrium region (Figure 148_2); three-force equilibrium region (Figure 148_3)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1. **弹性绳无伸长时（二力区域）**：质点仅受重力分力$P_\\parallel = mg\\sin\\varphi$和摩擦力$f$。\n   - 若$\\mu \\geq \\tan\\varphi$，则$f_{\\max} = \\mu mg\\cos\\varphi \\geq P_\\parallel$，质点可在以$o'$为圆心、$L$为半径的圆Ⅰ内任意静止。\n   - 若$\\mu < \\tan\\varphi$，则$f_{\\max} < P_\\parallel$，圆Ⅰ内无静止区域。\n\n2. **弹性绳有伸长时（三力区域）**：质点受$P_\\parallel$、$f$和弹性力$F = k(r-L)$。当$f = f_{\\max}$时，三力平衡构成闭合三角形，静止区域边界为封闭曲线Ⅲ，其极坐标方程为：\n$$(mg\\sin\\varphi + k(r-L)\\cos\\theta)^2 + (k(r-L)\\sin\\theta)^2 = (\\mu mg\\cos\\varphi)^2$$\n\n3. **静止区域的确定**：\n   - 当$\\mu > \\tan\\varphi$：圆Ⅰ与闭合曲线Ⅲ的交集为静止区域。\n   - 当$\\mu = \\tan\\varphi$：圆Ⅰ与闭合曲线Ⅲ的交点连线为过$o'$的直径，静止区域为两者之和。\n   - 当$\\mu < \\tan\\varphi$：仅闭合曲线Ⅲ内部为静止区域。",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution]\n1. **Elastic cord unstretched (two-force region)** The particle experiences $P_\\parallel = mg\\sin\\varphi$ and friction $f$.\n   - If $\\mu \\geq \\tan\\varphi$, $f_{\\max} \\geq P_\\parallel$, so the particle can rest anywhere inside circle Ⅰ (center $o'$, radius $L$).\n   - If $\\mu < \\tan\\varphi$, $f_{\\max} < P_\\parallel$, so no equilibrium in circle Ⅰ.\n\n2. **Elastic cord stretched (three-force region)** The particle experiences $P_\\parallel$, $f$, and elastic force $F = k(r-L)$. At maximum friction, the force balance gives a closed curve Ⅲ with polar equation:\n$$(mg\\sin\\varphi + k(r-L)\\cos\\theta)^2 + (k(r-L)\\sin\\theta)^2 = (\\mu mg\\cos\\varphi)^2$$\n\n3. **Stationary region**:\n   - $\\mu > \\tan\\varphi$: Intersection of circle Ⅰ and curve Ⅲ.\n   - $\\mu = \\tan\\varphi$: Union of circle Ⅰ and curve Ⅲ.\n   - $\\mu < \\tan\\varphi$: Interior of curve Ⅲ only.",
"problem_answer": "质点可静止的区域由静摩擦系数与倾角的关系决定，边界为圆Ⅰ和闭合曲线Ⅲ的组合。",
"difficulty": "4",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "149",
"problem_text_cn": "【149】一长方形均匀薄板$AB$，可绕通过其重心、垂直于长度方向的固定水平轴$o$（垂直纸面）自由转动，如图149_1所示。在板上轴$o$左侧距$o$点为$L$处以轻绳悬挂一质量为$m$的物体。在轴$o$的右侧板上放一质量也是$m$的立方体，立方体边长以及其左侧面到轴$o$的距离均为$l$。已知起始时板处于水平位置，挂物与地面相接触，轻绳绷紧，整个系统处于平衡状态。现在立方体右侧面中心处施一沿水平方向向右的力$F$去拉它，若用符号$\mu$表示立方体与板面间的静摩擦系数，当$F$从零开始逐渐增大至某一数值时，整个系统的平衡状态将开始被破坏。试讨论：可能出现几种平衡状态被破坏的情况？每种情况出现的条件是什么？要求在以$\mu$为纵坐标、$x=\left(\dfrac{2L}{l}-3\right)$为横坐标的图中，画出可能发生这几种情况出现的区域。不要求讨论这些区域交界线上的平衡状态被破坏的情况。",
"problem_text_en": "[149] A uniform rectangular plate $AB$ rotates freely about a horizontal axis $o$ through its center of mass. A mass $m$ hangs from a string at distance $L$ left of $o$, and a cube of mass $m$ (side length $l$) rests on the plate, with its left face $l$ right of $o$. Initially, the plate is horizontal, the hanging mass touches the ground, and the string is taut. A horizontal force $F$ is applied to the cube's right face. Discuss the possible ways equilibrium is broken and their conditions, and sketch the regions in a $\mu$-$x$ graph ($x=\\dfrac{2L}{l}-3$).",
"problem_img": ["149_1.png", "149_2.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["149_3.png"],
"img_cn": ["薄板与立方体系统示意图（图149_1）；平衡破坏条件推导（图149_2）；区域划分图（图149_3）。"],
"img_en": ["Plate and cube system diagram (Figure 149_1); equilibrium failure condition derivation (Figure 149_2); region division graph (Figure 149_3)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】初始平衡时，绳张力$T \\leq mg$，力矩平衡$TL = mg\\left(l+\\dfrac{l}{2}\\right)$，得$x = \\dfrac{2L}{l}-3 \\geq 0$。\n\n当$F$增大时，平衡破坏有三种可能：\n1. **立方体滑动**：$F > \\mu mg$，条件为$\\mu < 1$且$\\mu < x$。\n2. **立方体绕右下棱转动**：$F > mg$，条件为$1 < \\mu$且$1 < x$。\n3. **板偏转**：$F > xmg$，条件为$x < 1$且$x < \\mu$。\n\n在$\mu$-$x$图中，区域划分如下：\n- 当$\mu < 1$且$\mu < x$：立方体滑动。\n- 当$1 < \mu$且$1 < x$：立方体转动。\n- 当$x < 1$且$x < \mu$：板偏转。",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] Initial equilibrium requires $T \\leq mg$ and $TL = mg\\left(l+\\dfrac{l}{2}\\right)$, giving $x = \\dfrac{2L}{l}-3 \\geq 0$.\n\nAs $F$ increases, equilibrium fails in three ways:\n1. **Cube slides**: $F > \\mu mg$, when $\mu < 1$ and $\mu < x$.\n2. **Cube rotates about its lower right edge**: $F > mg$, when $1 < \mu$ and $1 < x$.\n3. **Plate deflects**: $F > xmg$, when $x < 1$ and $x < \mu$.\n\nRegions in the $\mu$-$x$ graph:\n- $\mu < 1$ and $\mu < x$: Cube slides.\n- $1 < \mu$ and $1 < x$: Cube rotates.\n- $x < 1$ and $x < \mu$: Plate deflects.",
"problem_answer": "平衡破坏有三种情况：立方体滑动、立方体转动、板偏转，条件由$\mu$与$x$的相对大小决定。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "150",
"problem_text_cn": "【150】半径为$R$的光滑半球形碗，固定于水平桌面上，一根长为$L$的光滑匀质棒，一端在碗内，一端在碗外，斜靠在碗缘。求平衡时，棒与水平面的夹角$\theta$。",
"problem_text_en": "[150] A smooth hemispherical bowl (radius $R$) rests on a horizontal table. A smooth uniform rod (length $L$) leans against the bowl's edge, with one end inside the bowl and the other outside. Find the angle $\theta$ between the rod and the horizontal in equilibrium.",
"problem_img": ["150_1.png", "150_2.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["150_3.png"],
"img_cn": ["棒与半球碗示意图（图150_1）；几何关系推导（图150_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Rod and hemispherical bowl diagram (Figure 150_1); geometric relation derivation (Figure 150_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】当$L > 4R$时棒无法平衡；当$L = 4R$时$\theta = 0$。当$L < 4R$时，由三力汇交原理和几何关系：\n$$\\overline{AC} = 2R\\cos\\theta - 2R\\sin\\theta\\tan\\theta = \\dfrac{L}{2}$$\n化简得：\n$$2\\cos^2\\theta - \\dfrac{L}{4R}\\cos\\theta - 1 = 0$$\n解得：\n$$\\cos\\theta = \\dfrac{1}{4}\\left[\\dfrac{L}{4R} + \\sqrt{\\left(\\dfrac{L}{4R}\\right)^2 + 8}\\right]$$",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] The rod cannot balance if $L > 4R$, and $\theta = 0$ if $L = 4R$. For $L < 4R$, using force concurrency and geometry:\n$$\\overline{AC} = 2R\\cos\\theta - 2R\\sin\\theta\\tan\\theta = \\dfrac{L}{2}$$\nSolving the quadratic equation:\n$$\\cos\\theta = \\dfrac{1}{4}\\left[\\dfrac{L}{4R} + \\sqrt{\\left(\\dfrac{L}{4R}\\right)^2 + 8}\\right]$$",
"problem_answer": "平衡时夹角满足$\\cos\\theta = \\dfrac{1}{4}\\left[\\dfrac{L}{4R} + \\sqrt{\\left(\\dfrac{L}{4R}\\right)^2 + 8}\\right]$（$L < 4R$）。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
},
{
"problem_id": "151",
"problem_text_cn": "【151】课桌的桌面与水平面之间的夹角$\alpha=40^\\circ$，在桌面上放一支正六角形铅笔，使铅笔既不向下滚动，又不向下滑动，如图151_1所示。试求：1)在此情况下，铅笔与桌面间的静摩擦系数应有多大？2)铅笔应该与桌面上水平方向成多大角度$\varphi$放置？",
"problem_text_en": "[151] A desk surface is inclined at $\alpha=40^\\circ$ to the horizontal. A regular hexagonal pencil rests on it, neither sliding nor rolling downward. (1) Find the required coefficient of static friction $\mu$. (2) Find the angle $\varphi$ between the pencil and the horizontal on the desk.",
"problem_img": ["151_1.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["151_2.png"],
"img_cn": ["铅笔在斜面上的受力分析（图151_1）；滑动与滚动临界条件推导（图151_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Force analysis of the pencil on the incline (Figure 151_1); sliding and rolling critical condition derivation (Figure 151_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1. **不滑动条件**：$mg\\sin\\alpha \\leq \\mu mg\\cos\\alpha$，得$\mu \\geq \\tan\\alpha \\approx 0.831$。\n2. **不滚动条件**：对过接触点平行于铅笔轴向的轴取矩，得：\n$$mg\\sin\\alpha \\cdot \\cos\\varphi_m \\cdot l\\cos30^\\circ = mg\\cos\\alpha \\cdot l\\sin30^\\circ$$\n解得：\n$$\\cos\\varphi_m = \\dfrac{\\tan30^\\circ}{\\tan\\alpha} \\approx 0.688 \\implies \\varphi_m \\approx 46^\\circ30'$$\n即$\varphi \\geq 46^\\circ30'$。",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution]\n1. **No sliding**: $mg\\sin\\alpha \\leq \\mu mg\\cos\\alpha$ $\implies$ $\mu \\geq \\tan\\alpha \\approx 0.831$.\n2. **No rolling**: Taking moments about the contact axis:\n$$mg\\sin\\alpha \\cdot \\cos\\varphi_m \\cdot l\\cos30^\\circ = mg\\cos\\alpha \\cdot l\\sin30^\\circ$$\nSolving gives:\n$$\\cos\\varphi_m = \\dfrac{\\tan30^\\circ}{\\tan\\alpha} \\approx 0.688 \\implies \\varphi_m \\approx 46^\\circ30'$$\nso $\varphi \\geq 46^\\circ30'$.",
"problem_answer": "1) 静摩擦系数$\mu \\geq 0.831$；2) 放置角度$\varphi \\geq 46^\\circ30'$。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
},
{
"problem_id": "152",
