"img_cn": ["三圆柱体堆叠示意图（图152_1）；受力分析与力矩平衡（图152_2）；摩擦系数计算（图152_3）。"],
"img_en": ["Three-cylinder stack diagram (Figure 152_1); force analysis and torque balance (Figure 152_2); friction coefficient calculation (Figure 152_3)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】对圆柱体受力分析，力矩平衡得$f_1 = f_2$，且$N_1 = N_2 + G$，故$\dfrac{f_1}{N_1} < \dfrac{f_2}{N_2}$，即$\mu_1 < \mu_2$。\n\n整体受力得$N_1 = \\dfrac{3}{2}G$，$N_2 = \\dfrac{1}{2}G$。竖直方向平衡：\n$$2N_2\\cos30^\\circ + 2f_1\\sin30^\\circ = G$$\n解得$f_1 = G\\left(1-\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\right)$，因此：\n$$\\mu_1 \\geq \\dfrac{2}{3}\\left(1-\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\right) \\approx 0.09,\\quad \\mu_2 \\geq 2\\left(1-\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\right) \\approx 0.27$$",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] Force and torque balance show $f_1 = f_2$ and $N_1 = N_2 + G$, so $\dfrac{f_1}{N_1} < \dfrac{f_2}{N_2}$ $\implies$ $\mu_1 < \mu_2$.\n\nOverall equilibrium gives $N_1 = \\dfrac{3}{2}G$, $N_2 = \\dfrac{1}{2}G$. Vertical balance:\n$$2N_2\\cos30^\\circ + 2f_1\\sin30^\\circ = G$$\nSolving for $f_1$ yields:\n$$\\mu_1 \\geq \\dfrac{2}{3}\\left(1-\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\right) \\approx 0.09,\\quad \\mu_2 \\geq 2\\left(1-\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\right) \\approx 0.27$$",
"problem_answer": "最小摩擦系数满足$\mu_1 < \mu_2$，且$\mu_1 \\geq 0.09$，$\mu_2 \\geq 0.27$。",
