"problem_text_cn": "【158】一块厚度为$h$的匀质长方形物块，静止地放在半径为$R$的半圆柱顶面上。设摩擦系数足够大，长方形物块与柱面不发生滑动。求此静止位置为稳定平衡的条件。",
"problem_text_en": "[158] A uniform rectangular block of thickness $h$ rests on top of a semicylinder of radius $R$. Friction is large enough to prevent sliding. Find the condition for the equilibrium to be stable.",
