"img_en": ["Stable equilibrium analysis of the block on the semicylinder (Figure 158_1); center of mass height variation derivation (Figure 158_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】当物块偏离平衡位置时，重心高度变化为：\n$$y = \\left(R+\\dfrac{h}{2}\\right)\\cos\\theta + R\\theta\\sin\\theta$$\n小角度近似得：\n$$y \\approx \\left(R+\\dfrac{h}{2}\\right) + \\dfrac{\\theta^2}{2}\\left(R-\\dfrac{h}{2}\\right)$$\n稳定平衡要求重心高度增加，即：\n$$R-\\dfrac{h}{2} > 0 \\implies R > \\dfrac{h}{2}$$\n",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] When the block is displaced, the center of mass height is:\n$$y = \\left(R+\\dfrac{h}{2}\\right)\\cos\\theta + R\\theta\\sin\\theta$$\nFor small $\\theta$, this approximates to:\n$$y \\approx \\left(R+\\dfrac{h}{2}\\right) + \\dfrac{\\theta^2}{2}\\left(R-\\dfrac{h}{2}\\right)$$\nStability requires the height to increase, so:\n$$R > \\dfrac{h}{2}$$\n",
"problem_answer": "稳定平衡的条件为$R > \\dfrac{h}{2}$（或$h < 2R$）。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
}
{
"problem_id": "159",
"problem_text_cn": "【159】截面为正方形的木棒水平地浮在水面上，为使木棒对于水平轴的扭转扰动呈稳定平衡，木棒的比重应为多大？",
"problem_text_en": "[159] A square-section wooden rod floats horizontally on water. Find the specific gravity of the rod for stable equilibrium against torsional disturbances about a horizontal axis.",
"problem_img": ["159_1.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["159_2.png"],
"img_cn": ["正方形木棒浮在水面的受力分析（图159_1）；稳定平衡条件推导（图159_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Force analysis of the square rod floating on water (Figure 159_1); derivation of stable equilibrium conditions (Figure 159_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】设木棒截面边长为$2a$，浸入水中深度为$2b$。稳定平衡要求浮心$B$在重心$G$的右侧，即$x_B > x_C$。通过几何推导得二次不等式：\n$$6b^2 - 6ab + a^2 > 0$$\n解得：\n$$b > \\dfrac{a}{3-\\sqrt{3}} \\quad \\text{或} \\quad b < \\dfrac{a}{3+\\sqrt{3}}$$\n因此比重$r = \\dfrac{b}{a}$满足：\n$$r > \\dfrac{1}{3-\\sqrt{3}} \\approx 0.79 \\quad \\text{或} \\quad r < \\dfrac{1}{3+\\sqrt{3}} \\approx 0.21$$",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] Let the rod's side length be $2a$ and immersion depth $2b$. Stability requires the center of buoyancy $B$ to lie to the right of the center of mass $G$ ($x_B > x_C$). Solving the quadratic inequality:\n$$6b^2 - 6ab + a^2 > 0$$\nGives:\n$$r > \\dfrac{1}{3-\\sqrt{3}} \\approx 0.79 \\quad \\text{or} \\quad r < \\dfrac{1}{3+\\sqrt{3}} \\approx 0.21$$",
"problem_answer": "木棒比重需满足$r > 0.79$或$r < 0.21$才能使扭转扰动下的平衡稳定。",
"difficulty": "3",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
},
{
"problem_id": "160",
"problem_text_cn": "【160】半径为$R$的圆环绕其铅垂直径以不变的角速度$\\omega$匀速转动。两质量为$m$的珠子用长为$L=R$的轻杆相连，套在圆环上可以无摩擦地滑动。试求轻杆在圆环上的平衡位置（用环心$o$与杆心$C$的连线与铅垂轴的夹角$\\theta$表示），并分析平衡的稳定性。",
"problem_text_en": "[160] A ring of radius $R$ rotates uniformly about its vertical diameter with angular velocity $\\omega$. Two beads of mass $m$ are connected by a light rod of length $L=R$ and slide frictionlessly on the ring. Find the equilibrium position of the rod (angle $\\theta$ between $oC$ and the vertical) and analyze stability.",
"problem_img": ["160_1.png", "160_2.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["160_3.png"],
"img_cn": ["圆环与珠子系统示意图（图160_1）；力矩平衡与稳定性分析（图160_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Ring and bead system diagram (Figure 160_1); torque balance and stability analysis (Figure 160_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】在转动参考系中，合力矩为：\n$$M = -mR\\sin\\theta\\left(\\sqrt{3}g - \\omega^2R\\cos\\theta\\right)$$\n平衡时$M=0$，解得：\n- 当$\\omega^2 > \\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{R}$时，平衡位置为$\\theta=0$、$\\theta=\\pi$、$\\theta=\\arccos\\left(\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{\\omega^2R}\\right)$，其中$\\theta=\\arccos\\left(\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{\\omega^2R}\\right)$稳定，其余不稳定。\n- 当$\\omega^2 \\leq \\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{R}$时，平衡位置为$\\theta=0$（稳定）、$\\theta=\\pi$（不稳定）。",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] In the rotating frame, the total torque is:\n$$M = -mR\\sin\\theta\\left(\\sqrt{3}g - \\omega^2R\\cos\\theta\\right)$$\nEquilibrium occurs at $M=0$:\n- If $\\omega^2 > \\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{R}$, equilibrium positions are $\\theta=0$, $\\theta=\\pi$, and $\\theta=\\arccos\\left(\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{\\omega^2R}\\right)$. Only $\\theta=\\arccos\\left(\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{\\omega^2R}\\right)$ is stable.\n- If $\\omega^2 \\leq \\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{R}$, equilibrium positions are $\\theta=0$ (stable) and $\\theta=\\pi$ (unstable).",
"problem_answer": "平衡位置由$\\omega$决定，稳定性分析如上。当$\\omega^2 > \\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{R}$时，$\\theta=\\arccos\\left(\\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{\\omega^2R}\\right)$为稳定平衡；当$\\omega^2 \\leq \\dfrac{\\sqrt{3}g}{R}$时，$\\theta=0$为稳定平衡。",
"difficulty": "4",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics", "Rotating Frames", "Stability"]
},
{
"problem_id": "161",
"problem_text_cn": "【161】质量密度为$\\rho$的液体中，有一任意形状、任意取向的平面，面积为$S$，平面几何中心离水面的深度为$h_c$。求此平面所受液体的总压力为多大？",
"problem_text_en": "[161] In a liquid of density $\\rho$, a plane of area $S$ is oriented arbitrarily, with its geometric center at depth $h_c$ below the surface. Find the total hydrostatic force on the plane.",
"problem_img": ["161_1.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["161_2.png"],
"img_cn": ["平面在液体中的受力分析（图161_1）；总压力推导（图161_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Force analysis of the plane in the liquid (Figure 161_1); total pressure derivation (Figure 161_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】平面上各面元的压力之和为：\n$$F = \\sum \\rho g h_i \\Delta S_i = \\rho g S \\dfrac{\\sum h_i \\Delta S_i}{S}$$\n其中$\\dfrac{\\sum h_i \\Delta S_i}{S}$为平面几何中心的深度$h_c$，因此：\n$$F = \\rho g h_c S$$\n此结果与平面取向无关，仅与几何中心深度和面积有关。",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] The total force is the sum of pressures on all surface elements:\n$$F = \\rho g S h_c$$\nThis result is independent of the plane's orientation, depending only on the depth of the geometric center and the area.",
"problem_answer": "平面所受总压力为$F = \\rho g h_c S$。",
"difficulty": "2",
"problem_tags": ["Fluid Mechanics", "Hydrostatic Pressure"]
},
{
