"img_en": ["Force analysis of balls in a density-gradient liquid (Figure 162_1); tension derivation (Figure 162_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】液体密度分布为$\\rho_x = \\rho_0 + \\dfrac{x}{H}(\\rho-\\rho_0)$。两球浮力分别为$F_{\\text{浮}1} = \\rho_{x_1} V g$，$F_{\\text{浮}2} = \\rho_{x_2} V g$，且$x_2 - x_1 = l$。平衡方程相减得：\n$$T = \\dfrac{1}{2}Vg\\left[(\\rho_2 - \\rho_1) - \\dfrac{l}{H}(\\rho - \\rho_0)\\right]$$",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] The liquid density is $\\rho_x = \\rho_0 + \\dfrac{x}{H}(\\rho-\\rho_0)$. Subtracting the equilibrium equations for the two balls gives:\n$$T = \\dfrac{1}{2}Vg\\left[(\\rho_2 - \\rho_1) - \\dfrac{l}{H}(\\rho - \\rho_0)\\right]$$",
"problem_answer": "绳中张力为$T = \\dfrac{1}{2}Vg\\left[(\\rho_2 - \\rho_1) - \\dfrac{l}{H}(\\rho - \\rho_0)\\right]$。",
