"img_en": ["Force analysis of the spherical surface in liquid (Figure 165_1); hemisphere pressure derivation (Figure 165_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1. **上、下半球面压力**：\n   - 上半球面：$f_1=\\rho g\\pi R^2\\left(H-\\dfrac{2}{3}R\\right)$（向下）\n   - 下半球面：$f_2=\\rho g\\pi R^2\\left(H+\\dfrac{2}{3}R\\right)$（向上）\n2. **左上半球面压力**：合力大小为：\n$$F=\\rho g\\pi R^2\\sqrt{H^2-\\dfrac{4}{3}RH\\cos\\theta+\\dfrac{4}{9}R^2}$$\n方向与竖直方向夹角$\\varphi$满足：\n$$\\tan\\varphi=\\dfrac{H\\sin\\theta}{H\\cos\\theta-\\dfrac{2}{3}R}$$",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution]\n1. **Pressure on upper/lower hemispheres**:\n   - Upper: $f_1=\\rho g\\pi R^2\\left(H-\\dfrac{2}{3}R\\right)$ (downward)\n   - Lower: $f_2=\\rho g\\pi R^2\\left(H+\\dfrac{2}{3}R\\right)$ (upward)\n2. **Pressure on upper-left hemisphere**:\n   $$F=\\rho g\\pi R^2\\sqrt{H^2-\\dfrac{4}{3}RH\\cos\\theta+\\dfrac{4}{9}R^2}$$\n   Direction: $\\tan\\varphi=\\dfrac{H\\sin\\theta}{H\\cos\\theta-\\dfrac{2}{3}R}$",
"problem_answer": "1) 上半球面压力$\\rho g\\pi R^2\\left(H-\\dfrac{2}{3}R\\right)$，下半球面压力$\\rho g\\pi R^2\\left(H+\\dfrac{2}{3}R\\right)$；2) 左上半球面压力大小为$\\rho g\\pi R^2\\sqrt{H^2-\\dfrac{4}{3}RH\\cos\\theta+\\dfrac{4}{9}R^2}$，方向如上。",
