"problem_text_en": "[167] Two identical cylinders of radius $R$ and mass $m$ rest on a horizontal table, enclosed in a rigid box (top, left, right panels) with side spacing $4R$. A third cylinder of radius $r$ ($0<r\\leqslant(\\sqrt{2}-1)R$) and mass $m$ is placed on top. Find the minimum coefficient of static friction $\mu$ for all three cylinders to be lifted when the box is pulled upward.",
