"problem_text_en": "[170] A uniform ladder of mass $M$ leans against a wall (coefficient of friction $\mu_1$) and rests on the ground (coefficient of friction $\mu_2$). A person of mass $m$ climbs slowly. Find the safe angle $\theta$ between the ladder and the ground.",
