"problem_id": "171",
"problem_text_cn": "【171】如图7-例6(a)，有两根不可伸长的柔绳，长度分别为$l_1$和$l_2$。它们的下端在$C$点相连结，并悬挂一质量为$m$的重物。上端分别与质量可忽略的小圆环$A$、$B$相连。圆环套在圆形水平横杆上。$A$、$B$可在横杆上滑动，它们与横杆间的静摩擦系数分别为$\mu_1$和$\mu_2$。已知$l_1$和$l_2$的数值，且$l_1<l_2$。试求$\mu_1$和$\mu_2$的各种取值情况下，此系统处于静力平衡时两环间的距离$AB$。",
"problem_text_en": "[171] Two inextensible strings of length $l_1<l_2$ connect a mass $m$ to rings $A$ and $B$ on a horizontal rod, with coefficients of friction $\mu_1$ and $\mu_2$. Find the equilibrium distance $AB$ between the rings for different values of $\mu_1$ and $\mu_2$.",
"problem_img": ["171_1.png", "171_2.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["171_3.png"],
"img_cn": ["柔绳与圆环系统受力分析（图171_1）；临界距离推导（图171_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Force analysis of the string and ring system (Figure 171_1); critical distance derivation (Figure 171_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1. **绳$BC$未张紧时**：$0 \\leqslant AB \\leqslant \\sqrt{l_2^2-l_1^2}$，与摩擦系数无关。\n2. **绳$BC$张紧且$\mu_2 \\leqslant \\sqrt{(l_2/l_1)^2-1}$时**：仅$A$、$C$、$m$共线，$AB$仍满足上式。\n3. **绳$BC$张紧且$\mu_2 > \\sqrt{(l_2/l_1)^2-1}$时**：\n   - 若$\\dfrac{l_2^2}{1+\\mu_2^2} < \\dfrac{l_1^2}{1+\\mu_1^2}$：$AB \\leqslant \\dfrac{1}{\\sqrt{1+\\mu_1^2}}\\left(l_1\\mu_1+\\sqrt{l_2^2+\\mu_1^2l_2^2-l_1^2}\\right)$\n   - 若$\\dfrac{l_2^2}{1+\\mu_2^2} > \\dfrac{l_1^2}{1+\\mu_1^2}$：$AB \\leqslant \\dfrac{1}{\\sqrt{1+\\mu_2^2}}\\left(l_2\\mu_2+\\sqrt{l_1^2+\\mu_2^2l_1^2-l_2^2}\\right)$\n   - 若$\\dfrac{l_2^2}{1+\\mu_2^2} = \\dfrac{l_1^2}{1+\\mu_1^2}$：$AB \\leqslant \\dfrac{l_2}{\\sqrt{1+\\mu_2^2}}(\\mu_1+\\mu_2)$",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution]\n1. **Before string $BC$ is taut**: $0 \\leqslant AB \\leqslant \\sqrt{l_2^2-l_1^2}$, independent of friction.\n2. **After $BC$ is taut and $\mu_2 \\leqslant \\sqrt{(l_2/l_1)^2-1}$**: Only $A$, $C$, $m$ are collinear, so $AB$ remains as above.\n3. **After $BC$ is taut and $\mu_2 > \\sqrt{(l_2/l_1)^2-1}$**:\n   - If $\\dfrac{l_2^2}{1+\\mu_2^2} < \\dfrac{l_1^2}{1+\\mu_1^2}$: $AB \\leqslant \\dfrac{1}{\\sqrt{1+\\mu_1^2}}\\left(l_1\\mu_1+\\sqrt{l_2^2+\\mu_1^2l_2^2-l_1^2}\\right)$\n   - If $\\dfrac{l_2^2}{1+\\mu_2^2} > \\dfrac{l_1^2}{1+\\mu_1^2}$: $AB \\leqslant \\dfrac{1}{\\sqrt{1+\\mu_2^2}}\\left(l_2\\mu_2+\\sqrt{l_1^2+\\mu_2^2l_1^2-l_2^2}\\right)$\n   - If $\\dfrac{l_2^2}{1+\\mu_2^2} = \\dfrac{l_1^2}{1+\\mu_1^2}$: $AB \\leqslant \\dfrac{l_2}{\\sqrt{1+\\mu_2^2}}(\\mu_1+\\mu_2)$",
"problem_answer": "两环间距离$AB$的取值范围由摩擦系数和绳长比决定，如上所示。",
"difficulty": "4",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
