{
"problem_id": "174",
"problem_text_cn": "【174】有一半径为$R$的圆柱体水平地横架在空中，有质量为$m_1$和$m_2$（$m_1=2m_2=2m$）的两个小物块（视为质点）用长为$\\dfrac{1}{2}\\pi R$的不可伸长的柔软细线相连，成为一个系统。质点与圆柱表面的静摩擦系数$\\mu<1$，系统横跨在圆柱上，$m_1$在右边，细线紧贴在圆柱面上，与圆柱表面无摩擦。令圆柱绕轴线沿顺时针方向极缓慢地旋转，直至柱上系统将要开始滑落。由此位置再极缓慢地沿逆时针方向转动圆柱体。问转过多大角度后，系统开始从左边滑落？（角度可用三角函数表示）",
"problem_text_en": "[174] A cylinder of radius $R$ is suspended horizontally. Two masses $m_1=2m$ and $m_2=m$ are connected by an inextensible string of length $\\dfrac{1}{2}\\pi R$, resting on the cylinder with coefficient of friction $\\mu<1$. The cylinder is rotated clockwise until the system is about to slip, then rotated counterclockwise. Find the angle $\\Delta\\theta$ after which the system slips to the left.",
"problem_img": ["174_1.png", "174_2.png"],
"problem_img_process": ["174_3.png"],
"img_cn": ["物块在圆柱上的受力分析（图174_1）；临界角推导（图174_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Force analysis of masses on the cylinder (Figure 174_1); critical angle derivation (Figure 174_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】\n1. **起始临界角**：$\\tan\\theta_1=\\dfrac{2-\\mu}{2\\mu+1}$\n2. **末态临界角**：\n   - 当$\\mu<\\dfrac{1}{2}$时，$\\tan\\theta_2=\\dfrac{2+\\mu}{1-2\\mu}$，转过角度$\\Delta\\theta=\\arctan\\dfrac{2+\\mu}{1-2\\mu}-\\arctan\\dfrac{2-\\mu}{2\\mu+1}$\n   - 当$\\mu=\\dfrac{1}{2}$时，$\\Delta\\theta=\\arctan\\dfrac{4}{3}$\n   - 当$\\dfrac{1}{2}<\\mu<1$时，$\\tan\\theta=\\dfrac{4}{3}\\mu-\\dfrac{1}{3}\\sqrt{4\\mu^2+3}$，转过角度$\\Delta\\theta=\\arctan\\dfrac{1+2\\mu}{2-\\mu}+\\arctan\\left[\\dfrac{4}{3}\\mu-\\dfrac{1}{3}\\sqrt{4\\mu^2+3}\\right]$",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution]\n1. **Initial critical angle**: $\\tan\\theta_1=\\dfrac{2-\\mu}{2\\mu+1}$\n2. **Final critical angle**:\n   - If $\\mu<\\dfrac{1}{2}$: $\\tan\\theta_2=\\dfrac{2+\\mu}{1-2\\mu}$, $\\Delta\\theta=\\arctan\\dfrac{2+\\mu}{1-2\\mu}-\\arctan\\dfrac{2-\\mu}{2\\mu+1}$\n   - If $\\mu=\\dfrac{1}{2}$: $\\Delta\\theta=\\arctan\\dfrac{4}{3}$\n   - If $\\dfrac{1}{2}<\\mu<1$: $\\tan\\theta=\\dfrac{4}{3}\\mu-\\dfrac{1}{3}\\sqrt{4\\mu^2+3}$, $\\Delta\\theta=\\arctan\\dfrac{1+2\\mu}{2-\\mu}+\\arctan\\left[\\dfrac{4}{3}\\mu-\\dfrac{1}{3}\\sqrt{4\\mu^2+3}\\right]$",
"problem_answer": "转过角度由摩擦系数决定，如上所示。",
"difficulty": "4",
"problem_tags": ["Mechanics"]
