"img_cn": ["板堆重心分析（图175_1）；极限伸出长度推导（图175_2）。"],
"img_en": ["Center of mass analysis of the plank stack (Figure 175_1); maximum overhang derivation (Figure 175_2)."],
"problem_solution_cn": "【分析与解】从最上方开始，每块板的右端必须放在上方所有板共同重心的正下方。递推得第$n$块板的极限伸出长度为：\n$$x_n = x_{n-1} + \\dfrac{1}{n}l$$\n因此各板伸出的极限长度依次为：\n$$l,\\;\\dfrac{1}{2}l,\\;\\dfrac{1}{3}l,\\;\\dots,\\;\\dfrac{1}{n}l$$",
"problem_solution_en": "[Analysis and Solution] Starting from the top plank, each plank's right end must lie directly below the combined center of mass of all planks above it. Recursion gives the maximum overhang for the $n$-th plank:\n$$x_n = x_{n-1} + \\dfrac{1}{n}l$$\nThus, the overhangs are:\n$$l,\\;\\dfrac{1}{2}l,\\;\\dfrac{1}{3}l,\\;\\dots,\\;\\dfrac{1}{n}l$$",
"problem_answer": "第$n$块板的极限伸出长度为$\\dfrac{1}{n}l$，总最大伸出长度为$l\\sum_{k=1}^n\\dfrac{1}{k}$。",
